AVGEvent_Fuchsia.Row51112004_Aside_AboutRole112: (I hope Fuchsia doesn't feel that my company disturbed her rest today...)

AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202097_From_Role124001: The thirty-second mark was just a basic passing grade.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204119_From_OtherRole: “Bunny Mark got more than one parent. Next time, don't you dare try to scrap him without a single word!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204102_From_OtherRole: “...A few days ago, someone going by the title of “Navigator” came to me with a badly damaged bot.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204106_From_OtherRole: “Whether it comes to worrying about an exam or deciding to become an investigator all on your own... you worry about it alone, never discuss it with anyone, and make the decision all by yourself!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204110_From_OtherRole: “But, even if you want to be a hero, why don't you tell us when you were struggling?”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204108_From_OtherRole: “You're just 'Kokona', a little brat who likes to show off!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204114_From_OtherRole: “When I repaired the bot, it became clear to me... you never realized the importance of all its combat logs!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204103_From_OtherRole: “Seeing all the marks from field use and maintenance... It made me realize how hard you must have been working. But you're just trying to go it alone again!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204117_From_OtherRole: “The design data of each module has been stored in this projector. We've done the assembly - you just need to finish up the fine-tuning.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204098_From_OtherRole: “Haha... We all have much to say, but allow me to speak for everyone for now.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204113_From_OtherRole: “Hmpf! There's still so many things I want to say, but this will have to suffice for now.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204122_From_OtherRole: “And don't forget, we've all left you a message! Don't forget to listen to them when you're home!”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204111_From_OtherRole: “Even if it's not us, you have many trustworthy companions by your side, right?”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204096_From_OtherRole: “Kokona, you may have graduated, but you're still just a kid.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204104_From_OtherRole: “Kokona, did you forget why I dragged you kicking and screaming into this club?”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204115_From_OtherRole: “I'm working at the AI Institute now. This is exactly the kind of data we need to train our new models.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204107_From_OtherRole: “I couldn't stand it! What do you think you are? A genius? A hero? That's not it...”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204118_From_OtherRole: “This new Sea Bunny drone - 'Bunny Mark' is now yours! In all the battles you've been through together, you've given him a soul.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204116_From_OtherRole: “I've installed a new intelligent core in your bot, while Elise and your mentor have improved the design of the basic framework.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204105_From_OtherRole: “Even though you were always smiling and seemed to get along with everyone... I could tell you were hiding so many things in your heart.”
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204121_From_Role124001: “Bunny Mark”... is this your new name?
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102009_From_Role124: “Bunny Mark” still needs some finishing touches.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201057_From_Role124001: ...Eating this, it feels like I've seen the Milky Way.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202038_From_Role124001: ...I hope that means we lived up to everyone's expectations.

AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202022_From_Role124001: We would come up with strange gadgets without any clear purpose and talk about the new food stalls that opened up near the school.
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202114_From_Role124001: If collapse syndrome gets me one day... this little Sea Bunny is proof of my existence.

AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204089_Aside_AboutRole124001: (I turn on the power, and the machine buzzes, projecting a translucent holographic image in the air.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202065_Aside_AboutRole124001: (I glance around, looking for a comfortable hiding place.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201080_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Without a better excuse, Kokona finishes the salad as instructed.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203002_Aside_AboutRole124: (When I ring the doorbell, no one responds.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202075_Aside_AboutRole124001: (In line with previous experience, I look for blind spots by the trees hidden from the bot's line of view.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201002_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Kokona invited me to participate in a taste-testing.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102040_Aside_AboutRole124: (Equipped with a smart core, the control program continues to optimize itself at rapid speeds, gradually stabilizing the flight pattern of “Bunny Mark.”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203004_Aside_AboutRole124: (I knock on the door, only to find it slightly ajar.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102041_Aside_AboutRole124: (The newborn drone "Bunny Mark" seems to be curiously exploring the world all on its own.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102031_Aside_AboutRole124: (Time continues to pass in relative silence.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202001_Aside_AboutRole124001: (After finishing my shift at the Astral Sanctuary, I accepted Kokona’s invitation to hang out, though we were to meet somewhere other than a food stall for once.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203008_Aside_AboutRole124: (Everyone's been a little worried for Kokona as of late.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204133_Aside_AboutRole124001: (With how fast she's going, I'm a little worried she's going to trip over.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204017_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Kokona, with her extensive experience as a field medic, adds a variety of reliable arguments to Celestia's speech.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204075_Aside_AboutRole124001: (No words are needed right now. I just give Kokona a gentle push on the back.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203012_Aside_AboutRole124: (Every time I enter Kokona's dorm, I feel as if I've been transported to a warehouse.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201004_Aside_AboutRole124001: (I didn't expect there to be so many people.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201032_Aside_AboutRole124001: (I never expected the diligent Kokona to have this side to her.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202003_Aside_AboutRole124001: (I didn't expect there to be such a place so close to downtown.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202002_Aside_AboutRole124001: (The greenway built around the artificial river provides a refreshing refuge of nature away from the hustle and bustle of the city.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202060_Aside_AboutRole124001: (The bush kept me hidden for a while, but the bot found me in the end.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203007_Aside_AboutRole124: (After hesitating for a bit, I open the door.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201064_Aside_AboutRole124001: (It really does live up to the name of “Spacetime Bibimbap.”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201036_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Today is turning out to be more exciting than expected.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201039_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Today is turning out to be more arduous than expected...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102052_Aside_AboutRole124: (Looks like the story of Kokona and “Bunny Mark” has just begun.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203050_Aside_AboutRole124: (When the image of a young Kokona playing house with a doll came to mind, I couldn't help but chuckle.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102037_Aside_AboutRole124: (The lights outside the window seemed to shine with Kokona's smile.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102032_Aside_AboutRole124: (The daylight waned, the sun softly melting into the horizon, stretching the shadows into evening's embrace.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204124_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Standing outside the room, I cannot make out Kokona's expression clearly, but I see her shoulders twitching.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201033_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Wait a moment... did she just say “each and every stall?”)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201108_Aside_AboutRole124001: (It's finally time for the scoring session.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201130_Aside_AboutRole124001: (After a busy day, the taste testing comes to a satisfying end.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204134_Aside_AboutRole124001: (I send a message to Astierred. We're going to have to celebrate a job well done.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201084_Aside_AboutRole124001: (We continue browsing for a bit, but with our stomachs close to bursting, we decide to stop and rest.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204079_Aside_AboutRole124001: (On the room's table lies a strange-looking bot with rabbit ears, carrying marks from a repair job.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203013_Aside_AboutRole124: (I find Kokona sprawled out in the middle of the mess.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204048_Aside_AboutRole124001: (I have to resist the allure of the fried noodle stand and slowly guide Kokona back to the subject.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203009_Aside_AboutRole124: (Even if she never said it outright, Kokona seems a little down ever since she gave up her bot.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203023_Aside_AboutRole124: (Though I'm a little curious, I feel it would be wrong of me to pry further. I'll just move it a bit and clean the nearby dust.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202070_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Even though it was supposed to just be a test, Kokona seems pretty competitive about the whole thing.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102016_Aside_AboutRole124: (Isn't a toolbox filled with an entire set of screwdrivers right there?)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203100_Aside_AboutRole124: (Proofs, calculations, and corrections... one page after another.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204072_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Should I be surprised? Looks like she was on to us from the start. But now that we've come this far, I won't leave her a choice.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203098_Aside_AboutRole124: (She talks about leaving things behind, but the truth is, she still can't let go.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102039_Aside_AboutRole124: (Under Kokona's command, “Bunny Mark” takes flight, swaying from side to side.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201062_Aside_AboutRole124001: (The taste was mild at first, but as the ingredients melted in my mouth, an indescribable explosion of flavors danced across the tip of my tongue like the Big Bang.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203017_PlayerOption_ToRole124: (Might as well help her tidy up.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202085_Aside_AboutRole124001: (The thirty-second mark passes, but the bot is nowhere to be found.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201015_Aside_AboutRole124001: (As a PUS investigator, Kokona is probably here on a critical mission...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202068_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Ah! Too slow... the bot found me.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204126_Aside_AboutRole124001: (A minute, maybe two, passes. Kokona takes a deep breath and turns to the door.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203014_Aside_AboutRole124: (Her breathing is steady. Looks like she just fell asleep.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203089_Aside_AboutRole124: (In a corner of the room that remains uncleaned lies a trash can filled with crumpled-up pieces of paper.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204003_Aside_AboutRole124001: (The Institute has opened its doors to the general public and is holding a variety of academic exchanges.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204077_Aside_AboutRole124001: (Before us lies a makeshift activity room.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203005_Aside_AboutRole124: (Does that mean I can go in?)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204002_Aside_AboutRole124001: (The Wright Institute of Technology is holding an Open Day.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124202079_Aside_AboutRole124001: (This round will probably end like the others.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201117_Aside_AboutRole124001: (One should follow their heart and make a careful decision...)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124204049_Aside_AboutRole124001: (We find ourselves at the corner of one of the campus buildings. There aren't any activities scheduled here for today, so there's basically no foot traffic around.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102042_Aside_AboutRole124: (I can't help but feel a resemblance with the girl standing in front of me.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124201134_Aside_AboutRole124001: (At that time, I did not grasp the meaning behind Kokona's last words.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124203020_Aside_AboutRole124: (Components, tools, schematics... most of the stuff here seems related to robotics.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102020_Aside_AboutRole124: (Kokona takes the screwdriver without much comment, then immediately turns her attention back to her work.)
AVGEvent_KokonaShiki.Row124102007_Aside_AboutRole124: (Following Kokona's voice, I make my way behind the mountain of cardboard boxes.)

AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201041_From_OtherRole: April 15 (crossed out), April 16... Area 89 (crossed out), Area 88... bombs successfully played at the demolition site.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201043_From_OtherRole: April 16, Area 88 demolition, poor fortune: I was lost all morning. Turns out the objective wasn't in the video store? I bought one of Kanami's new records to try and turn things around.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201044_From_OtherRole: May 3, Windy Town assault, poor fortune: Why do frag grenades look so similar to healing mines? At least I have Kanami's record to keep me company. Hoping for my luck to change soon.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201046_From_OtherRole: June 16, Port Euler demolition, good fortune: The demolition mission and fan meetup happened to be right next to each other! Finally, some good luck... I didn't even get lost once!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201045_From_OtherRole: June 1, rescue mission, unclear fortune: I got lost again, so I went to Kanami's concert. Believe in that light, chase that light, and keep believing that things will turn around one day!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201047_From_OtherRole: ...This is the good luck my idol brings to me! (The last few words seem to be sparkling with gold dust.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101072_From_Role128: “Nosy and doesn't play by the rules,” “full of hidden strength,” and “one who has the power to deal with collapse syndrome all on their own.”
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101012_From_Role128: ...Though, I admit, most of it is purely rumor.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101009_From_Role128: ...So the storied Navigator has heard of me. I should be honored.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202016_From_Role128: ...Did you come here just for this?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204086_From_Role128001: ...I once made a pact with someone.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203069_From_OtherRole: ...Longing for the sun yet unable to gaze at it. Is that why she's dressed this way?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202051_From_Role128: ...The Astral Sanctuary? Isn't that the place that treats patients with collapse syndrome?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101065_From_Role128: ...This hobby or that, does it matter?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202079_From_Role128: ...The wound was treated very well. You have my thanks. I didn't expect you to be so good at first aid.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102006_From_OtherRole: ...Thank you, Navigator. I'll make sure to follow your instructions.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201033_PlayerOption_ToRole128: This work is too much for one person.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202015_From_Role128: It's just a flesh wound. No big deal.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204026_From_Role128001: The greatest characteristics of the dagger are its sharp edge and its ability to be hidden.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101006_From_Role128: No need to worry, I'm not armed. We're here to parley.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102042_PlayerOption_ToRole128: You're not the only disciple here.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203072_From_OtherRole: Is she ok? You said she was an ER patient, so it must be serious, right? Go on, then. Take her to the hospital!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202028_From_Role128: Still, they did end up getting in a few...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204023_From_Role128001: As a beginner, you have to be prepared for monotonous training.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202024_From_Role128: Indeed. They planned to use me to get rid of the guards, then turn on me while I was weak to take the crystals all for themselves.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102044_From_Role128: That won't do. I was the one who invited you, so allow me to serve the tea...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202084_From_Role128: For the sake of The Scissors, I have to do my best. A sharp blade that remains sheathed is of no use to anyone.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203080_From_Role128001: Don't apologize. Thanks to you, I've finally gotten rid of the investigators.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202018_From_Role128: I took a small risk in performing my duties, that's all.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201061_From_Role128: I was careless and neglected this part of our work. Sure enough, if the leader doesn't set an example, their subordinates won't know what to do.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102057_From_Role128: Perhaps it's just a coincidence, but... those orchids I planted have finally bloomed.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202020_From_Role128: So, I followed our source to the transport site to verify the truth of the report.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102046_PlayerOption_ToRole128: We've become mentors and friends to one another, and that's precisely why...
AVGEvent_Lawine.128102000_PrologueTitle: A Mentor as Well as a Friend
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204122_From_Role128001: I confess: I had other intentions when I asked to meet you. I have sparred with a lot of people in an attempt to calm my mind but to little avail.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202088_From_Role128: Thank you very much for your help today. If it wasn't for you, this mission might have been delayed.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202089_From_Role128: Today's meeting was rushed, and I could not host you properly. The next time we see each other, let's enjoy a cup of hot tea.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102028_From_Role128: I asked you here today so that we could finish our ceremony from last time.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202023_PlayerOption_ToRole128: They were also after the crystals?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202026_From_Role128: They best remember the feeling of my pulse blade on their skin.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201035_From_Role128: One must inspire others by taking the initiative.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101074_PlayerOption_ToRole128: These rumors are just exaggerations, Lawine. Don't be led astray by gossip...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101076_From_Role128: But, we wouldn't have asked you to be our “guest” if we didn't recognize your strength, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203086_From_Role128001: But in the end, she's exactly like them. A bunch of hypocrites.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202025_From_Role128: But I wasn't going to let them win that easily!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203018_From_Role128001: Now, P.U.S is bringing down the hammer. They've got investigators combing this place for signs of our activity.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204119_From_Role128001: But I won't be helpless facing her again. That's for sure.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102037_From_Role128: But, Navigator, please allow me this toast!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101023_From_Role128: We won't treat a “guest” with inhospitality.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204077_From_Role128001: As a beginner, you were able to parry my attacks with ease... What kind of tactics did you utilize?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204017_From_Role128001: I would like to teach it to you as a token of my appreciation.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203048_From_OtherRole: See the person in the photo? That's Lawine, the Executor of The Scissors.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201007_From_Role128: I suppose you got the request to meet. I wanted to talk a bit about how you've been doing, just like last time.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202055_From_Role128: Thank you for your kindness, but I can do it myself. I have more experience treating wounds.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202061_From_Role128: Could you bring me the active iodine?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203042_From_Role128001: Are you saying... they can help me avoid the investigators?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203037_From_Role128001: Get out of here. Don't worry about me - I'll find a way to escape.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202011_From_Role128: This thing? They're the spider plant seeds I ordered a few days ago.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102031_From_Role128: It's a tradition of my family dōjō. When passing on one's legacy to a disciple, it is customary for the disciple to hold a ceremony as a show of respect and gratitude. We can do this through tea.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202034_PlayerOption_ToRole128: Let me take a look at the wound, just to be safe.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201053_From_Role128: No need for that. I'll be revising these reports myself.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201055_From_Role128: We made quite a few mistakes in our last battle. The team ended up in a sticky situation and suffered injuries as a result.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201066_From_Role128: Swift as the wind and agile as thunder... this is the speed we need to defeat P.U.S.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201054_From_Role128: A report is not meant to be a diary. Clearly, they've gotten lost in the weeds.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202033_From_Role128: It's not much. The blood will clot soon enough.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101005_From_Role128: Pleasure to meet you, Navigator. I'm Lawine.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203025_From_OtherRole: Lawine... You're not getting away this time!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202019_From_Role128: I got a report that the PUS was making a secret shipment of purified crystals.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201060_From_Role128: This is not difficult work. As you can see, some people are just lazy.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203010_From_Role128001: It's you... but why are you dressed up like that?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203097_From_Role128001: You were going to pick up some goods, right? I'm happy to come with you if you don't mind.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202022_PlayerOption_ToRole128: They were trying to get you to take each other out!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101084_From_Role128: Looks like the tea's grown a little cold. Let me heat it up for you.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101035_From_Role128: Just a pot of fresh tea from my hometown.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202017_PlayerOption_ToRole128: With your skills, I didn't expect...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202014_PlayerOption_ToRole128: I heard you were injured. How are you holding up?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203053_From_OtherRole: Uh... What's wrong with your friend? Why is she all covered up?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203077_From_Role128001: (cough) The hat has a pungent smell.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102035_From_Role128: Only with this peace, can I truly face that person...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203078_PlayerOption_ToRole128001: Oh, sorry about that. It must've been unpleasant.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204073_From_Role128001: Tsk, I got distracted in practice...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203026_From_Role128001: Tsk. Looks like they caught on to my scent.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201068_From_Role128: Mmm... I should be able to go faster. There are more ways to save time than I expected.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204113_From_Role128001: How do I put this... Your tips probably helped.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201024_From_Role128: Mm. It's not a big deal.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202065_From_Role128: Hm. The wound is recovering nicely. As expected, there was only a small amount of bleeding.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204022_From_Role128001: Good. As long as you're interested.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202038_From_Role128: I do, but it's mostly for minor injuries.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203020_From_Role128001: Yeah. I've been staying behind to make sure everyone gets out.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102016_From_Role128: It's fine, I'll wait here. We should finish our last conversation in person.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204118_From_Role128001: Perhaps I do not yet know how to deal with things related to her...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201052_PlayerOption_ToRole128: Mm... what a wonderful collection of words. I'm taking my time to appreciate them carefully.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101075_From_Role128: That's true. Seeing is believing - rumors are never quite reliable.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202078_From_Role128: Looks like the bleeding has stopped.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201031_From_Role128: A team surely works faster than a single person, but...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102036_From_Role128: Arranging a tea ceremony today may have been a bit presumptuous...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204027_From_Role128001: Before attacking, a warrior does not reveal to the enemy the position of their dagger.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101022_From_Role128: If you find something lacking, just say so.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101283_From_Role128: It's been a while since you arrived. I'm sure you want to stretch your legs.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204028_From_Role128001: Enough talk. Let's practice with the real thing, beginning with how to hold the dagger.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204094_From_Role128001: She's become the way she is... because of my weakness. Because I couldn't stop P.U.S; because I could not prevent her from betraying us...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203049_From_OtherRole: She is our most wanted fugitive. Evidence suggests that she is active in this area. If you see or hear anything about her, please inform me immediately.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102023_From_Role128: Good to see you again, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201004_From_Role128: If it's not urgent, come back later.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201028_From_Role128: If we found them out any later, there would be even more work to do.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102056_From_Role128: Mother often said that if you plant a seed with your heart's desire, you will sow a different fate.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203096_From_Role128001: Don't you have things to take care of?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201049_From_Role128: Navigator, a few reports that need to be revised are missing. Have you seen them?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204133_From_Role128001: I have important things to tell you...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204029_From_Role128001: For a beginner like yourself, I recommend a forward grip. Like this...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204021_PlayerOption_ToRole128001: Show interest in learning martial arts.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101040_From_Role128: I respect your vigilance in the face of the unknown.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101053_From_Role128: Indeed. It's a hobby of mine.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203091_From_Role128001: Yes, she was my partner back at PUS.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204124_From_Role128001: While I taught you martial arts, in a way, you have...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204117_PlayerOption_ToRole128001: I hope you'll stop being affected by past events.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101017_From_Role128: Not used to it, are you?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101059_From_Role128: They'll be flowering a bit later.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101069_From_Role128: You're not too different from the rumors, Navigator.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102058_From_Role128: Fate is a wonderful thing, Navigator... not to say that you aren't incredible in your own right.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204020_From_Role128001: Of course, I have high expectations of you.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204034_From_Role128001: I'll go easy on you. No one has to get hurt.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204088_From_Role128001: Although, I'm probably the only one who still remembers the pact.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101070_PlayerOption_ToRole128: I'd be curious to know what the rumors say about me.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101064_From_Role128: Does it surprise you? Why the interest, Navigator?
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204083_From_Role128001: To be as still as water, as immovable as a mountain. You managed to achieve this as a mere beginner... I still have a long way to go...
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204114_From_Role128001: Thinking of the special tactics you told me about, my body seemingly moved on its own, and the dagger felt incredibly light.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204127_PlayerOption_ToRole128001: Go on, then. They need you.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203024_From_OtherRole: This is where we lost her. Search the place, and don't let anyone suspicious escape.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102047_PlayerOption_ToRole128: We can sit here and enjoy this tea together!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203022_From_OtherRole: I think I just heard “her” voice!
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203016_From_Role128001: I just finished a combat operation.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101013_From_Role128: I've heard that you're proficient at treating collapse syndrome and that you played a pivotal role in the Grove Bank Incident.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204011_From_Role128001: My family runs a dojo. We are accustomed to expressing our intentions and thoughts through martial arts. Therefore, I've prepared a gift in my own way.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201025_From_Role128: I took part in many of these battles. Based on memory and record, I should be able to get through most of this soon enough.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102054_From_Role128: I once believed that constant and silent struggle was my ultimate calling.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204084_From_Role128001: I have trained far from enough... I still lack strength.
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204116_PlayerOption_ToRole128001: The Lawine I know is a formidable opponent.

AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202047_Aside_AboutRole128: (Lawine holds back her pain as she struggles to untie the blood-stained bandage.)

AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204237_Aside_AboutRole128001: (After a brief exchange, Lawine swings her dagger.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202073_Aside_AboutRole128: (Looking over, I confirm that there's no pus, only a little blood.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203306_Aside_AboutRole128001: (I hear sudden, hurried footsteps approaching from behind...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204044_Aside_AboutRole128001: (My sudden move puts Lawine on high alert.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102011_Aside_AboutRole128: (I wait and wait... but hear no response.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204065_Aside_AboutRole128001: (I wait for Lawine to make her next move...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201072_Aside_AboutRole128: (The mountain of papers disappears, as if cut through by an invisible blade.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204276_Aside_AboutRole128001: (In the end, she gives up, with great reluctance in her speech.)

AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203051_PlayerOption_ToRole128001: (I shrug my shoulders, indicating that I don't know anything about this person.)

AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203075_Aside_AboutRole128001: (The investigators in their blue and white uniforms leave us.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202058_Aside_AboutRole128: (Lawine shoots me a look out of the corner of her eye. This must be her way of asking for help...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203043_Aside_AboutRole128001: (Filled with disbelief, Lawine lets me put the disguise on her.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204007_Aside_AboutRole128001: (Although dressed in her combat suit, Lawine does not appear to be on alert.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204098_Aside_AboutRole128001: (I have seen firsthand Lawine's down-to-earth attitude as a leader and her decisive, swift actions as an executor.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202027_Aside_AboutRole128: (Lawine's glare was as sharp as a blade)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128101024_Aside_AboutRole128: (As we speak, steam starts escaping from the kettle on Lawine's table.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128201002_Aside_AboutRole128: (I give the door a few cautious knocks.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204102_Aside_AboutRole128001: (She seems slightly confused at the beginning, but as our eyes lock...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203044_Aside_AboutRole128001: (The oversized sunglasses cover half of Lawine's face while the large hat hides her long azure hair.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203015_Aside_AboutRole128001: (I follow Lawine into a secluded corner.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204031_Aside_AboutRole128001: (Following Lawine's instruction, I change the way I hold the dagger, no longer looking like a common thug...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203406_Aside_AboutRole128001: (I turn around and see a familiar person.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102003_Aside_AboutRole128: (We've admitted so many patients as of late that everyone's on constant overtime, but I don't want to disappoint Lawine by not showing up...)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202069_Aside_AboutRole128: (I push forward to untie Lawine's bandage on my own.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203047_Aside_AboutRole128001: (Standing close to Lawine, I can hear her breathing as she can hear mine. Both of us are equally nervous.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204107_Aside_AboutRole128001: (No longer confused, she swings her dagger with great precision, as if dancing in the wind.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128204069_Aside_AboutRole128001: (She spins her dagger before sheathing it as if she's lost the will to attack.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128202042_Aside_AboutRole128: (It's fully stocked with a variety of common medical supplies, along with a bunch of rubbing alcohol and bandages.)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128102012_Aside_AboutRole128: (Eh...? I check the patient list to make sure... that was the last one!)
AVGEvent_Lawine.Row128203059_Aside_AboutRole128001: (Hearing a bizarre and twisted story about the pair, the investigators present are all moved to tears.)

AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202042_PlayerOption_ToRole101: Who is this hero you speak of?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202020_Aside_AboutRole101: (A P.U.S investigator on patrol walks over angrily, glaring at us with disdain.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204013_Aside_AboutRole101: (The usually energetic girl sounds exhausted. It's a scene I've seen before, like a cat avoiding my gaze.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203018_Aside_AboutRole101: (A sudden blaring alarm rings from Michele's portable communicator.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102002_Aside_AboutRole101: (With no work planned, Michele unexpectedly invites me out for a secret rendezvous.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201142_Aside_AboutRole101: (As if struck by a heavy blow, her head droops in disappointment and dejection.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202001_Aside_AboutRole101: (It's a day off at Grand Beach.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201242_Aside_AboutRole101: (But in the very next moment, a fire of determination reignites in her blue eyes.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203069_Aside_AboutRole101: (But now, she glows like a triumphant hero.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102009_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele leads me by the hand into a cozy café filled with the lazy ambiance of lounging cats.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204038_Aside_AboutRole101: (The letter reads, "To the brave and charming Cat Investigator, this commemorative trophy is from all the players. It is our pleasure to bestow this honor upon you, whose courage and perseverance echo the heroes in our games.")
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204339_Aside_AboutRole101: (Many names are signed at the bottom of the letter, followed by a note: “Included are the Mighty Meow Arcade co-branded cat paw cookies. If you like the cookies, don't forget to preorder more.”)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201043_Aside_AboutRole101: (Taking on the first level again, Michele and I are totally in sync with our strategies.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203057_Aside_AboutRole101: (Charging into the scene, Michele stringifies the shield, using it to block the gushing erosion flow. Her stance is like a beacon of hope illuminating the darkness.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102013_Aside_AboutRole101: (Several playful cats approach uninvited, frolicking around Michele.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204101_Aside_AboutRole101: (It's another day off, and Michele has invited me over to her apartment.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204045_Aside_AboutRole101: (Meanwhile, I've set up the new game and grabbed the controller, ready to dive in, but Michele stands there, lost in thought, gazing at her precious "trophies.")
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201017_Aside_AboutRole101: (As I reach for the console, something familiar catches my eye on the table beside the sofa.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203067_Aside_AboutRole101: (Amidst everyone's gaze, Michele emerges slowly from the thick smoke. Her face is covered in ash, but beneath the grime, her smile shines as bright as ever.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102049_Aside_AboutRole101: (Surrounded by cats, we stayed together at the café until late in the evening.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202039_Aside_AboutRole101: (A disheartened Michele pulls out a gleaming badge bearing the P.U.S insignia with a sword of justice cutting across it—a testament to the bravery and resolve of every P.U.S Investigator that came before her.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203049_Aside_AboutRole101: (She lifts her gaze, locking eyes with me, her crystal blue eyes sharpened with resolve.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202037_Aside_AboutRole101: (The man doesn’t dial down his sarcastic tone one bit. Suddenly, someone calls out for him in the distance, and he cheerfully runs off.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102008_From_Role101: (Whispering) You're the only person I've ever brought to this place. So keep it a secret, okay?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204043_From_Role101: (Whispering) Maybe I can become a hero like my dad... If so, his legacy will live on, right?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102041_Aside_AboutRole101: (Her clear eyes are filled with warmth as she looks at me earnestly.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204026_Aside_AboutRole101: (Just as she's muttering her worries, there's a sudden, sharp knock at the door.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202010_Aside_AboutRole101: (The girl, usually as playful as a kitty, seems to have lost all her energy. She deliberately avoids making eye contact, not wanting to share her feelings with me.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201002_Aside_AboutRole101: (As invited, I head to Michele's place at P.U.S. Apartment One in Elmond. The moment I open the door, an unexpected sight greets me...)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202028_Aside_AboutRole101: (I'm beyond angry, but Michele grabs my hand, staying calm. Is this kind of gossip something she deals with often?)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204001_Aside_AboutRole101: (Through the door, I can hear her humming the theme song from the No.1 series. It's an upbeat tune, but her voice carries a hint of gloominess.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203060_Aside_AboutRole101: (Her petite frame, wielding the shield, stands firm against the blue-purple torrent, like a hero facing down a dragon's flames.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102001_Aside_AboutRole101: (A few days later, the sun's shining bright over the commercial hub.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204034_From_Role101: Whew—let me catch my breath for a second... Okay, I’m ready to open the door!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201001_Aside_AboutRole101: (One day, Investigator Michele schedules a briefing session with me right after returning from a mission.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102033_Aside_AboutRole101: (The fluffy, round furballs snuggle up to us, weaving in and out between us, meowing for pats and hugs.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203004_Aside_AboutRole101: (As always, Michele is full of enthusiasm, as if it’s just another typical gaming session. But anyone can sense the underlying reluctance and sadness in her tone.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202038_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele and I sit by the edge of the beach, silently facing each other as the sound of the waves ebb and flow around us.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204044_Aside_AboutRole101: (Muttering to herself, Michele places the trophy next to the sword and shield models. The three items act as her achievement trophies, shining brightly under the sunlight.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204037_Aside_AboutRole101: (Holding her breath, Michele carefully unwraps the package, revealing a game trophy filled with cat paw cookies. Alongside it is a thank you letter.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203053_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele vanishes before my eyes, rushing to the arcade entrance.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201044_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele lures the dragon into a hidden trap, and I seize the opportunity to unleash our ultimate combo move.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203001_Aside_AboutRole101: (The day of our meeting arrives at the bustling commercial hub.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203062_Aside_AboutRole101: (Though still terrified, the people trapped inside start moving with Michele's encouragement. As they pour out of the arcade, Michele is nowhere to be seen.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203063_Aside_AboutRole101: (The blue-purple torrent had seemingly swallowed the brave little hero. Everyone feared that the light of hope had been extinguished—)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203043_Aside_AboutRole101: (The blue-purple liquid keeps spilling out. Even standing outside the arcade, the gravity of the situation is worsening by the minute.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203059_Aside_AboutRole101: (Even from a distance, Michele's courageous voice rings out loud and clear.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201006_Aside_AboutRole101: (The two robot cats seem utterly exhausted, slumping beside the charging station, sound asleep. Yet Michele shows no sign of fatigue as if her energy has been completely restored the moment she steps back into the pure world of video games.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201016_Aside_AboutRole101: (It's hard to refuse the invitation of a super gamer girl, especially with stars practically twinkling in her eyes.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102050_Aside_AboutRole101: (After spending an entire day, Michele doesn't seem tired at all.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102014_Aside_AboutRole101: (It seems she's familiar with each of these cats. Surrounded by a flurry of fur, Michele drops her act of mystery and wit.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203051_Aside_AboutRole101: (Determination ignites in those adorable eyes, sparking with fierce will.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201018_Aside_AboutRole101: (It is a shining model of a giant sword, crafted with incredible detail, reminiscent of the "Sword of Light" used by Mighty Meow, the protagonist of Superheroes of Justice.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203068_Aside_AboutRole101: (Her cute casual outfit looks a bit tattered, adding a touch of scrappiness to her appearance.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203064_Aside_AboutRole101: (But then, Michele reappears out of nowhere!)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202053_Aside_AboutRole101: (Bathed in golden sunlight, her ocean-blue eyes shimmer with determination as the waves crash behind her.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203055_Aside_AboutRole101: (With a series of clattering sounds, she dismantles the promotional prop shield at the entrance.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201045_Aside_AboutRole101: (In an instant, a dazzling golden light bursts forth from the sword and shield, slicing the mighty dragon in half.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204036_Aside_AboutRole101: (Mustering her courage, Michele flings the door open. Behind it lies not only the new disc of "Superheroes of Justice," but also a mysterious package.)

AVGEvent_Season3.Row240102107_Aside_AboutRole146001: (A clap of thunder suddenly echoes outside.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240102060_Aside_AboutRole146001: (...The carefully maintained smile fading from her face.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240103062_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The woman who has suddenly appeared puts Celestia on high alert.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240105068_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The cards transform into several clones of The Great Artist.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108207_Aside_AboutRole146001: (After a prolonged moment, I feel puzzled by this sudden thought.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240109004_Aside_AboutRole146001: (After the battle with New Bethlehem, Astral Sanctuary has resumed usual operations.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107046_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The crimson lightning circles Audrey, swiftly maneuvering between covers, leaving the trail of bullets shot by Audrey far behind.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107177_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Fuchsia puts Celestia and me down as if carrying us all this way has been a piece of cake.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107180_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Seemingly displeased with my remark, Fuchsia throws me off. Luckily, I manage to land on my feet.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107026_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Fuchsia takes out a tactical mask and puts it on without any hesitation.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108060_Aside_AboutRole146001: (With her sharp senses, Fuchsia almost catches the trajectory of the bullet...)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108055_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Fuchsia sprints toward Julian as she has no time to dodge...)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108120_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Fuchsia once again bursts with power, dashing toward the two like a fleeting arrow.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108124_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Someone firmly grasps the muzzle of Fuchsia's gun, causing her to miss.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107032_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Every vein, nerve, and pore in her body expands, enhancing her sensory perception and reaction speed to the limit.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107038_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Her muscles tense, she stomps the ground with full force and shoots out like a bolt of lightning.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240103061_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Beautiful, elegant... and a barely perceptible hint of danger.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101078_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The reason for which lies in the center of the room.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108210_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Audrey slowly opens her eyes, within which lies a clear will.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240109046_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Audrey smiles as she watches Astierred and me before turning her gaze back at the window.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108148_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Audrey is sitting in the cage alone.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240106013_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The person who has invited her here is none other than the mastermind behind the attack.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107166_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As a sudden gust of wind blows right next to me, the scene in front of me rapidly retracts.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240103042_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The illusion in my mind dissipates as if it never existed to begin with.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108278_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The footsteps are receding. New Bethlehem must have seized the opportunity to retreat.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108266_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The arrival of Flavia and the Sentinel Bureau squad tips the balance.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108252_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Descending from the roof, Flavia gracefully lands atop a stacked shipping container along with the moonlight shining through the skylight.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240105061_Aside_AboutRole146001: (For an instant, Flavia hesitates as she ponders what The Great Artist has said.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240104066_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Although the content of the conversation remains unclear to me, I notice that the captain seems to become more and more nervous.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108115_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Although it is not as exactly as the intel suggested, Fuchsia has anticipated Celestia's help. She seizes the opportunity and fires everything she has at the enemy.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240109033_Aside_AboutRole146001: (While memories of the event still linger in my mind... there are too many questions that cannot be explained by logic. The experience cannot serve as a reference for her treatment...)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240109031_Aside_AboutRole146001: (While memories of the event still linger in my mind... I did say a lot of embarrassing things. I should keep it a secret for now.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101137_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Although it is just a game, it was much more tiring than I expected. Afterward, I feel like my body is falling apart.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108012_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The spiders land around Audrey and work under Giuliano's command, weaving a web that binds Audrey.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108150_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The stairs creak as I walk on them as if they might break at any moment.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240105031_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Her smooth moves are completed in an instant at a speed almost imperceptible to the naked eye.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107019_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Unable to resist Audrey's fierce attacks, Fuchsia takes refuge in the shadows of shipping containers.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108127_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The Astral Gate teleported more than just Celestia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107131_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The girl Celestia defeated - Have I met her before?)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107053_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Enraged by Fuchsia's actions, Audrey stops firing her machine gun and raises the grenade launcher in her left hand.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108132_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Bound by the spider web, Audrey lies right in front of me.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107173_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The mysterious girl has run for who knows how long while carrying us, finally stopping at a location far from the port.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240106020_From_OtherRole: (Otherwise, I wouldn't have accepted this job...)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240103098_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The interview goes a lot more smoothly than expected. Flavia is easier to get along with than she appears to be.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101133_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As much as I am trying my best, my body cannot keep up with the notes falling like a waterfall.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108175_Aside_AboutRole146001: (My feeble body hits the steel cage, producing a dull thud.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107222_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Now is the time to come up with a plan...)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107110_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The side effect of overloaded combat hits Fuchsia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101003_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The grand conference room fills with chattering.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101114_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The screen displays a long list of tracks.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101081_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Astonishing combo numbers keep popping up on the scoreboard of the arcade machine.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108258_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Out of his instinct as a sniper, Julian pushes Rafa aside as the bullet misses her head by inches.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108057_FromTalkert_Role112001: (Almost there! Not close enough! Not accurate enough!)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108234_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Did she single-handedly turn the tide of the battle?)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240105076_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The clones are intricately designed, indistinguishable even to someone as keen as Flavia.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108083_Aside_AboutRole146001: (In the corner of an image, I notice that Fuchsia's clothes are stained with the corrosive liquid shot by Rafa.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240102087_Aside_AboutRole146001: (This is the only connection Audrey has with her past self.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108219_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Such a phenomenon has never been observed on any of Astral Sanctuary's patients.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240106011_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The structure and the arrangement of items are almost identical to Grove Bank's vault.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240104075_Aside_AboutRole146001: (It is better to cooperate for now...)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101134_PlayerOption_ToRole146001: (Give up on the most difficult notes and try to hit the rest)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107159_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Through the gaps in the water, I notice that Audrey's clouded gaze regains clarity in an instant.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108084_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The liquid neutralizes Celestia's ability, rendering it useless.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108139_Aside_AboutRole146001: (A paperback diary, a rarity in the modern world.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108267_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Having recovered their strength, Astierred and Fuchsia move closer to Audrey and me amidst the gunfire.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240103047_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As I snap back to reality, I feel an unfamiliar weight on my wrist.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107077_Aside_AboutRole146001: (A sharp blade lies between Fuchsia's gun and Audrey's heart, splitting the bullet in two.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107161_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The water curtain comes pouring down, turning into a flood of destruction.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240106146_Aside_AboutRole146001: (With the onset of collapse syndrome, the string sequences that record the very existence of Audrey rapidly disintegrate like a dying star collapsing on itself.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101076_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As the door is opened, a blast of loud music pierces my eardrums.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107158_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As Rafa speaks, the massive tank explodes thunderously. The unknown liquid within gushes out, forming a huge water curtain under Rafa's control.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240103004_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As the aftermath of the Neutroville explosions settles, there are no more new patients for Astral Sanctuary to admit.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101130_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As the track song hits its climax, the difficulty of the game significantly increases.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107027_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The atomizer sprays crystalline powder that enters Fuchsia's nostrils as she breathes, entering her bloodstream.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101122_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As the music starts, notes begin to drop from the top of the screen.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240101136_Aside_AboutRole146001: (As the song comes to an end, a terrible score pops up on the screen - probably less than one-tenth of Bai Mo's.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108011_Aside_AboutRole146001: (The dark-haired young man approaches Audrey, who is passed out on the floor, and flicks his wrist, releasing multiple spider droids.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240107050_Aside_AboutRole146001: (In her hand, the Sawtooth is like an accurate and agile hunting knife, continuously firing bullets through gaps in covers toward Audrey's blind spots.)
AVGEvent_Season3.Row240108056_Aside_AboutRole146001: (Wielding the flame-spitting Sawtooth, Fuchsia attempts to take down Giuliano before he can pull the trigger.)

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204005_From_OtherRole: “People of different races and faiths live together in peace, building a brave new world.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204004_From_OtherRole: “As the devastating war comes to an end, peace returns to this world.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204006_From_OtherRole: "In such a world, every life is respected, and brutal acts and terror are outlawed. War and aggression are things of the past.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204007_From_OtherRole: “A world where all citizens of Earth are friends with one another.”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204035_From_OtherRole: “We must take the One Ring to the Land of Bliss!”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204039_From_OtherRole: “She has undergone a mask transformation. She is no longer human!”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201034_From_Role146: You'll be fine. There's still time, you have to trust me...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203057_From_Role146: Oh, Mr. Luna! You're looking much better today. Please send my regards to Sunny.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201033_From_Role146: Mm-hmm, I can help you... Yes, I'm a healer...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101003_From_Role146: The stargazing event is happening tonight! I've got everything prepared. Just make sure to show up, okay?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203058_From_Role146: Mrs. Anna Pavlovna, how are you feeling today? About you and your children...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203056_From_Role146: Hello, Mrs. Gima and Mrs. Estina. You two are inseparable, as always.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202089_From_Role146: Be it the moon, stars, or sun, all celestial bodies are part of this vast universe.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101029_From_OtherRole: A fireworks display will take place tomorrow. We're expecting a lot of tourists. Don't occupy this spot for too long.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201032_From_Role146: Please don't be afraid. My name is Celestia. I work at Astral Sanctuary.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202073_From_Role146: The Moon isn't visible at this time. But we should still be able to see the stars...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202008_From_OtherRole: “Hey, Celestia! The rental on your storage locker in P.U.S is about to expire. I'm sending some of your old stuff to Astral Sanctuary. I hope they can help you relax! Although I have no idea how to use any of them...”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202009_From_OtherRole: "Even if work gets hectic, make sure to take care of yourself—I worry about you!"
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202010_From_OtherRole: "I'll visit you once I'm free! See you soon~"
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202058_From_Role146: “Sorry! I got the boxes mixed up and accidentally opened yours. I promise that I didn't take anything...”
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201070_From_Role146: ...If your singing is this bad, why did you volunteer to sing?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204063_From_Role146: ...The final wish, it never came true...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101026_From_Role146: ...Navigator? A-Are you okay? Why are you staring at the map?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203033_From_Role146: ...But now, I no longer follow her blindly like a child.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204091_From_Role146: ...That it may only emit such a faint glow?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101035_From_Role146: ...But I've only got electric sparklers. They are far from everyone's expectations...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201075_From_OtherRole: ...Ah. You—you found it? You really found it for me...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201056_From_Role146: ...In any case, we can't just leave the patient here. We need to get him back to Astral Sanctuary...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201054_From_Role146: ...What happened to the left side of the screen?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101010_From_Role146: ...Are you saying I look a bit down?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202082_From_Role146: ...I don't have the talent or ability to become that shining star. I knew that, even back then.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101017_From_Role146: ...If only we had a weather controller or something.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204079_PlayerOption_ToRole146: ...By the way, what's this thing poking me all this time?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203088_From_Role146: I’m certain you’ve left a professional impression.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203085_From_Role146: You must have left quite the lasting impression.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146029_From_Role146: You worked very hard to surprise me. It must have taken you an entire day!
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202095_From_Role146: Knowing there's someone like you who understands me, right by my side...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203076_From_Role146: As different celestial bodies are born, they influence one another, forming the universe as we know it...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146010_From_Role146: I don't know why, but everyone I met today has been... too generous? I've received so many gifts that my bags are overflowing.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204021_From_Role146: What kind of movies do you like? I'm curious~
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201003_From_OtherRole: It's gone. I can't find it anywhere...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203013_From_Role146: But what should the theme of this event be?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203041_From_Role146: Wearing something from my childhood might bring back different feelings?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204089_PlayerOption_ToRole146: Perhaps Astral Sanctuary is just like the sparkler.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146018_From_OtherRole: Today is a special day! You should enjoy it!
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203015_From_Role146: Creating a close-knit community centered on the Sanctuary? That's a mature perspective.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204074_From_Role146: But if nothing changes, future generations will face the same sufferings, won’t they?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201095_From_Role146: You handled it brilliantly. I can't praise you enough.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204092_PlayerOption_ToRole146: But even a faint glow can illuminate many eyes.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203006_From_Role146: But emotional manifestations are, in fact, the external expressions of internal changes...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202083_From_Role146: But mother didn't care about any of that. All she hoped was for me to take over her position and status at P.U.S.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146033_PlayerOption_ToRole146: How did you figure it all out!?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201076_From_OtherRole: You're the first person to be so kind to me...

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202038_From_Role146: I suddenly felt dizzy when I turned around just now...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201044_From_Role146: So, you enjoy music too? That's another thing we have in common.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201093_From_Role146: If you don't mind, you can use mine instead. It's old too, but it still works...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204083_From_Role146: Would you like to light it up? Just flip the switch at the bottom.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201081_From_Role146: His mental state has finally stabilized.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202030_From_Role146: You’re... Oh, you’re helping with the patients?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203061_From_Role146: I think we've got enough people here, Navigator. Shall we?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204073_From_Role146: Even if my efforts prove futile, and I can’t fulfill the hopes of those before us, I won’t be discouraged.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204043_From_Role146: The audience seems satisfied, Navigator. Movies truly are enchanting.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203026_From_Role146: What did you pick up...? Oh, this bracelet...?

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204028_From_Role146: I need to guide everyone to their seats.

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101045_From_Role146: There are a lot of people here, Navigator...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201038_From_Role146: I know this is a bit out of the blue, but are you familiar with a lot of songs?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201009_From_Role146: Please keep the patient calm and make sure he doesn’t wander off—I'm counting on you!
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202047_From_Role146: I'll leave it to you for a bit while I clear my head.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202054_From_Role146: Is something wrong? You look worried.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202059_PlayerOption_ToRole146: So it was just a mix-up...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203036_From_Role146: I see... Your intuition is usually right, far better than mine.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101051_From_Role146: It seems that while I was feeling down, you had already found a more radiant 'star' for me.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201082_From_Role146: It turns out he once had a loved one who stayed by his side. But that person contracted Collapse Syndrome before he did and eventually went missing...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203021_From_Role146: But I’m not sure what we should give...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203009_From_Role146: Only with timely intervention can our treatment offer the greatest benefits to the patients.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201084_From_Role146: Only by humming this song could he slightly remember her face...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202097_From_Role146: The more I think about it, the more motivated I am.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201049_PlayerOption_ToRole146: We could play the song from my Star Pad.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203073_From_Role146: But without each of you, the city, the world—none of it could exist.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201062_From_Role146: B-But, I never did well in music class back in school...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204068_From_Role146: It never happened... We reached this "new world," but it didn’t come true...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201048_From_Role146: But I don't really know much about current music trends, so I'm at a bit of a loss... Do you have any ideas?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101032_From_Role146: But Grand Beach is not far from here. The weather probably won't be different...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201085_From_Role146: But now, even the melody have slipped away from him, leaving just the song's name...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201083_From_Role146: As Collapse Syndrome started affecting him, he began to forget everything related to that loved one.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202029_From_Role146: Phew... Eh? What time is it...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201096_From_Role146: Surely, I'll learn a lot from you as we work together. I'm looking forward to that, Navigator!
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201059_From_Role146: Oh? What do you have in mind?

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204081_From_Role146: Oh, it’s the electronic sparkler reserved to mark your seat.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202086_From_Role146: Mm-hmm. When I asked to forge my own path, my mother allowed me to leave, though she never really acknowledged my dreams.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203042_From_Role146: Alright. I guess it doesn't hurt to try...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146019_PlayerOption_ToRole146: Yeah, you should accept it. It's Nana's wish.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203060_From_Role146: Yep. I have always insisted on remembering everyone by their name.

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204020_From_Role146: Nice. I told everyone they could bring their favorite movies for the festival.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201030_From_Role146: I see. The patient's condition seems quite severe. I need to perform an emergency intervention.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204045_From_Role146: It's no big deal. Although it was busy today, watching movies gave me some rest.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204070_From_Role146: I know that. It wasn’t just because of the movie, but...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201091_From_Role146: There's no need to repair it. It's an ancient item from my time at P.U.S anyway.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204065_From_Role146: Mm-hmm, the wish of the survivors.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201088_From_Role146: Heh... Don't worry. I wasn't going to blame you.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202079_From_Role146: She had hoped that I would become a star more dazzling than anyone else.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203069_From_Role146: We want everyone to understand that they are not alone. At Astral Sanctuary, we are all connected just like these crystals...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146005_From_OtherRole: Because you're always so nice to us! Remember when you took care of me when I was sick?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204088_From_Role146: Since it's a toy that simulates fireworks, its brightness is low and its duration short...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201023_PlayerOption_ToRole146: Just hit a little bump on the road of life.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203018_From_Role146: Before you joined the Sanctuary, building that trust was something I struggled with...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202090_From_Role146: In the endless darkness, each one of them emits its unique light.
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203072_From_Role146: We may not know one another in this city. You might feel like just an atom, a speck of stardust...
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101031_From_Role146: Th-the sea? Are you suggesting we move the event to the beach?

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202034_Aside_AboutRole146: (Holding her forehead, Celestia suddenly sways, her body tilting, nearly falling down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204030_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia rushes off before finishing her sentence. I find our reserved seats and sit down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201028_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia's palm is sweaty—she must've rushed over right after I called.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201036_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia's emergency intervention worked, and the patient has gradually calmed down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101047_Aside_AboutRole146: (Before Celestia finishes her sentence,  a "boom" startles her.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203029_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia shows me one of the bracelet's crystals, its backside engraved with her name in a child's handwriting.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201040_Aside_AboutRole146: (As Celestia tells me the name of the song, the patient lifts up his head, his eyes filled with longing.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202072_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia gently takes the telescope from my hand and starts adjusting it.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101038_Aside_AboutRole146: (I give Celestia a look filled with determination.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101044_Aside_AboutRole146: (Arriving at the beach, we find a large crowd.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203055_Aside_AboutRole146: (Patients from diverse backgrounds, ages, and statuses are here. Celestia greets each of them proficiently.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202002_Aside_AboutRole146: (Upon arriving at Astral Sanctuary for work, I hear someone—no, something—calling for Celestia at the entrance.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204085_Aside_AboutRole146: (As instructed by Celestia, I “light” the sparkler.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204003_Aside_AboutRole146: (Cheers, shouts, and clamors accompany the roar of war machines, echoing in Celestia's and my ears.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201074_Aside_AboutRole146: (The singing is neither moving nor unpleasant. Average at best.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201066_Aside_AboutRole146: (Her singing is neither moving nor unpleasant. Average at best.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202026_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia is taking a nap, looking more exhausted than usual.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201153_Aside_AboutRole146: (After tapping the Star Pad, only the right side of the screen lit up.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201065_Aside_AboutRole146: (I used the half-broken Star Pad to look up the lyrics and guided Celestia as she sang to the patient.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204086_Aside_AboutRole146: (The sparkler's white light illuminates our faces as our eyes lock.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204055_Aside_AboutRole146: (The opening scene shows columns of tanks advancing under a purple sunset, gunfire tearing through the quiet night.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101028_Aside_AboutRole146: (I glance over Celestia’s shoulder at the computer displaying a map of the area around Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202012_Aside_AboutRole146: (After seeing the bot off, I carry the package into Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202050_Aside_AboutRole146: (Seeing Celestia recover her strength, I start my own work, feeling relieved.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202103_Aside_AboutRole146: (Seeing Celestia’s joy as she adjusts the telescope puts my mind at ease.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202005_Aside_AboutRole146: (After confirming that the packaging is intact, I accept the package from the delivery robot.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201002_Aside_AboutRole146: (On my first day commuting to Astral Sanctuary, I suddenly got caught up with someone sitting dejectedly by the plaza fountain.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101018_Aside_AboutRole146: (Seeing Celestia this defeated for the first time, I have no clue how to comfort her.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101004_Aside_AboutRole146: (A brief message that radiates Celestia's carefree excitement, with a hint of playfulness.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101041_Aside_AboutRole146: (We urgently contact the participants and leave a notice of the change of venue on the electronic noticeboard at Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204018_Aside_AboutRole146: (Even though they’re quite old, they still function well enough to show clear images in daylight.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202048_Aside_AboutRole146: (After calming Celestia down, I continue to receive visitors.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101002_Aside_AboutRole146: (It's been a week since the movie festival, I receive a text message from Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204008_Aside_AboutRole146: (In the setting sun, soldiers lay down their weapons and children return to their homes.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201073_Aside_AboutRole146: (I went ahead and sang the song to the patient.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101042_Aside_AboutRole146: (Holding hands, Celestia and I rush to Grand Beach.)

AVGEvent_Yvette.Row131201116_Aside_AboutRole131: (Watching the badge on Yvette's wrist, the color gradually changes from a tense red to a vibrant bright yellow, finally settling on a radiant yellow smiley face.)
