BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row19_PlayerOption1: An event ticket with a butterfly symbol?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId115: To keep you safe, you must follow my instructions precisely.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId115: From now on, information won't come freely.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Take a close look at the bottom of the mug...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId115: We'll talk more about it in person.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Sit in the second to last seat by the window.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId115: If you can beat me in a game...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row8_PlayerOption1: I'm here... this must be Café Reminiscence.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId115: I've intercepted some intel; seems that someone has their eye on you, Navigator.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId115: I might just share some secrets.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Can we meet in private? There's something I need to talk to you about...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId115: See the butterflies outside? Follow them.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Unfortunately, the person tailing you showed up there too.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Hold on. A waiter will bring you coffee soon.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row19_PlayerOption2: Does this have anything to do with the person after me?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row14_PlayerOption2: Let's try one of their signature drinks.

BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId133: ...After leaving the café, you showed three major signs of fatigue and five instances of scattered attention.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId133: It isn't foresight; it's deduction—a skill I've honed.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Then, with your orders of espresso con panna and mocha, you kept winning.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row30_TextContent_FromRoleId133: From now on, I'll need to stay close to observe and document everything in detail...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row28_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Could you please cooperate with me to ensure the accuracy of the data?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId133: You're like a fish out of water without coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId133: You've noticed this, too, haven't you?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Your performance in our challenges intriguingly correlates with your coffee consumption.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row26_TextContent_FromRoleId133: You just need to adjust the dose.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row27_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Slight adjustments can balance dependence and health perfectly.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId133: I have become accustomed to observing and deducing over time.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId133: After you ordered a latte, you snagged three consecutive wins.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Welcome. I'm here as your personal attendant.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Yes... You've ordered five cups of coffee today.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Just like your love for coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row23_PlayerOption1: Am I really that hooked on caffeine?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row23_PlayerOption2: Maybe I should consider giving up coffee?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId133: No need to worry. Enjoying coffee is quite the refined pastime.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row15_PlayerOption1: Hmm... But how did you do it?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId133: For this round, you just so happened to skip coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row11_PlayerOption2: I didn't have coffee whenever I lost... Could that be it?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row25_TextContent_FromRoleId133: That's not necessary. I'm not asking you to give up your hobby.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Stepping away from familiarity often leads to discomfort.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row11_PlayerOption1: If you put it this way...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row8_PlayerOption1: This... must be a coincidence, right?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId133: This record serves as supporting evidence.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId133: In that case... you can verify it for yourself.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row15_PlayerOption2: Don't tell me you can predict the future?

BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Stay right there and wait for me.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId112: I'm just glad you weren't hurt.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row19_PlayerOption2: It's fine, even if it's a little later today.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Just got word... the café will continue operations.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row5_PlayerOption1: What was that gunshot all about?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId112: The dagger and gun... let's say they're prepared for you.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Turns out, maids and mercenaries aren't so different; it's all about cleaning up "trash."
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId112: I hope you've learned your lesson. Next time...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId112: I went to the café for maid training.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row19_PlayerOption1: I've already spoken to the manager.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Looks like you won’t see the fruits of my maid training...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId112: My Sawtooth and dagger are in peak condition...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Since you've reserved a seat, why not swing by and check out my progress?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId112: What a shame, the café's about to close.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId112: And the amount of “trash” you need to clear.

Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row2_PlayerOption1: Maybe it's not quite over yet.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But everyone left in such a hurry, especially you, partner... You were the first one out the door!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId101: You mean this? Mighty Meow just found it on my doorstep...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row13_PlayerOption2: Everyone wrote what they wanted to say on it!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Fine, I'll leave you to it. I'll just continue with the cleanup...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I was hoping we could play some games together.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row6_PlayerOption1: Sorry, but I had something important to do for someone special...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Is this... everyone's birthday wishes for me?
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row6_PlayerOption2: I've got something even more important to take care of now.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row1_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I can't believe the birthday party's over already!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Getting so many birthday wishes is all thanks to you, partner! This birthday was amazing!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Huh? You're all mysterious, and I can't figure out what you're up to...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Awww... Thank you, partner, and thanks, everyone.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row9_PlayerOption2: This special someone is about to get a surprise!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row13_PlayerOption1: Yep, it's from all of us. We prepared it together.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Even though the party's over, I feel like you're all still with me.

Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row2_PlayerOption1: Maybe it's not quite over yet.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId101: You just head home and get ready.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But everyone left in such a hurry, especially you, partner... You were the first one out the door!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Mighty Meow came back earlier with a package in a rush.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Courier...? Could it be Mighty Meow?
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Relax, I've got the soda and controllers all set—ready to dive in anytime!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row1_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I can't believe the birthday party's over already!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row15_PlayerOption1: It's a long story. How about you check it out first?
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row6_PlayerOption2: It might just be the courier I mentioned.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId101: And tonight, let's play a little longer, okay?
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Oh wow... this is the latest sequel of Superheroes of Justice!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId101: This collector's edition is super rare! How did you manage to get one?
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row16_TextContent_FromPlayer: By the way, aren't we short on soda for our gaming sesh?

CreditScoreViolationExplanation.8_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Logging multiple accounts into the same device and performing far above the account's rank level will result in a smurfing/boosting violation.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.7_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Violations of this category refer to using third-party software or malicious programs to modify the game client. If you repeatedly team up with such players, you may also be penalized.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.1_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Violations of this category refer to behaviors such as deliberately avoiding attacking your opponents, not controlling your character, and/or purposely losing matches.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.2_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Violations of this category refer to quitting the game mid-match or being disconnected from the server for an extended period due to other reasons.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.3_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Violations of this category refer to negatively impacting other players' experience with character actions, items, and/or environmental mechanics.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.5_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Violations of this category refer to using voice chat or text to send offensive messages, including verbal abuse, hate speech, politically sensitive content, and/or obscene content.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.4_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Violations of this category refer to failing to accept matches when prompted.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.6_ViolationJudgmentDesc: Violations of this category refer to illegal teaming up, stream sniping, bribing opponents, and/or other methods of manipulating game outcomes.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.4_PunishDesc: Multiple violations within a short period will result in delayed matchmaking and placement in a low-priority queue. Frequent offenses over time will lower your reputation and temporarily ban you from ranked matches.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.1_PunishDesc: Your violation will be recorded. Multiple offenses within a certain period will lower your reputation and temporarily ban you from ranked matches.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.5_PunishDesc: Your violation will be recorded, and your reputation will be lowered.
CreditScoreViolationExplanation.7_PunishDesc: Violations will lower your reputation and result in a ban.

Emote.60000123_Desc: They say if you concentrate hard enough, you can make things appear...
Emote.60000158_Desc: Who came up with this bizarre mix of ingredients?
Emote.60000162_Desc: Splurge away! The guild leader's picking up the tab!
Emote.60000114_Desc: “To think, or not to think, that is the question...”
Emote.60000154_Desc: Pulling the trigger marks a new beginning.
Emote.60000172_Desc: My scythe seems quite interested in you.
Emote.60000174_Desc: The battle's over! Let me quickly stash away my mask.
Emote.60000134_Desc: No one can defeat me in my domain.
Emote.60000084_Desc: “Looks like someone needs to be taught a lesson.”
Emote.60000143_Desc: Wait, what was our plan again?
Emote.60000137_Desc: "The butterfly wants to play a game with you."
Emote.60000163_Desc: Your turn to shine, my friend.
Emote.60000115_Desc: "Please make me feel better with flowers..."
Emote.60000167_Desc: In the name of dedication, delays are not an option...
Emote.60000157_Desc: The mission to dodge the ninja blade... was a total flop!
Emote.60000138_Desc: Time for me to step up!
Emote.60000111_Desc: The fragrance is about to fill the battlefield.

Emote_I18N.60000105_Desc: Oh no, where's the tomato in my tomato scramble?
Emote_I18N.60000106_Desc: Oh great, my tomato scramble is missing the eggs...

GameplayCard_Escort2.10013009_Desc: [Weaken] Inflict burn on enemies when dealing damage, 1 DMG/s for 3s, up to 5 stacks.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013004_Desc: [Weaken] Slows enemies by 30% for 1.5s when hit.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013048_Desc: [Weaken] Upon death, reveal enemies within 5m to allies for 2s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013026_Desc: [Weaken] Reduce enemy Movement SPD by 20% within a 5m radius.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013015_Desc: [Skill] Using a skill restores 20 HP and 10 Armor. CD: 8s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013018_Desc: [Skill] Using Ultimate grants 10% Rate of Fire, Weapon Usability, and 50 temporary armor for 10s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013012_Desc: [Skill] 5% chance to reset CD when using non-Ultimate Skill.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013031_Desc: [Skill] Participating in a kill restores 25% CD of non-ultimate skills.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013047_Desc: [Skill] Silences enemies within 5m of a destroyed summon for 2s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013016_Desc: [Skill] Mark enemy for 5s on skill hit, teammates deal extra 30 DMG. CD: 10s per target.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013014_Desc: [Skill] Hitting enemies with a skill boosts Movement SPD by 10% for 3s. CD: 6s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013019_Desc: [Skill] Disables Ultimate, but reduces other skill CDs by 20%.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013050_Desc: [Skill] After using a skill, the next attack deals an extra 30 DMG. CD: 6s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013017_Desc: [Support] Buffing/healing teammates grants extra 20 HP and 10 Armor. CD: 8s per teammate.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013007_Desc: [Support] Shooting allies heals 10% of DMG as HP and 5% as armor.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013057_Desc: [Mechanic] Steal 20% of enemy's String Energy Points on kill.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013038_Desc: [Mechanic] Round escort time is reduced by 50% (max 30s).
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013055_Desc: [Mechanic] Increase experience earned from all sources by 15%.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013036_Desc: [Mechanic] Gain 15% more String Energy Points from all sources.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013039_Desc: [Mechanic] Overtime triggers when time hits 0; extends base overtime by 2s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013056_Desc: [Mechanic] Increase max capacity of each throwable by 1.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013020_Desc: [Survival] Restore 20 HP and 15 Armor/s after 7s unharmed.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013053_Desc: [Survival] Gain 30 Armor and 20% Movement SPD for 3s upon enemy kill or assist.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013025_Desc: [Survival] Within payload interaction range, gain 10% Stringified Movement SPD boost and 5% Stringified DMG Reduction.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013043_Desc: [Survival] Recover 50% of DMG dealt as HP.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013044_Desc: [Survival] Remove Armor and convert 135% of Armor cap to extra HP cap.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013051_Desc: Gain 50 temporary armor when armor is destroyed. CD: 15s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013030_Desc: [Survival] Picking up dropped Armor doubles its effect and refills the current magazine.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013052_Desc: [Survival] Near death triggers 3s of invincibility (immobile), then restores to 100 HP. CD: 45s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013032_Desc: Gain 100 temporary armor when HP is below 20%. CD: 40s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013005_Desc: [Survival] Gain 45 temporary armor by breaking enemy armor. CD: 10s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013034_Desc: [Survival] Avoid death and enter self-revive state; return with 50 HP after 5s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013021_Desc: Replenish temporary armor to 75 after 7s unharmed.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013041_Desc: [Agility] After canceling Wall-Stick, enter Stealth and remain unarmed for 3s. CD: 15s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013045_Desc: [Agility] Increase Movement SPD by 15% when moving toward the payload.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013040_Desc: [Agility] Stringify for 3s to auto-refill current magazine ammo.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013028_Desc: [Agility] Boost DMG by 30% for 3s after Stringifying for 5s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013035_Desc: [Agility] Respawn with 50% Movement SPD for 10s, reducing over time; ends if DMG is taken/dealt.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013024_Desc: [Damage] After 7s without receiving DMG, your next attack deals an extra 50 DMG.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013008_Desc: [Damage] When dealing DMG, instantly kill enemies if their HP drops below 10%.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013046_Desc: [Damage] Secondary Weapons gain an extra 50% DMG to stringified enemies.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013029_Desc: [Damage] Hitting stringified enemies has a 60% chance to refill the current weapon by 1 ammo.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013027_Desc: [Damage] Increase DMG by 10% within payload interaction zones.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013002_Desc: [Damage] Boosts DMG by 15% for targets within 15m.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013003_Desc: [Damage] Boosts DMG by 15% for targets beyond 15m.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013010_Desc: [Damage] Deal 10% more DMG to enemies near the payload.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013049_Desc: [Damage] Headshot DMG increased by 200%; other areas deal 50% less DMG.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013022_Desc: [Damage] When Armor is above 80% of its max value, increase DMG by 10%.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013054_Desc: [Damage] Upon death, leave a grenade with 150% DMG.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013042_Desc: [Damage] Each hit on the payload deals 2 DMG to enemies attached to it.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013001_Desc: [Damage] Headshots boost Movement SPD by 10% for 3s and heal 15 HP. CD: 6s.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013033_Desc: [Damage] When HP is below 50%, gain 10% Rate of Fire, Movement Speed, and Weapon Usability.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013006_Desc: [Damage] Breaking enemy armor slows them by 50% and deals 50 extra DMG for 2s. CD: 3s per target.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013011_Desc: [Damage] Each hit boosts 1% Rate of Fire and Weapon Usability for 5s, up to 15 stacks.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013081_Desc: Shooting effects vary by temperature level.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013094_Desc: Reduce max HP of enemies in Aroma zone.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013084_Desc: Fully recover if beacon is destroyed.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013092_Desc: Survive a fatal hit and auto-trigger teleport.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013083_Desc: Gain an extra Dash after dashing to enemies.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013091_Desc: Spawning a Decoy drops a delayed flashbang.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013085_Desc: Auto-trigger spirit state upon fatal hit.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013070_Desc: Enhance debuff when Sand Wall is hit.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013071_Desc: Enable one rebound for Sonar Disk.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013068_Desc: Inflict String-Block with ultimate's light screen.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013076_Desc: Force enemies apart within ultimate area.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013063_Desc: Gain Movement SPD when damaging enemies.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013079_Desc: Star bounces to a second teammate.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013059_Desc: Triggers a self-destruct when Pawtector is destroyed.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013093_Desc: Stun enemies lingering in the Aroma zone.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013082_Desc: The Grenade Launcher can be used while moving.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013069_Desc: Negate one fatal hit while Airborne.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013064_Desc: Inflict Silence with the electric field.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013067_Desc: Moving light screen deals extra DMG.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013060_Desc: The Mighty Meow can now move upon being deployed.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013075_Desc: Getting hit again during passive triggers stun.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013062_Desc: Delay reveal while in camo state.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013088_Desc: Enemies in the area take continuous damage, healing Fuchsia.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013065_Desc: Extend scan range on enemy detection with dagger scan.
GameplayCard_Escort2.10013074_Desc: First resurrection uses no ultimate energy.

Gift.1_Defaultmailtext: Dear 【{0}】, when I saw this, I thought of you. I hope it can bring you a measure of happiness and surprise!
Gift.2_Defaultmailtext: Whether in defense or offense, I will accompany you through thick and thin. So... could you gift me a 【{0}】?

Goods.10101019_Desc:
The personalized Inspector paint job commemorates Michele's smile upon completing her first quest.

"Vanguard, ready for assault!"
Goods.10404002_Desc: From the "Colorburst" series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10404004_Desc: The Dreambreaker series combines patchy blues with occasional yellow fragments for a striking, shattered effect.
Goods.10404005_Desc: The popular P.U.S-04 Vigilance adds a bright and distinctive finish to the P.U.S arsenal.
Goods.10404003_Desc: The Thunderfire series seamlessly blends contemporary sleekness with retro orange-gray criss-crossing elements.
Goods.31000033_Desc: Area 88 is where the largest financial system of Strinova is located.
Goods.30000115_Desc: Charge ahead! Explore new dimensions, each with its own youthful spirit!
Goods.30002014_Desc:
"A site secure! Plant the bomb!"

"Wait... where's my bomb?"
Goods.60000097_Desc: "No, no, just a little bit more."
Goods.60000080_Desc: "Oh my, a new BBQ stall?! Guess I'll have to try it now!"
Goods.60000100_Desc: "No matter the challenge, we'll face it together!"
Goods.10101002_Desc: The "Jungle" series features a primarily green gun body with subtle orange stripes. Not the prettiest tool in the shed, but it gets the job done.
Goods.31001034_Desc: "Why do I wear red? Because it brings good luck! The closer you are to me, the luckier you will be!"
Goods.10102009_Desc: The Crisscross series features a dark base with intersecting lines, creating a dazzling display on the battlefield.
Goods.31000181_Desc: “People need shelter and resources to survive, but also the bells and sunlight to awaken the soul.”
Goods.31001112_Desc: "In the name of the student council, these activities are forbidden at school."
Goods.10202002_Desc: The "Bushwhack" series camo design suits various combat environments.
Goods.10108002_Desc: Embers series paint job featuring fiery orange and ashy gray.
Goods.60001004_Desc: “Are you interested in flowers as well?”
Goods.31001081_Desc: "Surely you saw the troubled expression on the guest's face?"
Goods.31001121_Desc: What are you afraid of? Battle, farewell, or me turning it all upside down?
Goods.60000056_Desc: “Do you know what the world inside a donut looks like?”
Goods.60000082_Desc: “Can you blow bubbles better than I can?”
Goods.10102007_Desc: The "Faith" series features a black base with The Scissors emblem, showcasing the holder's unwavering resolve.
Goods.31000191_Desc: "The pioneers say the brilliance from the depths of string energy resembles sunrise, bringing long-lost splendor to humanity."
Goods.10101026_Desc: The "Wave Surfer" series evokes beachside wave imagery with its minimalist blockish color design.
Goods.21007_Desc:
"Do you have to arrive early for performances? Fine, let's rehearse." - The Big Bad Wolf, an unemployed person who wishes to remain anonymous
(Opening it 40 times guarantees an Epic outfit or weapon skin. Opening it 80 times guarantees a full set of Epic outfits or weapon skins)
Goods.31001113_Desc: "Hold those screams—let them loose when I hit the stage!"
Goods.10106111_Desc:
The special Spring Blessings edition of "Polaris," inspired by the motif "Ascendance," embodies the courage and determination Celestia has gradually built up through past hardships.

“For the patients, I won't back down anymore. This is what my predecessors taught me.”
Goods.10106108_Desc:
A special customized version of the Polaris featuring a smoothed barrel that provides better grip. The embellished azure crystals also serve as an energy source for the firearm, enabling its bullets to race toward the targets like shooting stars.

【“This is no ordinary wishing star. It always flies toward my desired target.”】
Goods.10106107_Desc:
A custom version of the Polaris, this model loses the original's cold weapon vibe, making it perfect for date nights. The scope also serves as a makeup mirror, enabling users to check their makeup anytime, anywhere.

"That was such a blast! I need to touch up my makeup... Heh.”
Goods.10106106_Desc:
The specialized "Polaris" Model was a gift obtained from the Celestia Space Center. Designed to resemble a space station, it symbolizes humanity's dream of reaching the endless cosmos. It's no exaggeration to call this weapon a masterpiece of industrial art.

"To the endless sky, I offer my endless longing and love."
Goods.10106201_Desc: This customized version of the Polaris features a striking scarlet rose in full bloom. A sword of knightly protection cuts through the design, telling a tale of beauty and valor.
Goods.10106104_Desc:
Artistic Polaris model. References to fairy tales from old Earth reveal a surprising innocence in this weapon's designer.

【Wrapped in fragile dreams, a child's innocence beams. Kindness and purity, in our essence, gleams.】
Goods.10403108_Desc:
A customized version of the "Champion" featuring enhanced sensitivity to light. Whether for photography or firing bullets, it performs in perfection.

“This moment is worth capturing, don't you think?”
Goods.10403115_Desc: The Campus Open Day edition of the Champion is crafted per the student council vice president's request. It captures the academy's spirit while celebrating the Grove family's honor.
Goods.10403111_Desc:
Crafted by Grove artisans, the "Champion" gala edition dazzles with a glass-like sheen and refreshing elegance. Perfect for making a statement at noble gatherings.

"Let's steal the spotlight."
Goods.10403105_Desc: The artistic custom version of "Champion" is inspired by old Earth's local folklore, vividly showcasing a deeply cultural aesthetic.
Goods.31000184_Desc: “As her deformed body falls into eternal decay, she draws the corrupted souls into the sea of flowers nevertheless.”
Goods.10111005_Desc: The Rebel series features a striking color contrast and a pattern design resembling a swift, powerful lightning bolt, perfectly capturing the spirit of rebellion and defiance.
Goods.31000193_Desc: “Silent is the ancient temple, yet the footsteps of pioneers and successors echo throughout.”
Goods.60001014_Desc: “I was so shocked I snapped by paintbrush!”
Goods.60001012_Desc: “I'm not talking to you for the next three minutes!”
Goods.60000092_Desc: “Ha-ha-ha-ha! Amazing! Yes, that. Could you do it again?”
Goods.31000154_Desc:
"Meow! Meow, meow, meow!"
Pawtector seems to be training Mighty Meow, who is not so good at video games.
Goods.31001120_Desc: “They called me the Grim Reaper before I became a countess. She is ever so unpredictable. Nonetheless, this is how I received an invitation.”
Goods.10106003_Desc: The "Multiverse" series features a Strinova-inspired design. Its simple yet intricate patterns exude a unique charm.
Goods.10503101_Desc: A custom relic edition of Night Scythe, infused with folklore and traditional craftsmanship from the Seeda Peninsula, giving modern firearms the feel of ancient weaponry. Perhaps, those who wield it in battle can hear the blessings of ancient warriors.
Goods.10503102_Desc:
The Gothic-style Night Scythe is the Undead Countess's cherished weapon. Adorned with thorns and a haunting ghostly visage, it's the embodiment of death itself.

"She invited me, so I've come. After all, her secrets intrigue me."
Goods.60001018_Desc: “I feel dizzy. I can't possibly finish all the drafts...”
Goods.60001015_Desc: “Yay! I finished it before the deadline!”
Goods.31000186_Desc: “She... It stands on top of the tower, bringing down endless fear and confusion.”
Goods.31000185_Desc: “If you find it, please listen carefully. What's sealed is not a mad desire but a trembling heart.”
Goods.31001065_Desc: “Please let us know if anything is not to your liking.”
Goods.31001107_Desc: "If you wish, I'd cross time and space to meet you."
Goods.10304103_Desc:
A customized version of the Judge. Under the setting sun, two cranes fly away, bidding farewell to the departed.

【The wings of the crane shall guide you home.】
Goods.10304110_Desc:
The Inspector butler edition combines clean design with functional add-ons, providing a classy companion for when you're in the mood for a gentle buzz.

"Feel free to indulge; I've got your back."
Goods.10304108_Desc:
A modified version of the "Judge" that incorporates chess pieces into the design, exclusively customized for chess show matches. Its sleek black and gold design makes it one of Nobunaga's favorites.

"I'll always be one move ahead of you."
Goods.10304109_Desc:
A modified version of the Judge that incorporates chess pieces into the design, exclusively customized for chess show matches. Its sleek black and gold design makes it one of Nobunaga's favorites.

【"I will also think one move ahead of you."】
Goods.10403107_Desc:
The customized "Manor's Grace" model's intricate design proves that high art can be just as deadly.

"Today's menu includes refreshing tea, delicious snacks, and a hearty supply of bullets."
Goods.31001066_Desc: “I'll come visit often, if only for the amazing tea.”
Goods.10106006_Desc: The "Chimera" series features an elegant orange mosaic design with deep and light tones, creating an artistic look.
Goods.30001022_Desc: "May it restore your body's strength once more..."
Goods.31001115_Desc: Hope the teacher doesn't catch me trying to build a mega toy in class!
Goods.60000053_Desc: "The 1 Bamboo might be small, but you can't win without it!"
Goods.20123102_Desc:
During the Spring Festival, the "Dreams to Reality" exhibit inspired a trend among the Strinovians, leading to a collection of refined garments modeled after ancient mural attire.

"Ahem, stop staring at me and get back to work, everyone. The festival is approaching, but let's stay focused on our tasks."
Goods.20205105_Desc:
During the Spring Festival, the "Dreams to Reality" exhibit inspired a trend among the Strinovians, leading to a collection of refined garments modeled after ancient mural attire.

"Oh my, it feels like I'm about to ascend to the heavens in this outfit."
Goods.20124109_Desc:
During the Spring Festival, the "Dreams to Reality" exhibit inspired a trend among the Strinovians, leading to a collection of refined garments modeled after ancient mural attire.

"How do I look? It suits me, right? I've heard so many legends about ancient celestial beings, and it's my first time dressing up like one. This is so much fun!"
Goods.10501103_Desc:
The personalized "Beareas" model features a luxurious purple finish, a cute panda face, and a fierce soundwave effect when firing, symbolizing the passionate heart hidden beneath the user’s cold exterior.

“The taciturn girl pursed her lips tightly, letting out no sound. The music dancing with gunfire speaks for her.”
Goods.10501110_Desc:
A customized version of Beareas, featuring camouflage painting by the host of a shooter game. Thanks to Yvette's stealth abilities, the compact Beareas is capable of delivering deadly strikes.

"Don't worry. They can't see me. I can take care of myself."
Goods.10501109_Desc:
A special edition "Beareas" model, featuring a bold retro-artistic design. Inspired by luminous pearls, it’s set with these gems, giving it an extraordinary elegance.

"The pearl in your hand sparkles, dazzling ever more gloriously in the dark."
Goods.10101003_Desc: From the "Colorburst" series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10301105_Desc:
A customized Chroma model, ideal for outdoor combat. The gun's decor is inspired by animals Maddelena sketched in the wild, with cute expressions sure to bring a smile.

"This is my little companion. Why not say hello?"
Goods.10301106_Desc:
The customized Chroma features a sleek space design enhanced with pink-purple energy beams symbolizing cosmic nebulae. These beams not only provide powerful energy for the weapon but also serve as excellent illuminators, making her creation shine brightly in the dark void of space.

“Let me adorn you to make you even more radiant.”
Goods.10301111_Desc:
Specialized Chroma model. Adorned in bright green and decorated with cartoonish characters, this firearm is the perfect embodiment of Maddelena - romantic whimsy and childlike innocence.

【“It's funny, isn't it? When we're young, we couldn't wait to grow up, and now that we're grown, we wish we could be children again.'"】
Goods.10301110_Desc:
The classically designed romantic Chroma model features a tambourine on its body, ready to play a delightful dance tune.

“Don't fear my bullets; I'm just inviting you to join in a tambourine performance.”
Goods.10301107_Desc:
This lightweight Chroma modification captures the essence of melody in its design. When fired, each shot resonates like a dynamic note.

“It's time to dance, my friends!”
Goods.10104110_Desc:
A customized Shadow Assault model, featuring a sapphire seamlessly set into the hollow barrel, mirroring The Scissors' flawless plan.

"It's time!"
Goods.10104107_Desc:
A customized version of the Shadow Assault featuring clever camouflage suitable for convert operations, embodying the concept of patience.

【“Hey, are the leaves talking?”】
Goods.10104101_Desc:
The customized Shadow Assault features gilded edges like the setting sun and a crimson barrel resembling twilight clouds, symbolizing the splendid future people once hoped to see.

“Beautiful as the evening glow may be, it cannot escape the storm that cleanses the sky.”
Goods.10104111_Desc:
The customized Shadow Assault features a concealed blade on its night-black frame, revealing its ruby-red edge only at critical moments, much like Lawine, who waits discreetly in the café, poised to act.

"There are unidentified people in the café... For your safety, I'll step in if necessary."
Goods.10501106_Desc:
The customized "Frost Core" model features a delicate ice core encased in intricate metalwork. The bullets it fires are not scorching hot, but bone-chillingly cold.

“Rest assured, this bullet won't hurt you, but it may harm you in another way.”
Goods.60000036_Desc: “And now we have even more patients...”
Goods.60000081_Desc: “May the world be full of colors.”
Goods.31000189_Desc: “We had the purest intentions, but the tower eventually led to opposite ends.”
Goods.60000078_Desc: “The way I fell was pretty cool, right?”
Goods.60000087_Desc: “I've been looking forward to this day.”
Goods.60001016_Desc: “My mood is as sweet as a refreshing glass of juice.”
Goods.60000071_Desc: “If I get serious, Mighty Meow won't be the only thing I throw!”
Goods.20107206_Desc:
"The most important ability of a detective is..."
"What is it?"
"Uh... Observing, summarizing, analyzing, and putting it into practice!"
"That's it? I expected some secrets. Don't forget you promised to catch the thief first."
"When is the thief planning to strike?"
"...Now."
"Oh! I better not waste time here! I'm off to find clues. See you!"

A girl with a coffee cup flits from a steam engine to an ancient whale fossil, exploring mischievously. In the retro museum, a battle between detective and thief is about to begin.
"I shouldn't have taken this job. I have no experience with thieves..." The detective nervously sips her coffee.
Her frustration centers around the exhibit in the glass case before her: the "Icarus Device." This legendary gadget, crafted with retro steam technology, uses intricate mechanisms to let a person fly—useless to Maddalena, but perfect for her quirky collection.
A notorious thief has issued a warning, vowing to snatch the Icarus Device in plain sight. Due to the bustling shopping festival, the warning arrives at the museum just a day before the scheduled heist. Desperate, the curator calls Urbino for help.
To cover her coffee expenses for the next month and the maintenance for her Fully Automatic Creative Retro Victorian Steampunk Gothic Hand-Operated Mechanical Latte Mocha Espresso Flat White Compression Modulating Machine, Maddalena jumps into action.
However...
Goods.60000088_Desc: “I'm sorry... I've apologized. You're not mad anymore, are you?”
Goods.10111056_Desc: The Predator series features a bionic camo design, offering excellent camouflage in complex environments.
Goods.31000001_Desc: Making contact and observing are only the first steps. It's up to you to make the next move, Navigator.
Goods.60000086_Desc: “How dare you show yourself in Preton? I'll make it pay!”
Goods.31001105_Desc: "Wishing everyone a bountiful year of wealth and prosperity... Wait, the lucky beast? It's this little one on my shoulder, of course!"
Goods.10101056_Desc: The "Golden Surge" series, launched by Polaris Labs, features a dark gold pattern that combines a cool, flashy look with a powerful sense of metallic stability.
Goods.10404101_Desc:
This retro Calibrator model replicates ancient murals from the "Dreams to Reality" historical exhibit. In your hands, it evokes an era of civilization’s brilliance.

"Under the beast's blessing, the pavilion shall stand tall."
Goods.10404103_Desc:
The arcade-themed Calibrator draws inspiration from Leona's favorite childhood fighting game. She'll always remember the nostalgia of executing secret combos.

"Take this! It's the ultimate justice combo!"
Goods.31001114_Desc: “Every season of campus life has something to cherish, like the cherry blossoms you're looking at.”
Goods.10106007_Desc: The "Prisma" series uses refractive fragmentation, with artistic purple shades evoking a kaleidoscopic feeling.
Goods.31000151_Desc:
“Welcome to The Hometown. How would you like your egg cooked?”
Shows like this seem to be quite popular at the restaurant called The Hometown.
Goods.10112105_Desc:
This retro Gambit model replicates ancient murals from the "Dreams to Reality" historical exhibit. In your hands, it evokes an era of civilization's brilliance.

"A celestial dance in timeless skies."
Goods.10112104_Desc:
The customized stage version of the Gambit is adorned with a microphone and floating musical notes. When you suddenly hear Galatea's voice, you may have already stepped into her trap.

“Do you like my singing? You're in for a treat.”
Goods.10112103_Desc:
A reimagined "Gambit" with plentiful feather details for a less intimidating look. The user claims even its appearance plays into the deception.

"Dazzling and spellbinding!"
Goods.10112107_Desc:
The arcade-themed Gambit features a gun skin designed to match the clothing, inspired by Galatea's favorite childhood space shooter game.

"I miss those childhood days playing games with my sister. She'd cry when she lost; it was adorable."
Goods.30001021_Desc: "The masked nurse of justice, ready to defeat all ailments!"
Goods.31001118_Desc: “Too long has the Castle of Eternal Night slumbered. It is time to awaken it. Will you take part in the grand revival?”
Goods.60001006_Desc: “Don't worry about me. I just need a moment...”
Goods.10102003_Desc: The "Tidal Wave" series is composed of a series of blue modules meant to imitate the shape of a wave. It may lack the sound of the sea, but it remains a delight.
Goods.10111055_Desc: The Graffiti series by Corridor Artisans creatively combines spray and street art elements, bringing Urbino's vibrant culture to life.
Goods.10304002_Desc: From the Deep Lake series. Streaks of light and dark on resplendent cyan make for a restrained and brooding design.
Goods.10101007_Desc: From the "Vivid" series. Made up of a variety of overlapping hexagonal color blocks, this firearm's streams of color give off the illusion of added firepower.
Goods.10106004_Desc: The "Ardor" series, URB-00 custom edition, features vibrant, edgy colors that reflect the latest trends, and is a favorite among Urbino members.
Goods.10112004_Desc: The "Ardor" series, URB-00 custom edition, features vibrant, edgy colors that reflect the latest trends, and is a favorite among Urbino members.
Goods.31000190_Desc: “The bear will protect you, though mainly the land beneath you.”
Goods.10502104_Desc:
A customized version of Solo featuring crimson jamón ibérico. With the right condiments, it could almost capture an authentic Iberian flavor. Such a delicious appearance might just make enemies drop their guard.

“Careful. Don't fall for this deliciously charming trap.”
Goods.10502102_Desc:
The customized Solo model features a dark theme with embedded crystals that gleam brightly even at night, exhibiting a mysterious deep blue shine like the sea.

"Wondering what I'm thinking? Why not... take a guess? It's a way to get to know each other."
Goods.10502106_Desc:
A modified version of Solo. It features gradients, bright colors, and grids to emphasize a futuristic feel. The additional buttons are also highly favored by gamers.

"Press a key, get a sound, and hear your opponents' screams."
Goods.10502107_Desc:
The modified Solo was Flavia's go-to weapon during her early missions with P.U.S. Its clean design echoes the precision of her successful missions.

"This gun sets the boundary—ten meters out is where danger starts."
Goods.10502109_Desc:
The Gothic-style Solo showcases a spirit butterfly fluttering over bones, as if mourning the departed, despite being the very lure that led them to this graveyard.

"Rest in peace. There is no death - only eternal slumber."
Goods.10502105_Desc:
This exclusive edition of Solo features decorations and colors inspired by beach elements like pearls, shells, and conchs. It makes one wonder if, when held to the ear, you might hear the sound of ocean waves.

"Doesn't it look like a whale made of shells? Light and free."
Goods.10502101_Desc:
A modified lightweight version of Solo, serving not only as a weapon but also as an essential accessory that holds the secrets of beauty for any lady.

“Be there in a second. I need to touch up my makeup and take care of the nearby enemies. It won't take long.”
Goods.60000012_Desc: “I'm off to bed... We'll talk tomorrow.”
Goods.10303104_Desc:
A customized version of the Dawn featuring an enhanced streamlined design and decorative metal that Reiichi finds befitting for the theme of space fantasy. There also appear to be fragments of a solar panel, but what are they used for? Only Reiichi, the inventor, knows the answer.

【“What is the solar panel used for? I figured it would provide extra functions to the gun. Unfortunately, that's a failed experiment.”】
Goods.10303108_Desc:
A special version of "Dawn," designed for camouflage in forests to reduce visibility, with built-in repair tools for close combat scenarios. However, as a sniper, Reiichi hopes they never need to be used.

"You need tools to repair stuff, whatever it is."
Goods.10303105_Desc:
A customized "Dawn" model with chess pieces in its design, crafted for a chess exhibition match. Reiichi made personal tweaks to the prototype, redesigning the pegasus frame and its unique patterns.

"Can you outsmart my traps and break free? Opportunities for advantage are brief. Hear that? Tick-tock."
Goods.10111002_Desc: The Fractured Lines series uses artfully broken lines to enhance visual impact. Its minimalist design conveys a layered and discordant beauty.
Goods.10101006_Desc: The Dreambreaker series combines patchy blues with occasional yellow fragments for a striking, shattered effect.
Goods.60000067_Desc: “The mysterious power is in your hands.”
Goods.10102056_Desc: The "Forbidden" series showcases a standard paint job adapted for improved concealment in Cosmite's environment. Its pronounced warning label is as good as any permit.
Goods.10301002_Desc: The Mystic Mark series's eye-catching indigo blocks laced with beautiful orange lines once found considerable favor in the community.
Goods.10202112_Desc:
This retro Quasar model replicates ancient murals from the "Dreams to Reality" historical exhibit. In your hands, it evokes an era of civilization's brilliance.

"The beauty of the land is unmatched... how I wish the painted scenes could truly appear."
Goods.10202113_Desc: A custom relic edition of Quasar that blends elements of Seeda Peninsula's culture, giving modern firearms an ancient material feel. Legend has it that those who carry it into the desert's depths receive the land's protection.
Goods.10202108_Desc:
A customized version of Quasar created to commemorate Kokona's victory in a cycling competition. Light and stylish, the barrel is designed with inspiration from bicycle dynamics.

“I'll tell you a secret: I am as fast as a bullet when I cycle.”
Goods.10202114_Desc: The Campus Open Day edition of Quasar draws inspiration from the crafting club, featuring a harmonized color scheme. The simple equations evoke memories of doodles on school desks.
Goods.10202107_Desc:
A modified version of Quasar featuring a new spray-paint process. Its precise sight can also be used to observe scanner malfunctions. Although it is only a minor improvement, Kokona has taken a liking to this modification.

"Kokona, please don't point your gun at Mighty Meow!"
Goods.31001116_Desc: Maybe I'll just head straight home from here... Wait, no... I'll get in trouble for that....
Goods.10106002_Desc: A Purple Crystal paint job featuring connoting purple with vibrant blue stripes.
Goods.10102005_Desc: The "Violet Gold" series features a unique blend of purple and gold, giving the weapon a distinct texture.
Goods.10111007_Desc: The Riot series features The Scissors' iconic colors and an unconventional design that symbolizes their rebellious nature, making this design popular among veteran members.
Goods.10102054_Desc: The "House of Cards" series features a tasteful heart and black square palette, adorned with elegant chibi versions of The Scissors, exuding a sense of luxury.
Goods.10106053_Desc: A model in the "House of Cards" series, coveted by Urbino fighters who favor bringing this artistic weapon into battle.
Goods.10113102_Desc:
The "Retribution" music fest edition is tailored for an electrifying stage show. With a bustling backdrop of mics, headsets, and keyboards, every detail perfectly complements Yugiri's style.

"To become a beloved idol... Are there more specific instructions? No worries, I'll make it happen."
Goods.10113101_Desc:
The "Retribution" ball edition captures the elegant dance of a gray swan on water. Feathers drift gracefully and vanish into tears upon touch.

"I never learned to dance formally; my steps are just imperfect imitations from books and films. Since you find it acceptable, I conclude that imitation works well enough."
Goods.10113103_Desc:
The "Retribution" Spring Blessing edition. Before breaking free from the lab, Yugiri had never encountered real snow, yet she found those icy, shimmering flakes enchanting. She made sure to add a touch of snow to her weapon's redesign.

"Snow that never melts… the most treasured memory of winter."
Goods.10111101_Desc:
A modified version of the Blossom. It allows Fragrans to rally her allies in addition to healing them.

"Don't worry. I'll drown out those discordant sounds."
Goods.10111106_Desc:
The Gothic-style Blossom is adorned with Cattleya orchids, carefully cultivated by Fragrans. If slumber is inevitable, let a requiem accompany it.

"There will be no pain, only a long, sweet dream enveloped in the fragrance of flowers."
Goods.10111105_Desc:
The Spring Blessing edition of Blossom. Known for its fiery tail, the legendary koi symbolizes good luck. Inspired by this theme, Fragrans customized her weapon, hoping her newly developed aroma will bring everyone luck in the new year.

"Let's name this aroma Koi. Maybe it'll help boost our battle win rate."
Goods.10101028_Desc: The "Weave" series draws inspiration from classic fashion pieces, featuring simple yet bold colors, perfect for showcasing style.
Goods.10602105_Desc:
The custom model of Freedom Reign unleashes all the potential of the original, like an untamable charging bull.

"This is what breaking free feels like!"
Goods.10602103_Desc:
A customized concept version of the Freedom Reigns made by Bai Mo featuring a breathtaking bold design. It is rumored that the shape of the gun pays tribute to one of his past hobbies...

ã€�Did you really believe that I wanted to become a baker? Don't tell anybody that. It's a rumor! A rumor!ã€?
RoleVoice
Goods.10602106_Desc:
An exclusive Freedom Reign custom edition. With a neon color-changing phantom emblem and "BAIMO" signature, it shines brightly at night, just as Baimo intended.

"Repeat after me, Bai...Mo. Haha, let's dash forward and light up the night!"
Goods.10602112_Desc:
The Freedom Reign arcade-exclusive edition features retro, playful colors that evoke the joy of your first gaming experiences.

"Turns out, the hero vs dragon theme never gets old! Wait, you want to be the dragon...?"
Goods.10602109_Desc:
The special election edition of Freedom Reign, featuring Bai Mo's favorite green design with added trinkets won from spray-paint competitions. With a single rebel gunshot, Urbino's new era may be set into motion.

“Let this rebellious bullet herald the dawn of a new era!”
Goods.10602104_Desc:
The Freedom Reigns custom job heavily leans into its metallic base reminiscent of freight machinery, often leading others to fatally underestimate its strength in battle. After all, it's not called a “Power Brake” for nothing.

"You can't sprint without mastering how to brake. Absolute control—that's the Urbino way.
Goods.10303102_Desc:
The "Lethal Servant" personalized version, designed and modified by Reiichi, serves as both a weapon and an umbrella, showcasing his unique ideals and aesthetics.

"This way, you can use the umbrella even when it's not raining."
Goods.30001020_Desc: "Bitter medicine works miracles; be brave and take it for a quick recovery."
Goods.31001097_Desc: Delightfully cute and tasty omelette rice!
Goods.10113007_Desc: The "Sunset" series features a tasteful orange-white gradient, symbolizing the coming of twilight.
Goods.10106008_Desc: The "Hive" series features a tech-inspired blue and purple theme with hexagrammic border designs, showcasing the beauty of precise and meticulous science.
Goods.31001106_Desc: "Captivated by my performance? That's only natural."
Goods.31000188_Desc: “Why? I don't know. I'm just a Mighty Meow.”
Goods.10101004_Desc: The popular PUS-04 “Vigilance” adds a bright and distinctive finish to the P.U.S arsenal.
Goods.10101112_Desc:
The Spring Blessings edition of the Inspector, features a Loong from Eastern mythology. The vibrant red design and blazing flames match Michele's excitement during the fireworks festival.

“How about I fire the first shot of the New Year? Hehe, just kidding."
Goods.10101109_Desc:
The custom Inspector model requires not just luck to become the God of Mahjong, but also the skill and courage to seize it. Fortunately, Michele has both in spades.

"Kong! Kong! Kong! Blossoming from a Kong, Big Four Winds, All Honours!"
Goods.10101102_Desc:
The custom Inspector design. Beneath its sweet exterior lurks a girl's biggest foe—calories.

"These chocolate mags look so tasty... I'm sure a bite would be fine... right?"
Goods.10101108_Desc:
The Inspector custom edition, tailored to Michele's combat style and quirks, serves as a warning amid the raging waves that she is not someone to mess with.

“You almost hit Captain Michele!”
Goods.10101018_Desc:
A customized paint job of the Inspector. Michele is also lovingly animated in Chibi style.
“You will beg for mercy.”
Goods.10101014_Desc:
A customized paint job of the Inspector. It tells of a truth Michele has always believed in.
“The pinker the skin, the stronger the blow.”
Goods.10101106_Desc:
A winter edition of the Inspector, blending camouflage with cuteness. Specially treated to ensure reliable performance even in the cold, it's Michele's favorite for challenges.

“Approach silently, like a snow leopard!”
Goods.10101104_Desc:
The Inspector concept model daringly integrates lava effects into its design, with flowing patterns that evoke the flames of purgatory.

“Amid sulfur and fire, justice prevails.”
Goods.10101107_Desc:
A customized concept version of the Inspector. Glided with blue and white strips, it is both luxurious and stylish. A cute baseball decoration adds a splash of playfulness to this weapon. Run the bases and win!

"This baseball is a souvenir for stealing a base!"
Michele smiles brightly as she wipes the sweat from her brow.
Goods.31000147_Desc: "Eh? It's so strange. You obviously followed the recipe step by step...!"
Goods.31001119_Desc: “There's no need to be afraid. Though I often have my eyes covered, I am not blind. I simply choose not to witness more suffering...”
Goods.20112058_Desc: “Combat and rock n' roll are not mutually exclusive.”
Goods.10201104_Desc:
The "Finale" custom edition gathers cherished memories close to the heart. Which one will you be hit with?

"Kanami's most precious memory will capture your heart!"
Goods.10201107_Desc:
A customized model of the "Finale." An energy beam reflected by diamonds flows within the barrel, where Kanami's signed announcement is carefully placed.

“Welcome to Kanami's magic world!”
Goods.10201109_Desc:
A customized edition of the "Finale" for the Galactic Concert. It showcases a sleek, futuristic design with starry accents that shimmer in sync with Kanami on stage.

“Bang! I'll be the brightest among the swirling stars!”
Goods.10201111_Desc:
Inspired by red plums in the snow, this unique modification of Finale features rugged branches winding around the barrel, capturing the delicate scent of blossoms in winter.

"Does this image remind you of a snowy plum forest? Perhaps Kanami is like the little bird singing from the treetops."
Goods.10201105_Desc:
The modded "Finale" model was originally just a performance prop for Kanami. With Reiichi's ingenuity, it's been transformed into a weapon for use in the wild. However, Kanami finds the design a bit peculiar.

"Why are there price tags on these wild spring onions?? Reiichi!!"
Goods.10201201_Desc:
The luxury edition of Finale features sparkling diamonds and swirling musical notes on the barrel. With exquisite craftsmanship and an advanced aiming system, it stands as a formidable weapon for suppressing foes.

"Gather your memories and resonate with me!"
Goods.10111004_Desc: The Vibrancy series boasts a colorful and energetic design, making it a favorite among new members of The Scissors.
Goods.31001064_Desc: “I haven't got the munchies. I need a full belly before I can fight!”
Goods.60000057_Desc: “Fay made this glass of milk tea.”
Goods.60000091_Desc: “The Masked Hero would never agree to this!”
Goods.31000192_Desc: “It's a beautiful place. Once everything settles down, let's look for rainbows.”
Goods.10102006_Desc: From the "Camo" series. The firearm features perfect textures to blend seamlessly into natural environments.
Goods.10102111_Desc:
A special Spring Blessings edition of "Rebelflame" features dragon-scale-like armor on the barrel, with a cyan spear running through it, highlighting its heroic spirit.

"Performing martial arts gets you a free meal? Well then, check this out."
Goods.10102108_Desc:
The "Rebelflame" personalized edition boasts a radical design and passionate colors, vowing to light up the night.

"Burn! Flames are the romance of the night!"
Goods.10102110_Desc:
A customized model of the Rebelflame. The red fox and the ruby symbolize the owner's fiery passion. Ming describes it as a flame dancing in the night, glowing before the dawn.

“Let us burn the decay and light up the night!”
Goods.10102109_Desc:
A customized version of the Rebelflame featuring a pale blue paint job with plenty of silver ornaments. Each shot is accompanied by the pleasant ringing of a bell as if it were telling an ancient legend.

【Huh? No need for those clichéd stories. I'll write my own legend.】
Goods.10102107_Desc:
A customized "Rebelflame," blending the sharpness of an eagle with the free spirit of a cowboy, perfectly captures a maverick's bravery and fearlessness.

"No prey seen by this eagle will ever escape."
Goods.10102115_Desc: The Campus Open Day edition of the Rebelflame is adorned with mythical elements from ancient legends, its wielder surging passion and boundless strength.
Goods.31000180_Desc: “Youth, courage, a world to explore. We had everything, our hope undying.”
Goods.10106005_Desc: From the "Illusion" series, this firearm's blue highlights twist and turn, as if melting into the design.
Goods.60000075_Desc: “Take a wrong turn, and you may never be able to return.”
Goods.10101027_Desc: The "Koi" series features a red and black pattern reminiscent of fire and gunpowder, bringing good luck to those who encounter it.
Goods.60000094_Desc: “The limited-edition biting shark toy... is sold out?”
Goods.10105105_Desc:
A customized version of the "Falcon" featuring a detailed map and compass meticulously wrapped in leather. It not only leads her to her nemesis but also guides her in seeking the truth amidst the unknown chaos.

"Observe carefully and think deeply. Where does the path lead?"
Goods.10105107_Desc:
Customized Falcon model. With its elegant design, it tracks every moment precisely, perfectly matching Meredith's meticulous habits.

"Work may be done early, but I'll keep an eye on you."
Goods.10105112_Desc:
A modified version of the Falcon. In Neon City, P.U.S and The Scissors are in a never-ending cat-and-mouse game. The cats have a particular fondness for chasing the mice, which is reflected in the firearm's design.

“In this city, you are the prey.”
Goods.10201103_Desc:
The "Midnight Pact" custom version features an elegant, minimalist design that symbolizes the value of time, reminding the user to take the shot at the perfect moment.

"Time, please slow down just a bit so I may capture their heart."
Goods.10101005_Desc: The Thunderfire series blends contemporary sleekness with retro orange-gray elements.
Goods.10102004_Desc: The "Neon" SCIS-08 custom edition showcases The Scissors' bold rebellion with its edgy color scheme.
Goods.10111006_Desc: The Youthful Camo series, redesigned by a Cloudscape Gallery designer, features vibrant and lively colors, exuding a fresh, youthful vibe.
Goods.10104056_Desc: The "Aviary" series imitates a lively avian ecosystem and subtly includes the user's personal symbol.
Goods.31000187_Desc: “Fragrance is more than just a scent. It signifies a symbol, a story, a memory, the formation of life and soul.”
Goods.10102008_Desc: From the "Arcane Purple" series, this firearm, adorned in bright purple, exudes a sense of mystery.
Goods.60000093_Desc: “Taiyaki, sweet shark - anything will do. Please!”
Goods.10603102_Desc:
A customized "Wildfire" with Eika's favorite space elements and a special flame-simulation device. After all, her dream is to be the coolest, most fired-up courier in the universe.

"Who would have thought that a little spark could light up the entire universe?"
Goods.10603101_Desc:
The custom design of Wildfire draws inspiration from the latest high school fashion trends. Flames shooting from the barrel symbolize youthful energy.

"Woo! Fire it up!"
Goods.10603108_Desc:
A customized stage version of the Wildfire. Its pink-black color scheme and classic plaid pattern bring one back to their school days. Class is over - it's idol time!

“If standing on a stage is what gets me heard, then I'll give it my all and become the most captivating idol the world has ever seen!”
Goods.10603103_Desc:
The "Wildfire" deep sea edition is inspired by Eika's favorite fish, featuring vibrant patterns that shine as brightly as Eika's sparks.

"Fiery Fish in blazing orange, making a grand entrance!"
Goods.10108109_Desc:
Custom Sawtooth model. Lightweight yet powerful, it clears away any unwanted 'trash and debris' like a vacuum.

"Cleaning like a maid, but with bullets."
Goods.10108114_Desc:
A customized version of Sawtooth, featuring camouflage painting by the host of a shooter game. No matter the battlefield, the shark's aggressive nature remains unchanged.

“The shark is hungry. Who will become my prey?”
Goods.10108115_Desc: The Campus Open Day edition of Sawtooth blends various daily stationery into its design. Finish your homework quickly, then relax and enjoy life!
Goods.10108104_Desc:
The Sawtooth concept custom model draws inspiration from ancient hunters. In times past, people feared those nocturnal stalkers, never knowing if they were the next target.

"In complete silence, she delivers an unpredictable fate."
Goods.10108105_Desc:
The custom Sawtooth model features an aerodynamic design and advanced biomechanical components. When firing, it deploys balance fins to optimize shooting precision. According to Fuchsia, looking cool isn’t just a bonus—it’s part of the power.

“Being cool is a form of power, got it?”
Goods.10108107_Desc:
A camo-modified version of Sawtooth. Beyond its camouflage design, it features bionic technology... What's it for? Maybe it even helps repel mosquitoes.

"Thanks to it, I no longer have to worry about getting mosquito bites while in hiding."
Goods.10102055_Desc: The "Lion Dance" series features a festive yellow and white design, depicting Scissors members performing lion dances, embodying spirit and vitality.
Goods.30000118_Desc:
"As the cat took a tumble, the snow leopard made a swift getaway!"

A special memento for Strinova's first anniversary, featuring the winning piece from the Graffiti Creation Contest. Description provided by the creator.
Goods.31002002_Desc:
"Have you ever truly looked at the starry sky?"
"I heard there is a unique star for everyone, waiting alone in the universe, hoping someone would gaze at it."
"If one day you see an unusual light in the sky, that's probably your star winking at you."
"Where is my star? Well... that's a secret."

The girl never stops chasing the night sky.
Through countless nights under the stars, she patiently waits for that one star in the vast galaxy to reveal itself.
One day, the star winks at her.
And the entire night sky changes its colors.
Goods.31002005_Desc:
【“Whether it's going on an adventure or simply sleeping in, one must do what they love the most on a rare off day!”
Having finished a day's work, Kokona changes into comfortable clothes and lays down.

Next to her are stacks of boxes and all kinds of items.
Among them are memorabilia she has not had time to organize and essential tools for her future explorations.
“Come on. Don't just stand there. Help me out.”】
Goods.31002007_Desc:
“It's not that I don't like going out...”
The girl shyly pulls down the brim of her bear hoodie. “It's just that there are too many people outside, and it's noisy... At home, I have Fay, blankets, and endless chilled drinks...”
“I think it's really nice to just stay at home... W-Wouldn't you agree?”
Goods.31002009_Desc:
【“Would you like another taiyaki? Or a sweet shark?”
Sitting on a floor mat, Fuchsia extends her hands to me, offering a piece of taiyaki in one and a sweet shark in the other - a dilemma of sweetness.
Although it is really tempting, I have already had too many sweet snacks today. I swallow as I firmly refuse Fuchsia's offer.
“Suit yourself.” Fuchsia shrugs before taking a huge bite, licking the crumbs from the corner of her mouth. Then, she stretches lazily and sprawls on the floor.
“This is how you should spend your holiday.”】
Goods.31002004_Desc:
【“What flower is this? It's an orchid.”
The floral fragrance of the tea wafts from the cups in front of Lawine and you.
The pale petals unfold in your cup of tea.
You notice that a similar flower is embroidered on her clothes.

“Orchids only bloom in spring, a season far too short in this world.”
As she sips some tea, the girl in front of you smiles, barely perceptible.
For her, this brief respite from all her responsibilities and duties is her spring.】
Goods.31002003_Desc:
【After playing a violin piece, Audrey sits next to you.
“Why do you still look so gloomy when I'm with you?”
“What are you worried about? The test we have to face? Or the inevitable collapse?”

She pours two cups of black tea and places one in front of you.
“Let go of all the troubles. Let us toast to hardship and... this world.”
As the cups touch, producing a crisp sound, the girl smiles confidently.】
Goods.31002008_Desc:
【As an idol, Kanami enjoys spending time on makeup and styles.
Whether it's a natural look or an elegant stage look, Kanami excels at putting them on, skillfully applying any makeup products.
As Kanami finishes her makeup, she draws a cute mark on the mirror with her lipstick.
“Navigator, will you be colored by my hues?”】
Goods.31002001_Desc:
Super gamer Michele has many stylish casual outfits. Of course, our cat lover prefers this cute cat-themed outfit, whether for its comfiness or the adorable kitty colors.

"Cats show their belly when they want to be friendly and feeling safe." The girl says, smiling.

Michele has changed her flashy gamer gear into a cute girl's outfit. Is the cat girl trying to tell you something with that change?
Goods.31001002_Desc:
Having become a frontline investigator, Michele carries with her the will of her father. When a badge number is reactivated, the pitiful criminals better tremble in fear, for the successor of the White Tiger will defeat every single one of them.

“Listen up! I have you surrounded! Surrender now!” Michele once intimidated suspects like this during operations.
And she kept her word, singlehandedly arresting over a dozen suspects.
"I thought I wouldn't see the light of day again. Was she going to devour us like a wild tiger?" a criminal recalls, trembling in fear.
Goods.31000178_Desc: 【The shark in the tank does not realize its freedom is lost, nor does it feel any pain. People pity it for losing the dignity of a predator, but the shark does not care.】
Goods.31001001_Desc:
The royal swordswoman, enchanting as a rose, gazes into the distance.
She sees nothing but carnage and rivers of blood.
The rose-decorated sword pierces an enemy's heart.
The rose is dyed in blood's hue; shadows cast wide their pall.
Her mind, like the breeze, wanders far, unconfined by any wall.
“For you alone, the flowers unveil their bloom; should they fade, what sorrow calls?”
Goods.30000035_Desc: Alone in the forest, one can only hear the sound of falling bamboo leaves.
Goods.30002132_Desc: A breathtaking sight woven into history and art.
Goods.20134_Desc: A mysterious gift from the True Wilderness—its surprises remain unknown until opened.
Goods.22132079_Desc: All injustice will perish in gunfire!
Goods.31000112_Desc: The start of all joys and sorrows.
Goods.30000106_Desc: Two pumpkins? What a sticky situation.
Goods.60000122_Desc: Is this really necessary? Snailie and I promise we’ll behave!
Goods.30002051_Desc: A top-notch water gun can turn the tide in any splash battle!
Goods.30000126_Desc: A small gesture of my goodwill.
Goods.22101069_Desc: Fight with me, and justice will be ours!
Goods.20205103_Desc:
A blinding light, a fleeting illusion—no one can truly capture the beauty of a peacock's feather, nor escape the trickery of the deceiver.




"Just another trick on you."
Goods.30002024_Desc: It's three o'clock! Time for tea!
Goods.30002070_Desc: I won the first half. I'll win the second half, too!
Goods.31000108_Desc: Would you like a cup of tea?
Goods.22115073_Desc: If you want to avoid being charmed, you have to do more than just closing your eyes.
Goods.30000075_Desc: Want to feel forever young? Keep your playful spirit alive!
Goods.22128112_Desc: Do not sink into the darkness!
Goods.22119112_Desc: Don't stop Aika! Is this what it feels like?
Goods.30002008_Desc: After greeting the world, the code created everything.
Goods.20109057_Desc: In sharp contrast to Reiichi's indifferent demeanor, this outfit features patterns of raging flames. Even the coldest of tools need to be driven by heat.
Goods.20101105_Desc:
In stark contrast to her usual authoritative demeanor, Michele becomes a mischievous demon straight out of a fairy tale.
 
Knock, knock. “Open up. It's Investigator Michele from the underworld. I'm here to inspect your snack stash today!”
Donning this outfit, Michele appears happier than usual.
But she's still herself. So, it should be fine, right?
Goods.20119108_Desc:
Eika's exclusive idol costume. The bunny on her mask might be soft and cuddly, but the plaid puffy skirt and tank top give a real rockstar vibe. Just what kind of expression could this idol's mask be hiding?

"My face may be hidden behind a mask, but you can feel my sincerity, right?"
Goods.25006_Name: Exclusive Spring Blessings Selection Gift Box
Goods.31000002_Desc: The anchor of the world. The beacon of the city. A shining tower of string energy.
Goods.22128113_Desc: This world isn't yours to take!
Goods.30002022_Desc: Sweet and homely, like the moonlight.
Goods.20901002_Desc: The question mark displayed on players who join mid-match
Goods.30002023_Desc: Rich and savory, with an enduring aftertaste.
Goods.20101051_Desc:
Michele leapt at the chance to customize her own racing outfit for the Port Euler Jet Ski Grand Prix.

Three, two, one... Go!!!
Goods.31000202_Desc: To boost training efficiency and mission success rates, P.U.S made some changes to the target's design.
Goods.20131058_Desc: In order to study the impact of letters on people's emotions, Yvette dons the courier's outfit, delivering letters to different households to feel their sentiments. However, when looking at the person she wants to send a letter to, Yvette notices her heartbeat suddenly accelerating.
Goods.30002119_Desc: For victory's sake, Michele will endure.
Goods.20133110_Desc:
To blend into the nightlife of Neon City, Meredith dons a streetwear outfit she is not accustomed to. Her headphones help her shut out the city's restlessness and noise, allowing her to stay true to herself.

“I shall guide everyone in this city just as you have guided me.”
Goods.30002046_Desc: Why are pets so obsessed with tissues?
Goods.20133101_Desc:
While working for P.U.S, Meredith once led a team to explore the True Wilderness. She designed this outfit to embody the spirit of adventure.

“If explorers halt due to the fear of the unknown, it will undermine humanity's courage and future.”
Goods.30001012_Desc: My skill is still in cooldown. Maybe we should pull back for now...
Goods.22109073_Name: Active skill: Light screen, blind them!
Goods.22120074_Name: Active Skill: Give it a Try
Goods.22108074_Name: Active Skill: Leave It to Me
Goods.20205102_Desc:
At the recent pool party, Galatea, a DJ under the Urbino music label, turned heads with her stylish ensemble. Attendees recall the moment she tossed her wide-brimmed straw hat into the pool, sparking a friendly scramble among partygoers. Somehow, by evening, the hat had made a surprising return to her head.




"I had a total blast! Count me in for the next one!"
Goods.31000197_Desc: A new pattern appeared on the Urbino street graffiti wall, but it's clearly not made with paint or ink.
Goods.60000124_Desc: It's time to unleash that move!
Goods.20109107_Desc:
There is more to country life than just fields and farms. You need a skilled handyman who is a jack of all trades. Leaky roofs? Short-circuiting appliances? Whatever needs fixing, he has got you covered.

“What? You need me to take care of the P.U.S security squad instead of appliances? Very well. Leave it to me”
Goods.31001076_Desc: I wonder how warm is the sunlight described in the books.
Goods.30000147_Desc: People admire the magician's tricks, mostly because of her unique style.
Goods.20107101_Desc:
It's been said that an explorer who can't fish isn't a true artist.
To visit the remote ecological zones in Strian's countryside for field sketches, Maddelena prepared this outdoor set. She journeys along the river, alternating between sketching and fishing, filling her canvas and fish basket.

"Yes! Got one! Don't run away! Taste my paint bubbles!”
Goods.31001129_Desc: Humans are swept away by tides of energy, yet still pursue the intense pain that life births.
Goods.31000052_Desc: The end of humanity is displayed here in its most unpleasant form.
Goods.31001009_Desc: Today, there will be... a different kind of rain.
Goods.31001004_Desc: Today, we sing! Tomorrow, we fight as one!
Goods.30000148_Desc: Her resume proves that a high school girl can truly do it all.
Goods.20112051_Desc:
Since when
have we been trapped within the confines of towering steel?
The starry sky grows dim,
no longer illuminating the path arrived on.
Goods.31001078_Desc: A melody born from the heart transforms into a song of eternity and hope.
Goods.20130_Desc: From battles to domestic matters, two versatile stewards will fully protect you.
Goods.31000005_Desc: Overflowing from the fragments is the color of the soul.
Goods.22137073_Desc: Listen closely, there will be echoes.
Goods.20109101_Desc:
Reiichi's outfit for eavesdropping missions.
Blending in is part of being a spy, even in a café.

"Today, there will be... a different kind of rain."
Goods.20109102_Desc:
Reiichi's diving gear for his seaside vacation is mainly practical but adorned with a few stylish trinkets. It hints that there's more to him beneath the surface.

"Wow... Even underwater, the corals are stunning."
As Reiichi surfaces from his dive, a subtle smile graces his face. The typically aloof demeanor is replaced by genuine enjoyment of the beach escape.
"Relax. I'm actually quite easygoing."
You feel like you have seen a rare side of Reiichi.
Goods.10304107_Desc:
One of the pieces of equipment Reiichi has modified. Featuring elements of stage lights and performance cars, it comes with special sound effects that satisfy Reiichi's pursuit of power and speed.

"Every street drummer dreams of performing on the grandest stage."
Goods.10303106_Desc:
One of Reiichi's modified weapons. The firearm's design has been altered to reflect a black market aesthetic. It’s an excellent piece of art—the decorations may be fake, but its lethality is real.

"When true is false, false is true; when false is true, true is false."
Goods.20131054_Desc: A cute lab coat decorated with clovers. Hope, faith, love, and fortune —Yvette wishes all these good things to be with you.
Goods.20105053_Desc: An elegant outfit inspired by playing cards. Hearts, Diamonds, Spades, and Clubs... Where's the Ace? Of course, it's Audrey herself!
Goods.30000102_Desc: There's only one word that comes to mind in defeat - destruction!

“I can show you a sight - the seabed dyed red by hot winds.”

“These are the marks of an ancient civilization. If possible, I would like to preserve them in our new buildings.”
Goods.20109056_Desc: This outfit, adorned with crossed swords, resembles an ancient pirate captain's attire. Reiichi does not fear the curse of the sea, for he has long cursed himself.
Goods.20137052_Desc: A performance costume featuring a shooting star pattern. The fluttering starlight resembles Kanami's gorgeous dance moves.

Goods.30000088_Desc: This is how I interpret freedom.
Goods.30002128_Desc: A trace of corrupted data and shattered consciousness.
Goods.10602201_Desc:
One of the many items Bai Mo uses in his livestreams and also the most frequently showcased. Bai Mo uses this uniquely designed weapon for combat, playing music, rapping, and occasionally as a baseball bat to knock sense into lunatics. Fans know it as well as they know the streamer himself.

Just got here. The stream hasn't started yet, has it?!!!
What's on the menu today? I can't wait!
Streaming at 2 in the morning? You've got guts...
LOL at the comment above. You're here, aren't you? Admit it, you're addicted to Bai Mo!
Uh... What's going on? Why is there only a gun here? Where is Bai Mo?
Hey, Look! The title of the stream changed... “Streamer on Leave, Weapon Taking Over?”
???
You've got to be kidding me... Since this is Bai Mo's stream... I guess I'll stick around and see what tricks the gun can pull off...
Goods.22120113_Desc: A warning for the naughty kids.
Goods.60000138_Desc: Time for me to step up!
Goods.30000107_Desc: These kinds of pranks don't faze me at all.
Goods.60000111_Desc: The fragrance is about to fill the battlefield.
Goods.31000038_Desc: Does the blue represent calmness or cruelty?
Goods.31000157_Desc: A kingdom of drinks and a treasure trove of art! I want to... I want to buy everything!
Goods.31000179_Desc: The fragrance is a blessing from the flowers...
