Goods.31000004_Desc: We seek the future, truth, and resistance.
Goods.20132101_Desc:
A black outfit designed for nighttime operations. Originally meant to blend seamlessly into the dark, Ming insisted on adding a touch of dark red, like a quietly burning flame—subtle yet unyielding. She will chase the night and drive it away.

“Go home, kids. The night is my battlefield.”
Goods.22119078_Desc: The reverse fire will never burn your friends, it will only sweep away all your opponents!
Goods.31001020_Desc: Voyaging across the cosmos, wandering through the celestial expanse.
Goods.31000046_Desc: On that day, she realized that it had always been absurd.
Goods.31000198_Desc: That confined, narrow space filled with precise instruments was once called the "Nest."
Goods.22119114_Desc: Then I wish you good health and see you soon!
Goods.30002012_Desc: This tower will stand for eternity. Some call it a beacon. Others, a shackle.
Goods.31000146_Desc: The warm light accompanied me through my lonely childhood.
Goods.30002009_Desc: What time is it? Are you still looking for a safe exit?
Goods.22205110_Desc: Nice effort, but it's time for your curtain call.
Goods.20105108_Desc:
In a ballroom of clinking glasses and swirling gowns, the star of the evening arrives fashionably late. She has shed the fierce spirit of a unicorn, draped in a deep-hued gown. Gracefully, she approaches her chosen dance partner, her skirt fluttering like the wings of a butterfly in the moonlight.

"Forgive me. I took a little extra time to find a dress worthy of our pairing."
Goods.31000118_Desc: Restarting will only take five minutes.
Goods.31000166_Desc: If I were reconstructed differently, will I still be who I am?
Goods.31000131_Desc: The wildfire burns in eternity, and the roses never wither.
Goods.10202103_Desc:
One of the Golden Tree Symphony concert souvenirs, Kokona regards it as one of her most treasured items. With this in hand, Kokona draws attention like a battlefield bard, then elegantly finishes off her foes.

"Maybe making music with you forever wouldn't be so bad?"
Goods.10201106_Desc:
A souvenir from the Golden Tree Symphony, this weapon is inspired by the design of a flute. Does she recall those memories when she wields it?

"H-Has the surprise been conveyed?
Goods.10602107_Desc:
A weapon modified from the instrument Bai Mo used during the Golden Tree Symphony. The tuba's bell is attached to the muzzle. Although it is unclear whether it increases firepower, but it definitely feels more “free.”

"Nice one, my friend! Let's play another song!"
Goods.10104109_Desc:
A prize from Lux Concerta, modified by Reiichi at Lawine's request into a commemorative firearm. Every now and then, she can be found brandishing the firearm and muttering something.

“The setting sun... It's glorious.”
Goods.31001037_Desc: Golden chimes announce the dawn of spring, carrying joy on the breeze.
Goods.20107056_Desc: Trying to figure out how to express feelings through creation, Maddelena takes a part-time job as a courier. She believes that letters are an important medium to convey one's intentions. She has designed her backpack in the shape of a mailbox, inviting the delivery of any precious sentiments.
Goods.31000103_Desc: A fragmented world is not unlike pieces that have come apart.
Goods.30000036_Desc: The moment I closed my eyes, the world became clear.
Goods.20101054_Desc: Michele occasionally puts on this casual outfit and goes hiking in her free time. Be careful not to mistake her for a wildcat in the bamboo forest.
Goods.20123051_Desc:
Besides handling construction, P.U.S Engineering is also responsible for preliminary site investigations and surveys. As for why the target location this time is an ancient castle... well, that is another story.

“All engineering personnel, follow me and number off!”
Goods.22205113_Desc: Apart from magic, I excel in taking your breath away.
Goods.20124206_Desc:
A Superstring Agent codenamed Summer Yellow. She is a member of the Mecha Angels, a secret special unit of P.U.S assembled to combat The Collapse and save the world with the power of love and peace.

—Official Artbook of the popular anime "Mecha Angel GEN"
Goods.31000058_Desc: A Shangri-La one cannot easily return to.
Goods.31000128_Desc: Rainwater flows to the sky from the ground, and we walk above the clouds.
Goods.31000195_Desc: Raindrops sink into the ground, blooming into pure white flowers. You said you need a guide; let me lead you into the violet rain.
Goods.20109053_Desc: In his crisp white attire, Reiichi looks like a young doctor. But in reality, he's only skilled in battlefield emergency care.
Goods.20115106_Desc:
A special host joins the midnight radio station of Neon City. What waves will the butterfly stir up in the dazzling city that never sleeps?

“To cleanse the city of its sins, you will serve as the first cycle of the butterfly effect.”
Goods.30000057_Desc: Beneath the calm lies a hidden storm; humanity's fate remains unknown.
Goods.30002054_Desc: How to deal with noise pollution? Just cover your ears!
Goods.10301108_Desc:
Maddelena's post-concert creation, crafted from newfound inspiration. The loading handle is equipped with strings, ready to strike a chord anytime.

"Did this performance reach your ears?"
Goods.30000101_Desc: The notes have gone mad. They're running away!
Goods.10201058_Desc: By repainting her firearm with inspiration from pop culture, Kanami hopes to attract fans who embrace the aesthetic.
Goods.30000099_Desc: The blend of paint and ice forms a masterpiece that pulls you into its depths.
Goods.30000078_Desc: When gliding, I can barely feel the weight of my own body.
Goods.20137103_Desc:
Kanami's choice of loungewear while on vacation. Few realize that beneath the spotlight, the invincible idol is just an ordinary girl offstage, entitled to enjoy her youthful moments.
Still, as an idol, she's always aware of others' gazes, feeling slightly nervous and thrilled, holding onto the person next to her.

"Ba-dum... Can you hear Kanami's heartbeat?"
Goods.31001007_Desc: Kanami is everyone's idol, but... for now, let me provide you with an exclusive maid café experience.
Goods.20137058_Desc: A special version of Kanami's performance outfit, inspired by the fresh green of four-leaf clovers, designed to pass good luck to fans through her songs.
Goods.31000149_Desc: Winter savory, white champaca, jasmine tea, oatmeal, tuna... The tiny coffee cup is large enough to contain everything.
Goods.22205112_Desc: Just kidding, of course I'd pull the trigger.
Goods.30000083_Desc: Warriors often hit the battlefield in slippers.
Goods.20108052_Desc: The elegant outfit, embroidered with thorns and a sword, symbolizes Nobunaga's turbulent fate and his fearless resolve to confront hardships.
Goods.22205070_Desc: The essence of magic is to deceive artfully.
Goods.31000158_Name: A Day in the Life of a Shark
Goods.31001012_Desc: The crane formation stands ready, but where lingers the friend once known?
Goods.31000083_Desc: A ray of lingering light at dusk.
Goods.31000082_Desc: There are shadows beneath the dawn.
Goods.20133052_Desc: With a striking mix of black and white, which side truly represents her? Meredith is as enigmatic as this outfit.
Goods.20128053_Desc: The black and red hues symbolize the calamity that befell her hometown. Lawine is determined to give it her all to prevent history from repeating itself.
Goods.20132053_Desc: A combat uniform in black and blue, decorated with lightning and eagle emblems. Ming's eyes are as sharp as a hawk's. The outfit highlights her dangerously intimidating aura.

Goods_I18N.10106102_Desc:
This customized version of the Polaris features a striking scarlet rose in full bloom. A sword of knightly protection cuts through the design, telling a tale of beauty and valor.

"As roses mirror people, so do swords.
Fueled by fire, built with steel.
In fierce battles, roses bloom.
The scarlet maiden on the battlefield has long accepted her fate to wither.
Yet in her moments of resting, as she gently caresses the petals,
who will be the one to cherish the garden within her heart?"
Goods_I18N.10106105_Desc:
The Polaris custom model cleverly incorporates medical themes, seemingly implying anti-war ideals...

They save lives not in the hope of praise, nor do they raise their guns to fight.
In front of them lies war, and behind them, peace.
Goods_I18N.10403201_Desc:
A personalized "Champion" model with a pristine barrel, basking in the Grove family's glory and victories. Fervent flames flow through it, symbolizing Lord Grove's indomitable spirit.

To protect her family, the young girl took this gun onto the battlefield. Now, with the newly upgraded weapon in hand, there's composure and determination in her once-furrowed brow. The answers to those questions? As before, seek them through bullets.
Goods_I18N.10403106_Desc:
A customized artistic version of the Champion, adorned with strings of the Guqin, concealing the pinnacle of technology under the classic design.

"In drifting clouds, her garments I find; in blossoms, her visage so fair.
She shines by the balustrade, caressed by the dew-laden air.
Should Jade Mountain's peak hold her not in view.
Then beneath the moon, on gemstone terrace, she'll appear anew."
Goods_I18N.10403104_Desc:
The custom Champion design by Audrey incorporates four unique musical elements. Each string of notes plays the same melody with distinct tones.

"It's a piano, a saxophone, an old vinyl spinning in solitude, capturing the faded memories of the past. I don't know what eras this gun has witnessed, but the moment it fires, the past becomes crystal clear."
Goods_I18N.10304105_Desc:
The custom "Judge" design is ideal for use by the water. The hovercraft-shaped barrel stabilizes the gun, enhancing its performance.

"I've spent too long thinking; it's time to enter the battlefield. There's still a long journey to my objective."
Goods_I18N.10304102_Desc:
The custom Judge concept features a cyberpunk theme with a stylish color palette. It's vibrant yet thought-provoking.

"Neon lights haven't yet faded, and dawn remains uncertain. Though the glory of the past remains, under the clashing of steel, the light of civilization no longer shines."
Goods_I18N.10501104_Desc:
The custom "Beareas" design was hazily sketched by Yvette after a ten-hour sugar crash.

"My hands just... did their thing! Not that I was itching to try the new model or anything."
Goods_I18N.10501111_Desc:
The special medical edition of Beareas features syringe and tube elements, monitoring opponents' heartbeats in real-time.

“Please... open up to me.”
Goods_I18N.10501102_Desc:
The custom Beareas model trades its icy look for a corn-themed design symbolizing life and harvest. It's hard not to find it... a bit appetizing.

"Uh... I know you're hungry, but this isn't for making popcorn..."
Goods_I18N.10501201_Desc:
A special ball edition of Beareas is more compact and lightweight, with added mechanical and gear elements, seamlessly complementing an evening gown.

“I know I'm going to a ball, but I want to bring Fay and my gun... Otherwise, I may feel insecure...”
Goods_I18N.10501202_Desc:

“I know I'm going to a ball, but I want to bring Fay and my gun... Otherwise, I may feel insecure...”

“I know I'm going to a ball, but I want to bring Fay and my gun... Otherwise, I may feel insecure...”
Goods_I18N.10301104_Desc:
The Chroma custom model features a cute water gun design. When it fires, the bullets surge like raging waves.

"The sea can be calm, yet it can also swallow everything. Freedom is similar; pursuing it might bring happiness or destruction."
Goods_I18N.10301102_Desc:
A customized concept model of the Chroma. Inspired by Maddalena's aesthetics, it features her favorite bunny-themed elements.

"The last bunny rides a rocket into the depths of space.
In the vastness of stars, a spark rises into the unknown, marking the end of the glorious bunny civilization."
Goods_I18N.10104113_Desc:
A special underground bar edition of the Shadow Assault, decorated with intricately carved orchids. While most people consider orchids fragile and fragrant, Lawine believes they represent purity and steadfastness.

"If they had a scent, it’d be a cold one."
Goods_I18N.10104106_Desc:
A custom version of Shadow Assault by Quadrant Foundries, cleverly cloaked in P.U.S. blue and white for stealth.

“By shedding illusions, I've become my true self.”
Goods_I18N.10104201_Desc:
A personalized Shadow Assault model, featuring plum blossom motifs and classical elements. It embodies legendary heroism and enduring pride, ready to confront any battle alongside its master.

"As snow falls in the dark, the battlefield is wrapped in a frigid embrace. As comrades fell, a lone general stood firm against the gale and snow. The sudden storm buried everything—including, perhaps, the plum tree.
Yet, as a leader, the general remained unyielding, determined to keep her promise beneath the plum blossom.
Surely, once winter passes, the arrival of spring is not far behind."
Goods_I18N.10104112_Desc:
A camouflage edition of the Shadow Assault, painted by Reiichi to aid stealth in the wilderness. As Lawine and her gun blend in with the earth, ryegrass, wild oats, and countless plants she cannot name sway as she crawls forward.

"Even wild grass has its own charm. Its roots are deep and unyielding."
Goods_I18N.10112102_Desc:
A special pool party edition of the Gambit. Inspired by seashells, the streamlined design features colors of seawater, beaches, and hibiscus, exuding a retro, romantic feeling.

"Before you play the next song, grab a drink at the bar. The night is still young."
Goods_I18N.20112111_Desc:
The realm of martial arts is supreme and pure. For a martial artist to break through in technique, they must first break through their mindset. Fuchsia does not entirely agree, but she secretly hopes to find the answers someday.

“What are martial arts? Why do we practice them? Are the answers really that important? I never cared about these questions, and look how far I've come.”
Goods_I18N.20120051_Desc:
"Each type of coffee bean has a unique aroma." Fragrans places the cup of coffee in front of Eika. "This one has floral and fruity notes. It should be delightful."

"Really? Like, as sweet as fruit?... Ah! It's so sour!!!"
Goods_I18N.10502103_Desc:
A special underground bar edition of Solo. This is obviously the dance of a peacock.

"Peacock tail feathers? No, these are my eyes watching you."
Goods_I18N.10303103_Desc:
A custom Dawn model, perfect for waterside use. The barrel sports a trident for an intimidating look.

"A hunter might be watching us at this very moment... Relax. We're the hunters now."
Goods_I18N.10202106_Desc:
A personalized version of Quasar. Inspired by classic fighter jets, it uses aerodynamics to reduce air resistance when the firearm is in motion—All that's left to figure out now is how to make the gun fly.

“Hmm... Maybe if we stringify the weapon, we can fold it into a paper airplane?”
Goods_I18N.10202102_Desc:
The tactical custom model of Quasar features an atomic-punk design, offering a more comfortable grip and advanced sights, making it ideal for long-range combat.

"That is the world of atomic-punk.
A world of an unrealistic future, a cold utopia, an eternal realm filled with hidden dangers.
It is a place of hope, fantasy, latent cruelty, and... an inevitably tragic end."
Goods_I18N.10202104_Desc:
A custom Quasar model featuring many duck-themed elements, symbolizing the courage to ride waves.

“Mission accomplished! Well done, Kokona!”
“Hurry up, we can still make it for the last song!”
Goods_I18N.10111103_Desc:
A special medical model of Blossom. Features an incense slot and a design that prioritizes usability.

"Can you smell that...? It's the scent of danger."
Goods_I18N.10111102_Desc:
The Blossom desert edition mimics the process of resin-seeping branches through its material and design. Rumor has it, it releases a woody aroma when fired—though, sadly, the target won't have a chance to enjoy it.

"What a pity. There aren't many flowers in the desert."
Goods_I18N.10602101_Desc:
A modified version of the Freedom Reign, crafted by Corridor Artisans. It excels in performance, maneuverability, stability, and design concept, making it a groundbreaking achievement of its era.

"In this unfettered era, freedom is more than just a slogan!
So, don't lock me up!"
Goods_I18N.10602108_Desc:
A special underground bar edition of Freedom Reign. With excessive decorations removed, it is more suitable as an everyday carry.

"Isn't it normal for a bar owner to carry a gun? If danger ever strikes, I need to clear a path to safety for my guests."
Goods_I18N.10101116_Desc: The Campus Open Day edition of the Inspector features a gamified design to promote the Esports Club. It symbolizes Michele's eagerness to share her passion with others.
Goods_I18N.10101105_Desc:
This war edition of the Inspector features a built-in pulse system that can influence real battle outcomes.

"A torrent of gunfire reduces everything to ashes. The will for vengeance roars with unyielding fury. We may not know why wars begin, but their means have nothing to do with justice."
Goods_I18N.10101201_Desc:
The custom Inspector features a white tiger emblem on the dark barrel, glowing with pulsating blue energy. Its wielder, armed with unwavering resolve, charges into the frontlines of justice.

When Michele submitted her modification request, the researchers at Polaris Labs were taken aback, doubting anyone could handle such wild string energy.
“Relax! I’m Michele—harnessing extra string energy is child's play for me!”
Goods_I18N.10101202_Desc:

Goods_I18N.10201102_Desc:
A custom version of Finale, a masterpiece by Corridor Artisans. Painted with brilliantly fluorescent colors, this gun is guaranteed to capture the fans' hearts.

"An idol must be flawless! Every shot should shine brilliantly."
Goods_I18N.10102201_Desc:
A customized model of the Rebelflame, with a thunderbolt-shaped barrel through which electricity surges like a dragon. Its gunshot is as loud as its owner's reputation. Rumor has it that a single shot from this weapon shakes the land like thunder, echoing through the world.

The Scissors' long-standing tradition of welcoming newcomers with stories has evolved into a martial arts showcase, drawing listeners from all over. As the vice-captain and speaker for the assault team, he eagerly shares tales of the captain's exploits.
During one session, while recounting the Wasteland Thunder story for the 50th time, a young listener unexpectedly interrupts, requesting to hear the adventures of the Thunderous Dragon outsmarting criminals.
Just as he prepares to answer, a figure in a battle suit makes a dramatic entrance.
“P-Prepare for combat? Now? What's the mission, Captain?”
“Simply put, it's a battle of wits against criminals!”
After grabbing a bag of chips, the figure waves to the young listener.
“Seeing is believing! Today, you'll witness it firsthand!”
Goods_I18N.10105108_Desc:
The Falcon underground bar model. As guests from afar gracefully arrive, her weapon seems to be watching it all.

"Don't worry. I'm bringing nothing in and taking nothing out. I'm just an observer. Whatever happens here is up to you."
Goods_I18N.10105103_Desc:
The artistic Falcon model comes alive with a bold, modern manga book flair. Its exaggerated design offers a fun twist, making battles feel less intense.

"Hey?!" "Anyone there?!" "Ouch!"
Amidst the gunfire, a manga-style speech bubble pops from the gun.
Suddenly, the once-serious battle isn't so serious anymore.
Goods_I18N.10105102_Desc:
An artistic version of the Falcon, inspired by ancient Earth's Egyptian culture. It channels the civilization's former glory, reawakening a legendary era.

"I had never witnessed such a glorious era.
Gold covered the land. Above the shifting sands, songs of fine wine and honey were sung, a fragment of its endless glory.
But now,
the gilded masks remain elegant, the ancient power still commanding,
a shimmering brilliance from a distant past."
Goods_I18N.10108112_Desc:
The modified Sawtooth has been by Fuchsia's side since childhood. Its cold barrel holds warmth in her heart.

"The path to mastery is not one I walk alone."
Goods_I18N.10108201_Desc:
A customized edition of the Sawtooth, inspired by the skeleton of a shark from old Earth. Equipped with high-performance light elements, recreating the might and solitude of the deep-sea beast.

Strinova's marine ecosystem is broken. Among the ocean's migratory creatures, only the sharks survived. Yet, they have lost their sharpness and strength, and even their sense of smell is fading. Bionic technology was needed to restore their former glory.
When Fuchsia received the modified Sawtooth, she couldn't help but admire the exquisite attention to detail.
“No big deal. It's only a scaled replica of a shark skeleton salvaged from the deep sea.”
The gunsmith remarks with a nonchalant raise of his eyebrow.
“The deep sea? Are there still sharks out there?
“Sadly, there remains just one... My colleague from Bionic Tech mentioned it's been extremely agitated lately."
Sharks are typically solitary and composed, so why this sudden agitation? Fuchsia is eager to uncover the reason behind the shark's unusual behavior.
Goods_I18N.10603105_Desc:
A special medical model of Wildfire. Its bullets are cleverly shaped like pills to appear less threatening. That's the hope, anyway.

"We'll have to add 'gunshot wound' to your medical history."
Goods_I18N.10603106_Desc:
A desert edition of Wildfire, rumored to grant three wishes. Yet, its current owner chooses to reach her goals through her own efforts.

“I wish to defeat all my enemies!”
Goods_I18N.20110105_Desc:
A modified stealth suit inspired by the movie "Phantom Thief," with a sleek, fitted design that matches Bai Mo's taste for style and comfort. However, the added custom bandages and neon glasses kind of defeat the purpose.

Standing in front of a mirror, Bai Mo marvels at his style, but what happens next is unforgettable - “Hmm, cosplaying as the Phantom Thief once in a while isn't half bad. Hey! Let me go! I'm not a thief!”
Goods_I18N.31002006_Desc:
"Today, I have to design a children's book for Astral Sanctuary. As for tomorrow, I promised my neighbor I'd help her design her living room..."
It is another incredibly fulfilling day for the girl who finds joy in helping others. But this time, you notice a hint of weariness in her expression.

"Hold on, Navigator. Don't move!"
"That's it! That's the look!"
The girl exclaims as if she has found the world's rarest treasure.
"Since it's your day off... Navigator, would you model for me?"
The girl approaches the person she trusts the most, sharing her unique warmth, her eyes filled with you and only you.
Goods_I18N.20101101_Desc:
A sporty baseball uniform with playful cat ears and a tail. Donning this outfit, Michele seems impressively agile and sharp.

“Steal! Steal! Steal! Base after base!”
As the audience's thunderous cheering fills the stadium, Michele dashes to second base.
Not only is she a super good gamer, Michele is also great at sports.
Her glistening sweat and bright, sunny smile are the most beautiful sight on the field.
Goods_I18N.20133107_Desc:
A mysterious guest has appeared at the underground bar. No one knows what brought her here or what secrets she holds.

"Are you sure we haven't met before? I can't help but feel like I've asked you this exact question many times before."
Goods_I18N.20108101_Desc:
Nobunaga's exclusive P.U.S. Spec Ops suit blends steel and leather, yet his elegance and calm demeanor remain undiminished.

“Activate remote control and the radar system. Don’t let anything slip past.”
Under Nobunaga's command, a meticulous raid is underway.
However, the operation ended before it even began.
"You must be the target. So, will you surrender? Or will you make me do it?"
Goods_I18N.20137208_Name: Century Idol - Light of the Embers
Goods_I18N.20133053_Desc: A special outfit customized for Meredith with a diamond core symbolizing her sharp, rational, and unwavering resolve.
Goods_I18N.20109103_Desc:
A special combat suit designed for experimental high-energy electromagnetic weapons, with enhanced insulation based on Reiichi's combat experience.
The silent sniper enters the battlefield, channeling intense energy.

“Careful. You might get a shock.”
Goods_I18N.20109105_Desc:
Reiichi's outfit for chess exhibition matches. The fedora and the extra wide lapel add a touch of leisure to the elegance, while the plain glasses provide a unique impression. Together with the dyed hair, one would not recognize him if not a close acquaintance.

“How many times have I told you? The whole point of the Queen's Gambit is to ensure the safety of the central board. Now isn't the time to sweat over a single pawn.”
Goods_I18N.20109003_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit. Even in total darkness, he harbors a glimmer of hope.
Goods_I18N.20109007_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The army green symbolizes his discipline.
Goods_I18N.20109005_Desc:
Reiichi's backup combat suit. Fully functional, it matches the combat capabilities of the original.

“Do not stop fighting. Do not despair.”
Goods_I18N.20109004_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The deep blue hue sings a song of sorrow.
Goods_I18N.20109008_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The light blue lining symbolizes the clear sky in his heart.
Goods_I18N.20109002_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The mysterious purple lining conceals his many burdens.
Goods_I18N.20109009_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The dim green symbolizes his nearly withered yet undying hope.
Goods_I18N.20109010_Desc: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The bright shirt contrasts sharply with the dark coat. He rarely wears it.
Goods_I18N.20109104_Desc:
Reiichi's custom-made outfit is inspired by old-era spacesuits, with some parts faithfully recreated. However, it has been modified for combat readiness in case of emergencies. If not for the conflicts, Reiichi might have pursued a path to the stars, unleashing his creativity across the vast cosmos.

“Pressure is normal, temperature is normal… Hmm, too bad I couldn't replicate the propulsion system.”
Goods_I18N.20109106_Desc:
Reiichi’s special gear for infiltrating the black market emphasizes the mystical allure of Eastern charm and his personal style. The pendant he wears is made from polished scrap, not a genuine antique, but convincing enough to pass as one.

“Heh... You've got a good eye. This is top-notch stuff.”
Goods_I18N.10304104_Desc:
A new model based on the Judge. The hidden Bablo Crystal inside has vastly improved the firearm's performance.

"Why dwell on the past?
Reject the old. Eliminate the stagnant. Destroy the obsolete.
And then... Embrace the new."
Goods_I18N.10104105_Desc:
A cyberpunk-style Shadow Assault model. Its dark blue barrel emits a violet glow, resembling an impending storm with thunder and lightning concealed among the clouds.

"Fear not every moment."
- The Song of Eternity
Goods_I18N.10303101_Desc:
Based on the original Dawn model, this long-range precision weapon is Quadrant Foundries' masterpiece, reigning as the ultimate ace on the battlefield.

"Cloaked in darkness, they await the light, scanning the sky for signs. A lone glimmer cuts through, igniting hope and signaling the arrival of dawn."
Goods_I18N.20128101_Desc:
Inspired by bamboo, this elegant outfit evokes a sense of peace, filled with Lawine's longing for her homeland.

【In her spare time, she often visits her cabin in the bamboo forest.
Through the gaps in the bamboo forest, the sun shines on the dim wooden floor.
Even with you by her side, she remains silent nonetheless.
Quietly, she hands you a fresh cup of tea.】
Goods_I18N.10102105_Desc:
Based on the Rebelflame, Quadrant Foundries introduces a fully updated model. Featuring a silver-gray metal body with a subtle red glow, it radiates a fierce intent.

"Our will is as strong as steel.
Together, we will burn the oppressors to ashes."
Goods_I18N.10102104_Desc:
Based on the Rebelflame, this cutting-edge weapon has been redesigned by Quadrant Foundries, enhancing its overall performance while retaining its original form.

"What catalyst drives scientific progress? It's simple: war."
Goods_I18N.20107104_Desc:
A space-themed white bodysuit featuring stylish mecha rabbit ears, making Maddelena seem less simple and more daring than usual.
 
 “Look! Doesn't the reflection of this outfit resemble moonlight?”
 “I heard that a bunny lived happily on the Moon. Could there be a mecha bunny on Strinova's moon as well?”
 The girl happily dreams of space under the cover of the night.
Goods_I18N.20132206_Desc: Named after the ancient thunderous Loong from the East, this heroic attire features dragon and lightning motifs. It travels with its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.
Goods_I18N.20132207_Desc: Named after the ancient thunderous Loong from the East, this heroic attire features dragon and lightning motifs. It travels with its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.

Goods_I18N.20105206_Desc: A Grove ceremonial gown inspired by the pure white lily, paired with a single-shoulder cape symbolizing the Grove family's pride and honor. This outfit reflects Audrey's initial inexperience and determination when first embracing her family duties.
Goods_I18N.20105207_Desc: A Grove ceremonial gown inspired by the pure white lily, paired with a single-shoulder cape symbolizing the Grove family's pride and honor. This outfit reflects Audrey's initial inexperience and determination when first embracing her family duties.

Goods_I18N.20108103_Desc:
An outfit inspired by cranes, featuring two white cranes painted on a black background as if they are soaring from an inky pine forest, chasing daylight.
Nobunaga always feels nostalgic when he dons this outfit. During the P.U.S Investigator course, he learned ancient Eastern military strategies—"Crane Wing Formation" was once their forte, requiring two partners to flank the enemy from both sides. Even without a partner, Nobunaga has managed to adapt the same tactics for solo combat.

“I have you surrounded. Surrender now.”
Goods_I18N.20131206_Desc: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
Goods_I18N.20131207_Desc: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
Goods_I18N.20131208_Desc: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.

Goods_I18N.20131210_Desc: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
Goods_I18N.20131107_Desc:
Yvette's outfit for the Urbino talent show. The light dress evokes poetic scenery of ancient civilizations. Yvette may not be the best dancer, but that didn't stop her from becoming the star of the show.

“I dance, for I miss you day and night.”
Goods_I18N.20131105_Desc:
Yvette's outfit for the Wilderness Winter Challenge. The elastic warm fleece is suitable for all winter outdoor activities, making it her favorite winter clothing.

“Are you cold? I don't feel cold at all.”
Goods_I18N.20131106_Desc:
The outfit Yvette wears to the Safety Day event. A sharp contrast to her usual cool-toned clothing, this outfit replicates a look from a fairy tale. However, unlike the protagonist in the story, she would not surrender without a fight.

【“Would you accept... my safety apple?”】
Goods_I18N.20131004_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The soft orange makes her look even sweeter and more charming.
Goods_I18N.20131007_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The touching warmth is buried deep in the snow.
Goods_I18N.20131006_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The bright yellow brings a warm feeling to the heart.
Goods_I18N.20131008_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The lush summer leaves can hardly conceal the girl's thoughts.
Goods_I18N.20131005_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The budding green resembles fresh sprouts under the sunlight.
Goods_I18N.20131003_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. Beneath her cold exterior, there lies a fiery heart.
Goods_I18N.20131002_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The vibrant purple makes her as graceful as a slender lavender.
Goods_I18N.20131102_Desc:
Yvette's beach outfit radiates youthful energy and a refreshing vibe, grabbing everyone's attention, much like a cute panda.

"Pandas are bears too," Yvette giggles, touching her ears. "At least Fei won’t feel alone at the summer music fest with a fellow bear around."
Goods_I18N.20131101_Desc:
Yvette's outfit for outdoor excursions. The simple, unembellished style reflects her pure heart. Of course, she occasionally shows her cute, girlish side.

【“Eh? You would like to have lunch with us? But I can't find Fay...”
“How about you and I have lunch in secret this time...”
Can Yvette really not find Fay? Or...
She is the only one who can give you the answer to that question.】
Goods_I18N.20205052_Desc:
It's rumored that Galatea designed this dress after gazing at the night sky for half an hour. Others say inspiration struck after she visited the Cloudscape Gallery's jewelry exhibition. Galatea neither confirms nor denies these rumors.


"Stars and gemstones are quite similar, aren't they?"
Goods_I18N.20110102_Desc:
Rumor has it that there is a highly skilled young man who shows up in the auto shop from time to time. No matter what the malfunction is or the age of a race car, as long as he repairs and tunes it, the vehicle's performance will be enhanced. Everyone praises his repair skills, but few inquire about his identity - this is exactly what he aims to achieve.

"Check out the repair. There's nothing my wrench can't fix."
"However, the parts are severely worn. You gotta take care of your car, buddy."
"Feel like you've seen me before? Well, it's a large city. Perhaps you have; perhaps you haven't. Don't overthink it."
Goods_I18N.20133055_Desc: An elegant outfit symbolizing scales of justice. A noble adjudicator shall deliver judgments for the world.
Goods_I18N.20108107_Desc:
Nobunaga's outfit for chess exhibition matches. The black and white checkered pattern and smooth lines exude a sense of fashion and elegance, making it Nobunaga's perfect “armor” for important occasions. Nobunaga used to be weary of the Bureau of Investigation's participation in such events, but...

“I thought you and I were just like these two pieces, never truly able to touch one another.”
Goods_I18N.20108104_Desc:
Nobunaga's racing suit for the Winter Wilderness Challenges offers great thermal insulation. The snow goggles and snug fit aid in securing the lead during snow races.

“Nobunaga! Again! That's his third Winter Wilderness title!”
Goods_I18N.20108008_Desc: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The light fades, leaving only ashes.
Goods_I18N.20108004_Desc: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, surging with emotions like waves rolling in.
Goods_I18N.20108007_Desc: Nobunaga's spare work outfit—the rust does not hide his lofty ambition.
Goods_I18N.20108003_Desc: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, symbolizing his will to break through obstacles like flying sparks.
Goods_I18N.20108005_Desc: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The flashing lightning represents his courage and wisdom.
Goods_I18N.20108006_Desc: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The dazzling amethyst represents his elegance and pride.
Goods_I18N.20108002_Desc: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, as fearless as a clear sky after rain.
Goods_I18N.20108056_Desc: Nobunaga's custom uniform features the rich green of a bamboo forest, perfectly highlighting the wearer's calm demeanor.
Goods_I18N.20108108_Desc:
Nobunaga dons this outfit when he is in charge of security at theater events. Inspired by the Mediterranean culture of old Earth, the design features a deep, understated style, conveying a sense of freedom and mystery.

“Toiling in the darkness, serving the light - Was it the same for that person?”
Goods_I18N.20115103_Desc:
Wearing a beautiful dress, Flavia is as glamorous as a dazzling peacock, capturing the spotlight on the dance floor.

"Don't stress about it. Leave it to me. As your dance partner, I'll take care of you."
Goods_I18N.20146055_Desc: The elegant purple dress accentuates Celestia's mysterious elegance. It suits her well, but she never speaks of the story behind it.
Goods_I18N.20205007_Desc: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by top-grade cymophane.
Goods_I18N.20205002_Desc: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by the colors of a peacock's eye.
Goods_I18N.20205005_Desc: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by a gloomy dusk with impending snow.
Goods_I18N.20205006_Desc: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by ripe grapes in the vineyard.
Goods_I18N.20205004_Desc: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by an upper-class banquet.
Goods_I18N.20205003_Desc: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by a lush bamboo forest.
Goods_I18N.20146206_Desc: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a sharp and bold spirit.
Goods_I18N.20146207_Desc: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a sharp and bold spirit.

Goods_I18N.20146210_Desc: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a sharp and bold spirit.
Goods_I18N.10403112_Desc:
Spring Blessings defending champion model. A dragon soars through the clouds, symbolizing Audrey's dreams for her future.

【"In this new year, perhaps I'll give Urbino a little shock."】
Goods_I18N.20110052_Desc: A combat hoodie with a cola print, perfectly matching Bai Mo's vibe. Wearing this outfit, Bai Mo bursts with energy and passion, just like a shaken can of cola.
Goods_I18N.30002141_Desc: First place winner: A brilliant creation by Navigator@pewchii_.
Goods_I18N.20137101_Desc:
Kanami wears this stunning gown only for formal events. It blends youthful romance with mature elegance, highlighting her unique brilliance.

"This is the dress I wore when I first took the stage as an idol. I will never forget how I felt back then. I must meet everyone's expectations to feel that kind of emotion again."
Goods_I18N.60000105_Desc: Oh no, where's the tomato in my tomato scramble?
Goods_I18N.20105101_Desc:
The maid outfit worn by the manager of Café Reminiscence has been tailored to Audrey's liking. Despite the outfit, Audrey's elite leadership aura remains unmistakable.

"Go ahead, take a good look! B-But make sure to try our new coffee... please?"
Goods_I18N.20120053_Desc:
During The Scissors' castle exploration, Fragrans, to everyone's surprise, was the fastest to emerge, even with a blindfold on.
"Bats use sound; I use scent... The air outside the castle is indeed much fresher."
Goods_I18N.20120054_Desc:
After an aquarium trip with her friends, Fragrans made herself a jellyfish-themed outfit.
“Jellyfish... they strike me as light blue flowers blooming on the seabed.”
Goods_I18N.20105056_Desc:
Walls, turrets, gates—when it comes to classic castle design, that's Audrey's expertise. To assess this property's potential, Audrey donned a brand-new outfit.

"I'm just in need of a horror-themed mansion."
Goods_I18N.20105010_Desc: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Luxurious yet understated, the outfit showcases her resilient will.
Goods_I18N.20105009_Desc: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her gaze reaches the vast ocean.
Goods_I18N.20105008_Desc: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her gaze reaches the vast ocean.
Goods_I18N.20105006_Desc: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Secrets flow beneath the simple attire.
Goods_I18N.20105002_Desc: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her unwavering will stands firm like a green mountain.
Goods_I18N.20105007_Desc: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. A verdant meadow lies within her dreams.
Goods_I18N.20105005_Desc: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. True elegance needs no lavish adornment.
Goods_I18N.20105109_Desc:
Audrey's outfit for the Spring Blessings family banquet features a dress inspired by the sunset glow and a moonlit shawl, blending graceful elegance with youthful allure.

"Please, have a seat. You are an honored guest at the Grove family banquet."
Goods_I18N.20105105_Desc:
The outfit Audrey wears while exploring the True Wilderness. Lightweight and comfortable, the outfit lets air through and helps cool the body. The camera in the bag captures visions of the future.

"I must personally inspect the new development areas in collaboration with P.U.S. These photos will witness the rise of a new metropolis."
Goods_I18N.20105110_Desc:
Audrey's custom work outfit. Serious yet fashionable, it is her go-to choice for important occasions. The design has since become popular among office ladies of Neutroville.

“I'm in a hurry - I have another decision to make.”
Goods_I18N.30002011_Desc: If thought itself is just matter, how can we prove that we are conscious at all?
Goods_I18N.20110053_Desc: A combat uniform in the style of a space suit, not only reflecting Bai Mo's unique personality but also possessing an elegant sense of fantasy.
Goods_I18N.10304106_Desc:
A special edition "Judge" model featuring a paint job awarded to Nobunaga for winning the Wilderness Winter Challenge for the second time. The design mirrors the snowmobile he rode during the race. Whenever Nobunaga holds it, he remembers the joy of racing through the snowfields.

"Heh... Let's ride, my friend."
Goods_I18N.20205054_Desc:
Although Galatea is used to being in noisy environments, she occasionally retreats to the peaceful mountains and forests.

“I listen to human voices all the time. Sometimes, I just want to hear what nature has to say.”
Goods_I18N.60000106_Desc: Oh great, my tomato scramble is missing the eggs...
Goods_I18N.10501107_Desc:
A special version of the Beareas with a plush shoulder pad and a comfy grip that greatly reduces recoil. Strangely, it also tends to make users feel sleepy...

"Oh, no... I-I'm going to fall asleep..."
Goods_I18N.20128104_Desc:
Beneath the flamboyant combat uniform lies Lawine's calm and rational heart. In the shadows, she strikes with lethal precision.

Under the night sky, a shadow races through the city.
No one sees her. No one hears her.
“You let your guard down... playing right into my hands.”
Lawine, the enforcer of The Scissors, strikes again against those who oppose her faith.
Goods_I18N.20124103_Desc:
The outfit Kokona wears as a guide at the Space Center features radiation protection, making it ideal for space engineers.

"Astronaut Kokona out of the spacecraft and reporting for duty. I'm feeling great!"
Goods_I18N.20124053_Desc: A modified version of Kokona's combat uniform, incorporating the stripes of a white tiger into the design. Donning this outfit, she appears exceptionally valiant and undeniably dangerous.
Goods_I18N.20124105_Desc:
The outfit Kokona wears to mountain biking competitions in the fall. Light and durable, it offers excellent breathability and wind resistance reduction and comes equipped with a sufficient tool kit. Rumor has it that Kokona won the championship wearing this outfit.

"Are you surprised? Great power lies in my body!"
Goods_I18N.20124106_Desc:
The formal dress Kokona prepared for the Golden Tree Symphony concert, featuring a cute little hat that showcases her playfulness and eagerness for the challenge.

"Care to try a piano duet? How can a conductor excel without understanding the music?"
Goods_I18N.20124104_Desc:
A piece of outdoor gear modified by Kokona. Originally intended for exploration, it has been transformed into a ceremonial outfit suitable for outings and picnics. Speaking of which, the strawberries on the outfit seem to be edible.

“If you're interested, feel free to have a bite.”
Goods_I18N.20124108_Desc: The most romanticized explorer image in Xinxia's mind comes from the popular action-adventure movie series. Xinxia visited old clothing design stores and customized this classic outfit piece by piece. ["Treasures! There are treasures everywhere! Hehe~ But compared to the treasures, I prefer the adventures I encountered along the way!"]
Goods_I18N.20124002_Desc: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform. The light pink lifts the spirits.
Goods_I18N.20124005_Desc: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in light purple, resembling the twilight.
Goods_I18N.20124007_Desc: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in light green, making one feel melancholic.
Goods_I18N.20124003_Desc: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform. The mix of gray and blue resembles the sky over the mountains.
Goods_I18N.20124004_Desc: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in azure, resembling the autumn sky.
Goods_I18N.20124008_Desc: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in red and white, suitable for medical operations.
Goods_I18N.20124006_Desc: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in green camouflage, perfect for stealth operations.
Goods_I18N.30002141_Name: Damn it... I should not have lost!
Goods_I18N.20131108_Desc:
Goggles, tactical helmet, combat suit... At the Navigator's invitation, Yvette thoroughly equipped herself with all the gear a tactical analyst needs. Although the battlefield is nothing like the lab, Yvette utilizes her analytical and research skills to support her allies on the front lines.

"T-Tactical Analyst Yvette reporting for duty..."
Her shy, soft voice trembles slightly.
"Um... Navigator, did the combat data I collected help anyone?”
Those gentle, familiar hands softly brush her forehead.
The nervous, blushing girl gradually calms down. The Navigator's reassurance seems to be a magical remedy, empowering her to face anything with courage and resolve.
Goods_I18N.20128106_Desc:
The outfit Lawine wears to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. Its rebellious design makes her stand out in the classical setting, drawing all eyes.

"Music does calm the heart. I don't mind joining you."
Goods_I18N.20128109_Desc:
Lawine's maid outfit for working undercover at the café. The red and black tones exude a sense of profound elegance, while the twin daggers hidden behind her add a dangerous touch of beauty.

"The daggers? They're for your protection. Please relax, my dear guest..."
Goods_I18N.20128003_Desc: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The cold blue evokes a chill in the heart.
Goods_I18N.20128007_Desc: Lawine's spare combat uniform in blue, resembling the silent cold night.
Goods_I18N.20128004_Desc: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The forest green hem looks particularly sleek and neat.
Goods_I18N.20128002_Desc: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The dazzling gold dust flows like fine sand in the wind.
Goods_I18N.20128008_Desc: Lawine's spare combat uniform in blue, making her as sharp as thunder on a rainy night.
Goods_I18N.20128005_Desc: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The beautiful purple showcases her graceful figure.
Goods_I18N.20128006_Desc: Lawine's spare combat uniform in green, resembling grass fluttering in the wind.
Goods_I18N.20128201_Desc: The loungewear Lawine dons at home. Only her true friends have a chance to see her in this outfit.
Goods_I18N.20158_Desc: No need to worry about being a novice. A mix of energy and calm can resolve any issue.
Goods_I18N.20132055_Desc: Ming's racing outfit incorporates her favorite racing elements. Behind wheels, she turns into a blue whirlwind, becoming the swiftest presence on the track.
Goods_I18N.20132107_Desc:
Ming's outfit for a night out during Spring Blessings. The bold red dress makes her look spirited and valiant, capturing a heroine's flair.

"No, I'm not here to uphold justice, just to savor some good food and drinks!"
Goods_I18N.20146106_Desc:
Celestia's outfit for meteor shower nights combines warmth with style. Its thicker material keeps her cozy while the cute design highlights her simple beauty under the starry sky.

“The beauty of a meteor lies in its fleeting light. Like meteors, we cross the night sky and find each other.”
Goods_I18N.20146105_Desc:
The outfit Celestia prepared for the amusement park event. The refreshing denim jacket exudes a sense of excitement while the hat perfectly covers her shy eyes when pulled down...

“There are still many attractions left... um, you don't have to look at me, you know?”
Goods_I18N.20146109_Desc:
Celestia's outfit for hosting the Spring Blessings Eve event at Astral Sanctuary. The decorated skirt can't conceal her wish to explore the night with the one she holds most dear.

"Would you go for a walk with me after the event? Just the two of us."
Goods_I18N.20146201_Desc: Celestia only puts on this loungewear when resting. Only those closest to her have a chance to see her in this outfit.
Goods_I18N.20146104_Desc:
An experimental spacesuit Celestia wears at the Space Center. Made from various polymer materials, the outfit offers excellent insulation and impact resistance. Originally designed for interstellar travel, it now resides in the museum for visitors to experience.

“Before stepping into space, we ventured into the fog of dimensions. That's what the tag says.”
Goods_I18N.20146006_Desc: Astierred's spare work uniform. The leaf-like skirt subtly reveals patterns of stars.
Goods_I18N.20146007_Desc: Celestia's spare work uniform. The deep blue dress gives her an air of mystery.
Goods_I18N.20146011_Desc: Celestia's spare work uniform in elegant purple, suitable for formal occasions.
Goods_I18N.20146009_Desc: Celestia's spare work uniform in navy blue, highlighting her grace.
Goods_I18N.20146010_Desc: Celestia's spare work uniform in warm orange, reminiscent of lights and delicacies.
Goods_I18N.20146005_Desc: Celestia's spare work uniform in lime green, accentuating her charm.
Goods_I18N.20146008_Desc: Celestia's spare work uniform in purple, flowing like a drifting cloud.
Goods_I18N.20120052_Desc:
Spring is Fragrans' favorite season, full of vitality and renewal.
"Let's make this year's first fragrance a sakura scent."
Goods_I18N.20205055_Desc:
Who cast the old castle into darkness, and who turned that darkness into a new stage?

“A magician knows more tricks than making doves appear out of thin air. Bats could also do the trick.”
Goods_I18N.20112054_Desc: The crane ascends into the blue sky, taking hopes and dreams with it.
Goods_I18N.20112101_Desc:
The outfit is inspired by hunters who once roamed the forests at night. Its bizarre design embodies the tension of the era.

“Come on, Fuchsia. You're the only one left! The Nightstalker suits you perfectly!”
“This outfit is not suitable for carrying out missions.”
“Live a little, would you? Come on, it's photo time!”
“Uh... fine.”

Hearing her companions' teasing, Fuchsia remains silent for a while. She knows it's all in fun and that no matter how her outfit changes, her past remains unchanged.
Yet for some reason, she feels a long-lost sense of warmth in her heart.
Goods_I18N.20133051_Desc: An outfit prepared by Meredith for aquatic field research. She moves cautiously under the cover of the waves.
Goods_I18N.20133106_Desc:
Meredith puts on this outfit when performing with her band. The bold design reflects her understanding of the spirit of rock n' roll. A composed scholar, Meredith also longs for freedom without restraints.

“Rock n' roll embodies freedom and exploration, aligning perfectly with the spirit of science.”
Goods_I18N.10102106_Desc:
A creative water gun model inspired by the Rebelflame. Don't mistake it for a toy—Ming shows no mercy.

"Let us sing, my friends. For freedom. For the motherland. For our ideals."
Goods_I18N.20124102_Desc:
Inspired by flight suits from old movies, this outfit reflects Kokona's unfulfilled dreams. Ever curious, she has always yearned for the sky and distant lands, eager to explore the unknown.

“Let's see. This is the center stick, and that is the altimeter... Relax. I've read the manual dozens of times. Remember where to pull to activate the ejection seat. We're taking off!”
Goods_I18N.20101206_Desc: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
Goods_I18N.20101207_Desc: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
Goods_I18N.20101208_Desc: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
Goods_I18N.20101209_Desc: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
Goods_I18N.20101210_Desc: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
Goods_I18N.10112101_Desc:
A special Magicians' Awards edition of the Gambit. Don't be fooled by the alluring red feathers; her magic is as dazzling as it is deadly.

“Next up, I'll make bullets disappear... Just kidding. There's no escape for you now.”
Goods_I18N.300003_Desc:
Opening each chest gives you a chance to win random rewards, using up reward attempts. Once all attempts for an item are exhausted, it won't appear again. The more you open, the higher the chance for unclaimed rewards, with a guarantee of receiving all rewards by the 30th try.
Begin your adventure into the world of aromas.
Goods_I18N.20159_Desc:
Opening each chest gives you a chance to win random rewards, using up reward attempts. Once all attempts for an item are exhausted, it won't appear again. The more you open, the higher the chance for unclaimed rewards, with a guarantee of receiving all rewards by the 30th try.
Meet the gentle perfumer and indulge in rich fragrances.
Goods_I18N.20107103_Desc:
The beautiful seaside inspires the young painter. The refreshing sailor suit makes her even more charming.

【The azure sea, the white waves, and the singing crowd; Maddelena is intoxicated by the beautiful scene.
Taking out the paintbrush she carries with her at all times, she expresses her emotions onto the canvas.
After a while, a sudden idea comes to her:
Deep in everyone's heart, there is an ocean unique to them.】
Goods_I18N.20137053_Desc: This elegant mint-colored outfit makes Kanami appear even more pure and charming, adding a touch of coolness to the passionate summer concert.
Goods_I18N.20115104_Desc:
Wearing a vibrant and elegant restaurant uniform, Flavia seamlessly blends into a street-side café. Under the beautiful sunset, Flavia and the guests savor Iberian delicacies as much as the romantic atmosphere.

"At sunset, I serve them jamón ibérico and all its rich flavors."
Goods_I18N.20107105_Desc:
Maddelena's outfit for flash mob performances. Ever since the Golden Tree Symphony event, her passion for music has awakened, though not for classical tunes...

"Melodies exist only for a moment before vanishing. Don't you find it romantic?"
Goods_I18N.20107110_Desc:
Maddelena prepared this outfit for the amusement park event. Its cute design blends seamlessly with the park's cartoon characters.

【“I'm only dressed like this to better understand children's feelings... After all, I get commissioned to create children's picture books from time to time.”】
Goods_I18N.20107106_Desc:
The outfit Maddelena wears to the Golden Tree Symphony concert, designed by herself. The small hat sometimes helps her hide her shy face.

"I can't afford to embarrass myself here!"
Goods_I18N.20107007_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The interwoven silver and red make her stand out from the crowd.
Goods_I18N.20107010_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit, incredibly clear like a lake in winter.
Goods_I18N.20107011_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit, modest and serene like leaves of fall.
Goods_I18N.20107002_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The bright green symbolizes vitality and vigor.
Goods_I18N.20107004_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The deep indigo symbolizes creativity and intuition.
Goods_I18N.20107003_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The tender pink resembles butterflies and blooming flowers.
Goods_I18N.20107009_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The interwoven blue and green resemble ripples in a lake.
Goods_I18N.20107008_Desc: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The noble purple makes her seem like a flower swaying in the wind.
Goods_I18N.20107102_Desc:
Wearing this outfit, Maddelena appears sweet and energetic, like a dazzling neon light weaving through the streets. As an artist, she occasionally indulges in the extraordinary.

"Hiya! Good evening! Woo!"
With a face full of excitement, she glides by on her roller skates.
Her elegant figure and the flickering rainbow lights dazzle onlookers.
Whatever this whimsical girl does, it is always in the name of "gathering inspiration."
Goods_I18N.20107108_Desc:
Maddelena designed this vibrant classic dress after doing a lot of research. When she dances, tambourines ring with her every move, reflecting the romantic charm of a bygone era.

“I initially just needed some inspiration, but now I've completely fallen in love with the dance!”
Goods_I18N.20107201_Desc: Loungewear designed by Maddelena, inspired by the green fields and orange fruit. Coming up with fun designs at home with you is the precious time she cherishes the most.
Goods_I18N.20120005_Desc: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat. Its deep rose color highlights her mature elegance.
Goods_I18N.20120002_Desc: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, in a refreshing green reminiscent of freshly sprouted tea leaves.
Goods_I18N.20120006_Desc: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, with tones reminiscent of autumn leaves, foreshadowing winter's arrival.
Goods_I18N.20120004_Desc: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat. The violet blooms in the night, as intoxicating as fine wine.
Goods_I18N.20120007_Desc: An alternative color scheme for Fragrans' lab coat, where blue symbolizes not just melancholy, but also inner peace.
Goods_I18N.20120003_Desc: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, featuring a purity akin to refined essence.
Goods_I18N.20120102_Desc:
Fragrans' medical attire, whether she's accustomed to it or not, serves the same purpose: to heal and soothe.

"It's important for you to rest well."
Goods_I18N.32000030_Desc:
A spectacular case designed by Cloudscape Gallery, a subsidiary of Urbino. The design is inspired by crystal fissures in the Ocarnus Dungeon. The crystal mutation symbolizes an impending disaster. Who is there to turn the tide and save the day?

Season 3 Advanced Warrant PLUS Exclusive

Medal Slots: 3
Goods_I18N.32000028_Desc:
A reflective case designed by Cloudscape Gallery, a subsidiary of Urbino. The design is inspired by memories provided by Yugiri. The snail that drifts between abstraction and representation is always exploring the world and itself.

Season 2 Advanced Warrant PLUS Exclusive

Medal Slots: 3
Goods_I18N.32000024_Desc:
A fragrant case designed by Cloudburst Museum, a subsidiary of Urbino. Inspired by the Fragrans Immersion series, its unique aroma wraps around the body like an invisible ribbon.

Season 1 Advanced Warrant PLUS Exclusive

Medal Slots: 3
Goods_I18N.32000033_Desc:
A conceptual case designed by Urbino’s Cloudscape Gallery. It draws inspiration from a captivating battle scene featuring Mara. Like a shadowy specter, Mara strikes her prey with claws as swift as lightning, ensnaring prey in an inescapable grasp.

Season 3 Advanced Warrant PLUS Exclusive

Medal Slots: 3
Goods_I18N.10111052_Desc: Manufactured by Quadrant Foundries, the Summer Beach series of firearms perfectly blends various beach elements onto the barrel. In tranquil moments, you might even hear the echo of the waves.
Goods_I18N.20110101_Desc:
A baker's uniform designed by Bai Mo, featuring an avant-garde design and comfortable lining. However, he has rarely had the chance to put it on.

【“Look. This blueberry milk bread is golden on the outside with a soft and fluffy texture and a sweet and sour taste. I baked it myself. ”
Bai Mo once worked undercover in one of his bakeries for several days.
Seeing people enjoy the bread he has baked fills his heart with joy.
To this day, that remains one of his fondest memories.】
Goods_I18N.20110056_Desc: Bai Mo's barista outfit is rumored to be from when he secretly worked at a cafe in Urbino for half a month.
Goods_I18N.20110007_Desc: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit. He has battled waves and dived into the depths of the sea.
Goods_I18N.20110002_Desc: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit makes him look like a young boy about to enjoy a picnic.
Goods_I18N.20110005_Desc: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, resembling the vast green fields in his childhood dreams.
Goods_I18N.20110006_Desc: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, resembling the autumn leaves that dance in the wind of freedom.
Goods_I18N.20110004_Desc: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, bold yet romantic and elegant.
Goods_I18N.20110008_Desc: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit. In the sea of sand, the voice of freedom will stir a new storm.
Goods_I18N.20110003_Desc: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit in elegant lake blue reflects his unrestrained spirit.
Goods_I18N.20110106_Desc:
A performance suit customized by the Bai Group. Wearing it, Bai Mo exudes a calm and dignified aura—until he starts talking...

"My pitch isn't half bad, right?"
Goods_I18N.20157_Desc: The mysterious evening invitation arrives. Who will join you—the hunter in the night or the dancer in the candlelight?
Goods_I18N.10111001_Desc: Relentless firepower to dominate the battlefield, offering an excellent balance of accuracy and firing rate. Equipped with a 1.25x scope.
Goods_I18N.20101112_Desc:
Michele's outfit for the Spring Blessings fireworks celebration. The vibrant dress captures the festive spirit, and the jingling gold bells announce the arrival of spring.

"Ding-dong! What are you waiting for? The fireworks celebration is about to start!"
Goods_I18N.20101011_Desc: Michele's spare investigator uniform in an industrial style, reliable and practical.
Goods_I18N.20101008_Desc: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a muted khaki, simple and durable.
Goods_I18N.20101009_Desc: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a bright, spritely pink.
Goods_I18N.20101012_Desc: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a calm, subdued blue-gray.
Goods_I18N.20101006_Desc: Michele's investigator uniform in a minty fresh blue.
Goods_I18N.20101007_Desc: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a lively spring green.
Goods_I18N.20101010_Desc: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a mysterious, ethereal purple.
Goods_I18N.20101110_Desc:
Michele's Campus Open Day esports outfit includes a compact backpack that opens into an Esports Club game console. Cute accessories highlight her identity as a passionate gamer.

"Gaming and studying aren't at odds—a super gamer puts 100% passion into both!"
Goods_I18N.20132104_Desc:
A rugged cowboy outfit that embodies a maverick's longing for freedom and adventure. Thinking of this, Ming whistles cheerfully.

“Let's pull off a big score!”
Goods_I18N.20115102_Desc:
A luxurious and elegant maid outfit inspired by butterflies. Donning this enhancing outfit, Flavia mysteriously appears in the café. She seems to have obtained important intel about someone.

“Are you looking to trade information? You'll have to defeat me first.”
Goods_I18N.20124055_Desc: An elegant outfit with snowflake and pine tree patterns becomes even more graceful on Kokona. She alone may understand its true significance.
Goods_I18N.20112102_Desc:
Fuchsia's assassination suit for urban combat, combining practicality and mobility with her personal aesthetics. The shark-fin aerodynamic panels further aid in gliding. Donning this outfit, she becomes a shadow darting between buildings, speaking via the sound of gunfire.

【“Bang! A quick and clean end. That's all.”】
Goods_I18N.20112105_Desc:
A maid outfit designed by Fuchsia, reflecting her understanding of maid duties. It is lightweight and tight-fitting, allowing Fuchsia to display her powerful and efficient combat abilities.

"If you don't want to end up on the declutter list... stay out of the way."
Goods_I18N.20112103_Desc:
Fuchsia's outfit during the first Champion of Relaxation competition. Lightweight, comfortable, and cool, the outfit features brown and green tones that allow her to blend into her surroundings as she treks through rivers and mountains.

“Thanks to my outfit, I could sneak up on animals without being noticed... An interesting experience.”
Goods_I18N.20112104_Desc:
The outfit Fuchsia wore to the festival parade. Originally intended to help her keep a low profile while protecting VIPs, its attention-grabbing design unexpectedly made her the star of the parade.

“What a noisy bunch.”
Goods_I18N.20112106_Desc:
Fuchsia wears this outfit when she works as a bartender in the underground bar. Watching her expert moves, one can't help but ask,

"Why are you so skilled at this?!"

"It's nothing out of the ordinary. I just like to be the best in every field, bartending included. Would you like a drink?"
Goods_I18N.20112206_Desc: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
Goods_I18N.20112207_Desc: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
Goods_I18N.20112208_Desc: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
Goods_I18N.20112209_Desc: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
Goods_I18N.20112210_Desc: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
Goods_I18N.20112007_Desc: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. May all who walk upon this earth be free.
Goods_I18N.20112006_Desc: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. Aren't humans just another type of fish?
Goods_I18N.20112003_Desc: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. The eye-catching red signifies the heat of the muzzle.
Goods_I18N.20112002_Desc: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform, cold as ice, sharp as a killer.
Goods_I18N.20112005_Desc: Fuchsia's spare combat suit: Purple isn't just mysterious, it can also be deadly.
Goods_I18N.20112008_Desc: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. Stealth is not just about concealing one's presence.
Goods_I18N.20112004_Desc: Fuchsia's spare combat suit, designed for twilight—the witching hour, when demons emerge, ready to devour.
Goods_I18N.20112057_Desc: Fuchsia's athletic outfit features a striking mix of pink shark and teal iceberg, creating a unique visual impact.
Goods_I18N.20119101_Desc:
Eika’s self-styled outdoor gear showcases bold and edgy fashion that embodies the wild spirit of a high school girl. Exactly where she "lets loose" after school is her little secret.

“The day of a high school student only begins after school!”
Goods_I18N.20119055_Desc: Eika's uniform for her farm job. Based on a basic work uniform, it blends elements of meadow green and earthy tones. Her cheerful presence is a hit at the farm, even attracting the farm's robotic herding dog. Are they playing a friendly game... or is Eika simply afraid of dogs?
Goods_I18N.20119052_Desc: Eika's outfit for her café job, inspired by the "Manager's Daily Coffee Pick." As both a barista and model, Eika often prepares coffee for customers herself. Her sales figures are said to be impressive.
Goods_I18N.20119102_Desc:
Eika put together this outfit for her side job at the planetarium, blending elements from sci-fi movies with a girl's dreamy imagination of the stars. While working inside the planetarium, Eika realizes that being a galactic courier could be the coolest job ever.

"If our family restaurant spanned the universe, would I have to deliver food among planets?"
Goods_I18N.20119053_Desc: Eika's fast food uniform. This unique combo of a school and staff attire, helps her look the part and complements her youthful style. Rumor is that the dripping red feature was inspired by Eika's mournful experience of accidentally spilling chili sauce all over a big plate of chicken nuggets.
Goods_I18N.20119051_Desc: The outfit Eika wears while working at a fashion store, blending uniform style with trending pink and dark city designs. As an in-store model, Eika often showcases these outfits herself, reportedly boosting sales impressively.
Goods_I18N.20119054_Desc: Eika wears this uniform when working part-time at the game store. It's accented with the color scheme of a popular gaming console. Promoting games is part of the job, so Eika often competes with pro gamers. It's become quite the attraction.
Goods_I18N.20115051_Desc: Flavia's custom outfit, inspired by coffee, milk, and cream. Walking the line between coffee and milk is a dangerous game.
Goods_I18N.20101107_Desc:
A blue and white navy combat suit, thoughtfully designed to match Michele's fighting style, complete with a communication device and a cute survival backpack. Facing the sea breeze, Michele looks even more spirited than usual.

“Anchors aweigh! Hope you don't get seasick!”
Goods_I18N.20205051_Desc:
Though Galatea prefers "stronger" drinks over coffee, she admits that these coffee beans do have a unique flavor.

"Hmm... Next time, I'll add some liquor and make spiked Sidra coffee."
Goods_I18N.10104104_Desc:
Biochemistry-themed version of the Shadow Assault by Quadrant Foundries. While the concept of 'biochemistry' no longer exists in Strinova, its influence on ancient Earth and the warning it carries still endure.

"Biochemical weapons are just one of many boundaries, but war knows no limits. Cruel times will eventually end. Unchecked power will ultimately become humanity's despair."
Goods_I18N.20110103_Desc:
A futuristic sports outfit with bright colors and a sleek design. Bai Mo has infused it with his own unique touches.

"Oh, you've found me! Are you here to take me back as well?"
Although cornered, Bai Mo still bears a cunning smile.
"I'm not slacking off. The leader of Urbino must be free. Locking me in an office would be a huge waste."
As you're drawn in by his words, he leaps away, skillfully escaping your view with expert parkour.
Goods_I18N.30004009_Desc: Is this... the end? Season 1 rank reward.
Goods_I18N.20112110_Desc:
Aside from a well-stocked arsenal, victory in battle requires clever strategies and overwhelming firepower. Fuchsia knows this well, as shown by her Shark Squad's success in live-action shooter games.

"If you're my eagle eyes, Navigator, then I'm your shark teeth. Let's win this, just like we always do!"
Goods_I18N.20110051_Desc: A chef's outfit featuring patterns of fish and bamboo leaves, reminiscent of the aroma of sushi. To Bai Mo, freedom and delicacies are the two most important things in life.
Goods_I18N.20137104_Desc:
The outfit Kanami wore when she performed in a rural concert. The mud on her light dungarees skirt does not ruin her cute style. Kanami chose to keep this outfit after the show ended.

“There's something so satisfying about watching the crops grow day by day.”
Goods_I18N.20137108_Desc:
Kanami's costume for her mythological play. Inspired by a Greek goddess, the dress resembles pure ocean waves with a skirt shaped like a mermaid's tail, topped with a golden laurel for a touch of sanctity.

“I will pray for you. Always.” The girl pours all her emotions and thoughts into the final line. “Rehearsing with you really does... Uh, never mind.”

The girl hesitates for a moment before deciding not to finish her sentence.
Goods_I18N.20137055_Desc: Kanami's promotional outfit for the coffee brand was inspired by latte art, designed to convey a warm, coffee-like sentiment to her fans.
Goods_I18N.20137106_Desc:
Kanami wore this dress, which borrows elements from the tuxedo and the tutu, for the magic show that she was invited to perform in at Laurel Hall. Elegance and romance are Kanami's eternal pursuits, and there seems to be a hidden mystery in the gorgeous ornaments on the skirt.

"Phew... You can do it, Kanami. We must get our things back!"
Goods_I18N.20137105_Desc:
The outfit Kanami wears when invited to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. It highlights her charm and coordination with the conductor. Intentional, perhaps?

"I would like to dream the most beautiful dream with you."
Goods_I18N.20137056_Desc: Kanami's special edition costume is inspired by a sunflower field under the bright sun, showcasing Kanami's boundless ardor.
Goods_I18N.20137051_Desc: Kanami's special performance costume, with a charming yet slightly dangerous aura. Perhaps she will appear in your dreams tonight.
Goods_I18N.20137006_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume, as elegant as a phoenix and as subtle as a dragon's whisper.
Goods_I18N.20137005_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume. The nightingale's song lingers in the endless night.
Goods_I18N.20137004_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume in brilliant violet, blooming to its fullest.
Goods_I18N.20137003_Desc: Kanami's spare performance outfit, in dazzling orange and yellow, mirrors the passionate flames in her heart.
Goods_I18N.20137007_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume. The gilded color reflects the idol's radiance.
Goods_I18N.20137002_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume in cyan, resembling delicate petals.
Goods_I18N.20137008_Desc: Kanami's spare performance costume in green, symbolizing growth.
Goods_I18N.20132102_Desc:
A tight combat uniform in black and red that blends high-tech and retro aesthetics. Her cool and tough facade does little to hide the burning heat deep in her soul.

“Don't make a mess. I don't have time to clean up after you.”
“Listen to me if you want to live! Understood?”
Under Ming's command, each attack is as sharp as a scalpel.
But she fights not for distant ideals, but for survival and the wrath deep within her.
Goods_I18N.20110054_Desc: A black and green racing-style combat uniform makes Bai Mo look dashing and unique. Speed and passion perfectly describe him.
Goods_I18N.10108110_Desc:
A specially modded version of Sawtooth, featuring tools for precise measurement. A skilled bartender knows that controlling drink quality is essential.

"Let's add a touch more malt aroma. My current rating for this drink is only 99.5."
