Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Going to food stalls after work is the best way to meet new friends.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row16_PlayerOption2: I'd like to have some refreshing after work.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId124: But if you want to make friends quickly, the best way is to go out to restaurants together!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row12_PlayerOption1: You don't seem to be talking about an ordinary restaurant
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Haha... we might have just discovered the secret to world peace!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Hello! Navigator, my name is Kokona.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Looks like the friend request went through.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row16_PlayerOption1: If it's a food stall... it's gotta be barbecue
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId124: By the way, there's going to be a taste-testing soon. Let's go together!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId124: That's right... why didn't I think of that?
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId124: What would you like to eat, Navigator? I'll treat you next time!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row12_PlayerOption2: A very down-to-earth way to put it.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row20-b_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I know, I know. We can't go without some ice-cold soda!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I've already heard quite a lot about you.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId124: The friend of my friend is also my friend. That's why I also want to get to know you, Navigator!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId124: That's right. We need something grander than a regular restaurant.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row8_PlayerOption1: If you keep this up, won't you befriend the whole world?

Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Going to food stalls after work is the best way to meet new friends.
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row16_PlayerOption2: I'd like to have some refreshing after work.
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId124: But if you want to make friends quickly, the best way is to go out to restaurants together!
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row12_PlayerOption1: You don't seem to be talking about an ordinary restaurant
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Haha... we might have just discovered the secret to world peace!
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Hello! Navigator, my name is Kokona.
Kokona_124_Lv_2.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Looks like the friend request went through.
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row16_PlayerOption1: If it's a food stall... it's gotta be barbecue
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId124: By the way, there's going to be a taste-testing soon. Let's go together!
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId124: That's right... why didn't I think of that?
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId124: What would you like to eat, Navigator? I'll treat you next time!
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row12_PlayerOption2: A very down-to-earth way to put it.
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row20-b_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I know, I know. We can't go without some ice-cold soda!
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I've already heard quite a lot about you.
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId124: The friend of my friend is also my friend. That's why I also want to get to know you, Navigator!
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId124: That's right. We need something grander than a regular restaurant.
Kokona_124_Lv_2.Row8_PlayerOption1: If you keep this up, won't you befriend the whole world?

Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Come over, and we'll have some hot pot!
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row17_PlayerOption1: Why not share it with everyone?
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId124: But she gave me way too much food. I can't finish it all by myself.
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row11-a_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Don't be so casual about it.
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row4_PlayerOption1: The one who made the vegetable salad?
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Sigh... It's not like I don't appreciate her kindness.
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Oh, right. No need to bring any veggies!
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row19-b_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Hehe... I've been waiting for you to say that!
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Everyone can bring whatever they'd like to eat.
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Navigator, please help me figure out a solution!
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Navigator, do you remember the old lady with the salad store?
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row12-b_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I will. Thank you so much!
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row17_PlayerOption2: All of a sudden, I got a craving for veggies.
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId124: In that case, we might as well call out everyone in the search team!
Kokona_124_Lv_3.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId124: She sent me a big basket of vegetables!

Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId124: The last time I played with Michele, she destroyed me.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId124: That's why you're the Navigator! You get it.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId124: So long as I carry this title, I'll always worry that I'm not good enough.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId124: She's way too good. I don't even know how I lost.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row3_PlayerOption2: This title makes me feel a great sense of responsibility.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Our “Senpai alliance” is certain to win!
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId124: But before that, please accompany me on a round of special training!
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row3_PlayerOption1: That seems to be the case.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Let's invite Astierred next time and have a senpai vs. kouhai duel of the ages!
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Navigator, you understand how I feel, don't you?
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row7_PlayerOption1: You've done a good job already, Kokona.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row7_PlayerOption2: Kokona is way more qualified than I am.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId124: In any case, I need to do some special training.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I went into it full of confidence, thinking I'd at least be able to get a draw.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I think we might have something in common.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row4-a_TextContent_FromRoleId124: As “Senpais,” it's hard for both of us.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId124: A Senpai can never admit defeat!
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row13_PlayerOption1: There's nothing we can do about that.
Kokona_124_Lv_5.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId124: We can't let this continue. It'll ruin our dignity as Senpais!

Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId124: After getting off work, I might be busy until midnight, just like last time.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Operational reports, after-action reviews, damage assessments...
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Are you guys preparing for the Wright Institute of Technology's Open Day?
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row7-a_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Why do you sound like a cruel-hearted boss?
Kokona_124_Lv_7.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId124: There's no way I can finish it all.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row13_PlayerOption2: You should take on some field work, then.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Hehe... that's why I came looking for you.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Of course it's fine! What concerns my friends also concerns me.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I miss my first days of skewers and soda.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row8-b_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Putting it like that is way too cunning.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId124: In that case, I'll leave you be for the time being.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Is the Astral Sanctuary going to join in, too?
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row16_PlayerOption2: The Astral Sanctuary will be providing information sessions to universities.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId124: This is way too much paperwork...
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I'd rather be patrolling the streets like back in my rookie days than doing this kind of boring work.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row16_PlayerOption1: My apologies. I've been very busy...
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId124: This is a good opportunity. Don't let it go to waste.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row6_PlayerOption1: This is proof that your work is important
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row13_PlayerOption1: You should take a proper rest.
Kokona_124_Lv_7.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Just let me know if you need anything.

Kokona_124_Lv_9.Row13_PlayerOption1: Did you fall asleep on the keyboard?
Kokona_124_Lv_9.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Sigh... so sleepy. I didn't sleep at all last night. I need to get some rest.
Kokona_124_Lv_9.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I won't say too much, haha...
Kokona_124_Lv_9.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I'm about ready to go into hikki mode.
Kokona_124_Lv_9.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I'll be turning off my phone and going dark on social media. Consider this your advance notice.
Kokona_124_Lv_9.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I left in such a hurry that I didn't have a chance to tell you...
Kokona_124_Lv_9.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I encountered a bit of a problem when debugging Bunny Mark. I'm gonna have to put some thought into this.

Label.1006_LabelContent: Can summon allies in battle to assist you.
Label.1001_LabelContent: Easy to play and quick to learn.

Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId128: What do you need? I may be able to help.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId128: It's got a long shelf life, so you can take your time with eating it.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I've gotten good feedback from my team.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId128: There's a problem with the base's sensor system.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row10_PlayerOption2: I might not be able to finish all this...
Lawine_128_Lv_1.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Navigator, you won't be able to use the pass I gave you just yet.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I've got around ten more boxes, so there's plenty to share.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row3_PlayerOption1: What a coincidence. I was just planning on going out to get some food.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I just so happened to be purchasing supplies for the team.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I've had them stored for a while.
Lawine_128_Lv_1.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId128: It's good for recovery after training.

Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row27_TextContent_FromRoleId128: But to understand him so quickly... Navigator, do you also like idols?
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId128: But it's quite rare to see a subordinate who doesn't change their ways despite repeated admonitions.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId128: But none of this affected his performance in combat.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row20_TextContent_FromPlayer: Liking idols also allowed him to grow.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId128: In every report, he expresses his great love for his idol. It seems that no one can shake him out of these feelings.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I tried talking to him before, but nothing came of it.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row19_TextContent_FromPlayer: Just like how you like to drink a cup of tea after battle.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I know what you mean, but I'm not going to put drinking tea in my report.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row23_TextContent_FromPlayer: Using your love for idols to motivate you in battle.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.RowNewRow_0_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Delete logs based on actual data.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId128: The new combat reports are well-written, and our recent operations were completed without a hitch.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId128: There's a very unconventional team member who always adds things completely unrelated to the mission to his reports.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId128: In a way, his willpower is very impressive.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row18_PlayerOption2: Looks like that idol really has brought him good luck.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row26_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Improving like this sounds quite nice.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Ever since he became a fan of his favorite idol, he's had the best marksmanship on the team.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row5_PlayerOption2: Changing a person's habits is a difficult thing.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row13_TextContent_FromPlayer: This is “the good luck my idol brings to me!”
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row18_PlayerOption1: This must be how he soothes his mind.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Pursuing an idol for peace of mind? What a novel idea.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.Row5_PlayerOption1: He's treating his reports like they're a diary.
Lawine_128_Lv_3.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId128: When it comes to my lazy teammates, I think leading by example has paid off.

Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Last time, we agreed to meet up for some tea. If you're free, come take a seat.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId128: It's always difficult for one person to convince the other.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I originally wanted to just hold a tea tasting, but in the end, it seems like everyone's taken a side.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId128: As long as you put in the effort, you can make any cup of tea delicious.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row4_PlayerOption2: Sounds more like a debate conference.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row10_PlayerOption1: I can feel it from your tea.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.RowNewRow_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I don't know what you like, so I brewed a bit of each.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId128: By the way, Navigator, what's your favorite kind of tea?
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Yeah, neither the black tea or green tea supporters are letting up.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId128: My techniques with tea are nothing special. It's just a personal hobby.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.RowNewRow_0_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Delete logs based on actual data.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId128: They're arguing about which is better - black tea or green tea.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId128: When I approved the request, it was because I wanted them to feel the joy of tea.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Recently, the team got together for a tea tasting.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row15_PlayerOption2: Thank you. I'll be over in a moment.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row4_PlayerOption1: The room must be filled with the scent of gunpowder.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId128: The taste of a cup of tea has nothing to do with the leaves you use.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row15_PlayerOption1: I'm excited. It's been a while since I've had some tea.
Lawine_128_Lv_5.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Then make sure you're not late today. I'll be waiting for you there.

Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId128: ...Even if we can't see it anymore.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId128: That disguise you lent me last time... The hat had a bit of a strange odor.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Back in the day, the dojo's children would wear these on their chests during festivals.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId128: You helped me last time, Navigator. Consider this a thank-you gift.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId128: We can think of them as things that people in the old world used to express their wishes.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row13_PlayerOption1: Sounds a bit like a talisman.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Yeah. It has a lot of childhood memories.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Yeah. It was a good opportunity to make use of my orchids.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId128: There are times when you'll be in danger.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId128: She would fill sachets with lavender, mugwort, and autumn orchids, then wear them on her clothes like incense.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Some of my orchids have bloomed, so I made a sachet.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId128: By the way, I've harvested a lot of orchid spices this time. Enough for several sachets.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Hopefully, this sachet can bring you some good luck.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I came up with an idea.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row20_PlayerOption1: Lawine, did you prepare a sachet for me, too?
Lawine_128_Lv_7.RowNewRow_0_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Delete logs based on actual data.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId128: It worked quite well. The odor's gone.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row6_PlayerOption2: A clever solution to that pesky odor.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Now that we don't see these traditions anymore, I've come to see those memories as even more precious.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Wait a moment. I'll give you some a bit later.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Think nothing of it. You've also helped me greatly.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row6_PlayerOption1: This matter has been causing me a headache for a while. You've helped a lot.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId128: This is something my mother taught me how to do.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Sachets were once used to ward off evil spirits and pray for blessings.
Lawine_128_Lv_7.Row13_PlayerOption2: The sachet must have a special meaning to you.

Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row27_TextContent_FromRoleId128: ...Please be patient until that agreed upon day. I'll tell you everything, I promise.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Our last sparring session went quite well.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row23_PlayerOption1: You mentioned that there was still something you wanted to say...
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId128: But you might need to make a personal appearance to satisfy them.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId128: In a sense, you've already graduated.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId128: In a few days, our operation in Preton will come to an end. As promised, I will wait for you at the teahouse.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row16_PlayerOption1: Sounds like I can recruit some disciples of my own.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row6_PlayerOption1: Why don't we try my “special tactics?”
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I'll train you in martial arts, and you'll help temper my mind. I'd also like to seek your advice on other tactical matters.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Let me give it a try.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.RowNewRow_0_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Delete logs based on actual data.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Things worked out better than expected.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row24_TextContent_FromPlayer: Can you tell me during the in-person demonstration?
Lawine_128_Lv_9.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I was recently asked to teach self-defense to the children in the sanctuary.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId128: Perfect timing. I was about to invite you over for an in-person demonstration.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId128: It becomes tricky when the target is a child.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId128: I tried many things, but none of them attracted any interest.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId128: The children managed to get the hang of those moves you taught me pretty quickly.
Lawine_128_Lv_9.Row16_PlayerOption2: I'll lend you some out-of-battlefield assistance.

Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId107: It's rare to have a day off. I wonder if you would consider going to see a solo exhibition with me?
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Astierred gave me your contact details...
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId107: She's told me a lot of stories about your glorious deeds, Navigator.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row22_PlayerOption2: Can I sample drinks at the expo?
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId107: She also mentioned that you're usually very busy. I hope I haven't disturbed you.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId107: So dedicated! That's what you expect from the Astral Sanctuary's top performer...!
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId107: The posters say the exhibition will feature designs such as the Waterfall of Joy and the Coffee Fountain.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row26_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I've sent you the address and schedule of the exhibition.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Navigator, do you have anything planned for the holiday?
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I feel that we'll see a lot of interesting things.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Astierred told me that you've always got a cup of coffee in your hand.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row13_PlayerOption2: I'm more used to staying at home and drinking coffee...
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Yeah, the last time I got into trouble, Astierred helped take care of my wounds.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId107: A master who can drink five cups of Starlight Coffee in a single go!
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I've wanted to take you there for a while.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row13_PlayerOption1: I was just thinking of doing some overtime at the Astral Sanctuary.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId107: You can't waste a good vacation, right?
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row9_PlayerOption1: Fortunately, I happen to have some time off.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Keep work-life balance in mind. Don't push yourself too much.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Remember me? I'm the designer who was looking for you last time - Maddelena Leary.
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row22_PlayerOption1: In that case, I'm very interested!
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I guess we won't know until we get there...
Maddelena_107_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId107: What a load off my mind...

Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row8_PlayerOption1: Why don't you tell me about it?
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId107: But... I suddenly had a flash of inspiration!
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId107: But, I've run into a problem that no painter can escape.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Which direction do you think would be more interesting?
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Don't mind me. This is just a special name that I came up with.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Hmm... the aesthetic of a mountain village with smoke rising up from cooking pots and the crisscrossing of streets offers a unique charm.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId107: The sky, berry castle, and country fields.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId107: A sky theme? ...That's great for conveying the freedom and purity of vast distances.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId107: If that's the theme, I'd use color to showcase the sweetness of berries and a dreamy fairy tale.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId107: What if we need all three elements?
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId107: There are three directions I can take.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId107: There are so many things I want to express... I'm at such a loss.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I just signed up for the Fun and Wonders exhibition.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId107: What would it be like to conceive of a piece named Dreams - Colorful Berries Under the Fluffy Clouds: Story of Harvest?
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I've got an idea now. The final result won't let you down, Navigator!
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId107: This helps me remember my inspirations when creating a piece.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId107: ...I'm not quite sure what to paint.
Maddelena_107_Lv_3.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I'll be seeking your advice, Navigator.

Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Just thinking about the proof gives me a headache. I really don't want to go back to working on it.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Now, there's one more person in this world who thinks like I do.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId107: After the vacation ends, I think I'll take some more time off...
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Berrytown is still as beautiful as I remember.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Navigator, for your health, I hope you can take it easy on the coffee... especially Starlight Coffee!
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Unfortunately, as a designer, I have no idea how to make a time machine.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Agreed. It's rare for me to go on a trip, and yet all I could do was gaze at the crowds of people.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I hope this trip didn't disappoint you, Navigator.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I can't press pause on happy times.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I can only use this paintbrush to record the beauty of the world.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row12_PlayerOption1: It's more interesting than those rides you need to queue up all day for.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId107: It's amazing... We did so many things during the day, but I'm still not tired at all.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId107: But if two insomniacs can't sleep, they might as well chat for a little while.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row4_PlayerOption2: Seems like I can't sleep without coffee anymore.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row12_PlayerOption2: If only I could vacation there forever.
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Thank you! I'm glad that you think so!
Maddelena_107_Lv_5.Row4_PlayerOption1: Not yet. I'm feeling quite energetic right now.

Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I accidentally triggered the guesthouse's alarm!!
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row11_PlayerOption2: Why did I smell burning in the other room?
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Did you come to my room this morning?
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row3_PlayerOption1: I happened to see that you forgot to lock your door.
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Judging from the presentation alone, I can say with confidence that they're as good as any five-star restaurant.
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId107: In terms of taste, I asked Astierred to give me a lot of feedback.
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row19_PlayerOption1: Why did the alarm go off all of a sudden?!
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I-I'll deal with it right away...
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row11_PlayerOption1: I've got a bad feeling about this...
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I cooked a new dish with the strawberries we got from the villagers.
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I was so focused on painting last night... I totally forgot.
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Oh, right. I've still got a fresh batch of berries from last night.
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Thank you for the blanket. I might have caught a cold if it wasn't for you.
Maddelena_107_Lv_7.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId107: This dish... we'll call it “spicy strawberry pizza!”

Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId107: The art seminar I mentioned... we'll have to arrange it for another day.
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId107: ...When you're not so busy, please remember to make some time for me.
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId107: It's already late. Are you still working, Navigator?
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row3_PlayerOption2: Did you mean to send that message?
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Oops, sorry. That went to the wrong person...
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Um... It's nothing... Please keep working hard!
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId107: It's just that... right now, I feel a little envious of Astierred...
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId107: You're also a doctor at the Astral Sanctuary. I can understand!
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I've always thought that it was an incredible profession!
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId107: We've both been very busy as of late.
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row7_PlayerOption2: There's a medical report due tonight.
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId107: I've got several designs due tomorrow!
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Reliable doctors such as yourself give us the confidence to take collapse syndrome head-on.
Maddelena_107_Lv_9.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId107: Wait a moment. I'll send it to you now.

MapLoadingTips.1_Tips: Press <ActionKey Name="SettingSideAndFly" Gamepadaction="SettingGamePadSideAndFly" Baseline="-4" Widgetsize="25"/> to sidestep and dodge incoming bullets.
MapLoadingTips.2_Tips: Press <ActionKey Name="GameKeyTips" Gamepadaction="GameKeyTips_Gamepad" Baseline="-4" Widgetsize="25"/> to View Skill Details
MapLoadingTips.4_Tips: Press <ActionKey Name="MarkWheel" Baseline="-4" Widgetsize="25"/> to mark locations.
MapLoadingTips.7_Tips: Stringify Glide lets you get around even faster—Master it for standout plays!
MapLoadingTips.5_Tips: In the Push-to-Talk settings, press <ActionKey Name="EnableTeamVoice" Baseline="-4" Widgetsize="25"/> to enable team voice chat.
MapLoadingTips.8_Tips: If an area proves hard to crack, communicate with your teammates to switch attack objectives.
MapLoadingTips.6_Tips: Bomb detonation takes time—Stop the defending team from defusing it as quickly as you can.
MapLoadingTips.3_Tips: Press <ActionKey Name="Wall2D" Baseline="-4" Widgetsize="25"/> near certain walls to Wall-Stick and move along the surface.

Michele_101_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Even at work, you've got to find some balance.
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Greeting and caring for citizens is also part of an investigator's duty.
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Haha, I told you already. You're my gaming partner.
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId101: For us investigators, the concerns of our citizens are just like our own.
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Just a little sneaky break—keep it a secret, okay partner?
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row9_PlayerOption2: No slacking off on the job!
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Hey there, Navigator! It's Officer Michele, checking in again!
Michele_101_Lv_1.RowNewRow_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Delete logs based on actual data.
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Come over, and let's game once I'm off work. I've got some delicious pineapple buns that you can snack on.
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's a bit different this time...
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: If you need help, feel free to reach out to your nearest Investigation Bureau!
Michele_101_Lv_1.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But I really can't wait to clock out!

Michele_101_Lv_3.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: There's gotta be a way to improve Mighty Meow's image and make everyone love him.
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Partner, why do you think everyone's so scared of Mighty Meow?
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row11_PlayerOption1: But isn't Mighty Meow a tactical robo-cat?
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Oh look, a passerby. Mighty Meow, give them a wave!
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But his “blazing” power is only expressed on the battlefield!
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row17_PlayerOption3: Let's just go with both paws up.
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row17_PlayerOption2: They say the right paw invites good fortune...
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row17_PlayerOption1: They say the left paw invites wealth...
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row5_PlayerOption1: Probably because his "blazing" power is just...
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But which paw should it wave first?
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Mighty Meow could look into new ventures!
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Mighty Meow lost control of its blaster...
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Great idea, double the luck and fortune!
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row11_PlayerOption2: Got it. From now on, he's the "Fortune Meow."
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Time to head back and write those report... We'll figure it out next time. I'm sure we'll think of something!
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: He's such a well-behaved little cutie...
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Oh no! Mighty Meow just fired a shot to the left!
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Even though it didn’t work out, I'm still thankful for all your help, partner.
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId101: We'll train Mighty Meow to be the best "Fortune Meow" ever.
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Maybe we can have Mighty Meow wave at people by the bureau entrance. It could become bring luck and fortune to everyone!
Michele_101_Lv_3.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I like that name! It sounds much friendlier.

Michele_101_Lv_5.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId101: The Investigator's Guide to Self-Improvement, P.U.S Road Safety Management Regulations,  Investigator's Guidebook to Common Firearms, Tactical Robo-Cat Assembly: Beginner to Expert, The Significance and Cultural Heritage of Investigator Badges.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId101: This isn't working. It's way too inefficient.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId101: After chatting with you, partner, I feel much more energized.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I’ve decided—I'm heading to the convenience store for some bread!
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row10_PlayerOption2: I don't even want to think about it...
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Exactly! With that bread, there's no need to worry about forgetting things when you're sleepy!
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I struggled so hard to finish just the first book.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I really need the comfort of my bed right now.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I'll come find you to hang out once my test's over!
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's said that if you print what you want to remember on a piece of bread, you'll never forget it.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Seems like I'm not the only one who gets drowsy the moment I open a book, haha.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row18_PlayerOption1: Wait... What has reading got to do with bread?
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Delicious bread acquired! I'm saved... I'm starving from all that reading.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: We've got an investigator assessment coming up soon.
Michele_101_Lv_5.Row10_PlayerOption1: These are all on the test??

Michele_101_Lv_7.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Paper Detective: Mysteries of the Ancient Tomb.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row21_PlayerOption2: Can you really type and play at the same time?
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId101: How did you know? I'm being swarmed by them right now.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's a detective game, so it needs that suspenseful and eerie vibe!
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row25_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Just give me a sec. I'll get it right this time!
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I just had a look at the manual.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row7_PlayerOption1: Um, something seems a bit off about that.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Wait... wasn't this supposed to be a detective game?
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Interesting, right? They've never done a tomb theme before!
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I'm trying it out. If it's fun, I'll bring you along.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Time to show them my shooting skills.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's fine. It's just a tutorial stage.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId0: Nope. But a huge wave of zombies just appeared out of nowhere!
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Yep! I bought it during the spring sale.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Game over... Didn't expect the tutorial to be so hard.
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row21_PlayerOption1: Just focus on the game, watch out for zombies!
Michele_101_Lv_7.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId101: "Step into the shoes of legendary detective Charlotte Holmes, alongside your partner, the brilliant young archaeologist Laura Crawford, to solve the mystery of the thousand-year-old tomb."

Michele_101_Lv_9.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But I have to finish an 18-page apology letter first.
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row9_PlayerOption2: Where did you sneak off to this time?
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row4_PlayerOption1: You haven't logged in to your account for a while.
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row12_PlayerOption1: So, you've been hiding with the cats.
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Yeah. I've been busy writing apology letters lately...
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Oh right, I haven't taken you there yet.
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Criticism from superiors and an endless pile of written apologies.
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId101: They say these are the two unavoidable disasters in life...
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's a super relaxing, healing place full of kitties!
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I've been thinking, we haven't seen much of each other lately.
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's a good thing I came here. My energy is finally slowly recharging.
Michele_101_Lv_9.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I've wanted to bring you here for ages.

PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId146: But I got the message, Navigator.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row15_PlayerOption1: No, what’s really a pity is...
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Today is a really important day for you...
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Haha, that's because I’m still building up my confidence in singing...
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Ah, even though I rehearsed many times, it still sounds a bit off...
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I hope your kindness will continue to be with me in the future.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row16_TextContent_FromPlayer: I didn't get to hear your birthday song in person.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId146: So, I’ve prepared a little surprise.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row8_PlayerOption1: Not at all, I think it sounded beautiful.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Just be patient, maybe next time your wish will come true!
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row10_PlayerOption1: Just hearing your voice makes me really happy.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_1.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId146: If only I could have practiced a few more times...

PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId146: This won't do, you can't keep going on like this.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Whether it's feeding seagulls at the beach or watching a fireworks festival...
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId146: You've been working overtime for so many days now...
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId146: You know, it was your birthday just a few days ago.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId146: All you need to do is relax and enjoy the break~
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Don't worry, I've got it all sorted.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Whatever you want to do, I'll be right there with you.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I finally got through to you!
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row4_PlayerOption1: Oops, I guess I got carried away with the workload.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId146: You could have left the work to me...
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row4_PlayerOption2: Almost there, just a few more pages to go.
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I'm sending you on a vacation right now, and it's non-negotiable!
PlayerBirthday_HuiXing_Lv_2.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Even though it's a bit late now, but...

PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row21_TextContent_FromPlayer: Two crates of your favorite soda, on their way!
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Hey, partner! Did you get it?
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row20_PlayerOption1: Double surprise sure didn’t come easy.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Hehe~ As long as it makes you happy, it’s all worth it!! (^▽^)
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Hehe~ Now you get double the surprise! (≧▽≦)
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row11_PlayerOption1: Haha, you actually sang it twice.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I'll stay off the mic during our game later, my voice needs a break.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId101: My voice is toast... all that singing really took it out of me...
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row20_PlayerOption2: I've got a little treat for you.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId101: The birthday song I sang for you!
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId101: For real?! You're the best, Partner!! (≧▽≦)
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's my special gift for your birthday!
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Did it come through this time?
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId101: You didn’t get it? I'll sing it again!

PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row9_PlayerOption2: Couldn't resist... ended up taking on some extra shifts.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I've been saving up for this, so whatever anime or game merch you want, I've got you covered!
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But I bet you didn't volunteer for overtime!
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I couldn’t celebrate your birthday with you in person...
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Just like writing apology letters, never-ending!
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row5_PlayerOption1: I'm also "on duty" at Astral Sanctuary.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I heard Miss Celestia even gave you time off...
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row14_1_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I booked you tickets for the Arton City Comic Con, did you get them?
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: The captain sent me to another district for a mission, and I won't be back for a few days.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row9_PlayerOption1: There's too much work, I'm struggling to keep up.
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I'm getting excited just thinking about it! It's going to be epic! (≧▽≦)
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Great! It's actually a belated birthday gift, hehe~ (^▽^)
PlayerBirthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId101: It's all because Astral Sanctuary's got you swamped.

PlayModeControl.14_ModeInfo:
10-Player Scrimmage

Victory Conditions:
1. Defeat the specified number of enemies within the designated time.
2. When the match ends, rank in the top 6.
PlayModeControl.3_ModeInfo:
10-Player Rumble

Victory Conditions:
Comostrings: During the Final Showdown, knock down all enemies or prevent the enemy from collecting 3,000 cores.
Core Catchers: During the Final Showdown, collect 3,000 cores.
PlayModeControl.22_ModeInfo:
12-Player Boom Fest

1. At the start of each round, a few players are randomly chosen as Carriers.
2. The Bomb explodes after a set time or when the round ends.
3. Carriers can pass the Bomb using melee attacks.
4. HP mechanic removed; getting hit significantly slows you down.
5. Survive each round to earn points; the highest score wins.
PlayModeControl.10_ModeInfo:
15-Player Snowball Fight

Victory Condition:
1. Earn points by surviving or landing hits from within the battlefield
PlayModeControl.8_ModeInfo:
15-Player Hide-and-Seek

Victory Conditions:
1. Seekers: Find and defeat all Runners.
2. Runners: Evade the Seekers and stay alive until the end of the match.
PlayModeControl.4_ModeInfo:
4-Team 3v3 Deathmatch

Victory Conditions:
1. Defeat the specified number of enemies within the time limit.
2. Rank in the top three teams at the end of the match.
PlayModeControl.5_ModeInfo:
3v3v3 Team Arena

Victory Conditions:
1. Defeat the specified number of enemies within the time limit.
2. Rank in the top two teams at the end of the match.
PlayModeControl.16_ModeInfo:
5v5v5 Bobblehead Brawl

Victory Conditions:
1. Eliminate all other teams during the Final Showdown
2. The team with more surviving players at the end of the Final Showdown wins
PlayModeControl.26_ModeInfo:
5v5 Escort Battle

Victory Conditions:
1. Attackers: Escort the payload to the destination within the specified time.
2. Defenders: Prevent the payload from reaching the destination within the specified time.
Special Mechanics:
1. Approach or stick on the payload to advance it forward.
2. Adjust the String Energy Network while in the Safe Zone or waiting to respawn.
3. Team members will respawn together periodically.
PlayModeControl.15_ModeInfo:
5v5 Attack and Defend

Victory Conditions:
Attackers: Destroy the objective or defeat all Defenders
Defenders: Defend the objective
PlayModeControl.1_ModeInfo:
6v6 Team Battle

Victory Conditions:
1. The first team to reach the designated number of defeats wins.
2. At the end of the match, the team with the most enemy defeats wins.
PlayModeControl.9_ModeInfo:
7v7 Attack and Defend

Victory Conditions:
1. First team to reach the target number of crystals wins.
2. If time runs out, the team with the most crystals wins.

PlayModeControl_I18N.11_ModeInfo:
15 players split into two teams

Victory Conditions:
Superstring Agents: Survive until the match ends.
Crystallines: Defeat all Superstring Agents before time runs out.

Special Mechanics:
1. Card buff mechanism is enabled.
2. Superstrings start with passive skills unlocked.
3. Crystallines killed by Ninjatos cannot be revived.
PlayModeControl_I18N.6_ModeInfo:
5v5 Escort Battle

Victory Conditions:
1. Attackers: Escort the payload to the destination within the specified time.
2. Defenders: Prevent the payload from reaching the destination within the specified time.

Special Mechanics:
1. Approach or stick on the payload to advance it forward.
2. You can adjust the String Energy Network while in a Safe Zone or waiting to respawn.
3. You can resupply your tactical items multiple times.
4. Team members will respawn together periodically.

PledgeEvent.146009_TextEvent: The comfort of a clear night
PledgeEvent.146007_TextEvent: The stress of a physical check-up

PledgeItem.11202_ItemStory:
The work certificate of the Strongman moving company. There are no complicated procedures. Present the certificate, and you are good to go.
Five minutes of rest for every five hours of work may sound tough to most people, but Fuchsia is not most people. Determinated to become stronger, she has become a strongwoman rivaling cargo robots.
PledgeItem.10701_ItemStory:
Admission tickets for the Fun and Wonders art exhibition, featuring patterns designed by Cloudscape Gallery's Maddelena.
Tickets for this exhibition are highly sought-after, requiring at least six months' advance booking to secure a chance to attend.
These two hard-to-come-by tickets are an extra reward for Maddelena's participation in the design.
PledgeItem.10103_ItemStory:
A model of the giant sword from Superheroes of Justice, sold as a set with the sword model. In Michele's hands, the tiny model performs incredible wonders.
“Go forth and face the difficulties. The light of hope shall not diminish!”
PledgeItem.10101_ItemStory:
A shiny model of the giant sword from Superheroes of Justice. Michele's father gave it to her on her birthday. It embodies her pure faith and dreams.
“With your sword in hand, follow your heart and tear through the darkness! This is the way of gamers.”
PledgeItem.10501_Name: The Spiral of Speech Hardcover Edition
PledgeItem.13102_ItemStory: The usually well-behaved Fay suddenly runs away from home, causing Yvette to worry greatly. Yvette finds Fay on Commercial Street being attacked by a bunch of kids. Fay seems to be holding... a cup of milk tea in her paw?
PledgeItem.10701_Desc: Admission tickets to an artistic feast of surprises and inspiration...
PledgeItem.14601_ItemStory:
A tablet with the left side of the screen damaged, once used to record collapse syndrome patient data. It now serves as a memento of your first collaboration with Celestia.
Astral Sanctuary's logo is at the center of the screen, with scattered stars representing visiting patients.
PledgeItem.10504_ItemStory:
A pair of medals of honor engraved with black and white unicorns, bearing the trust of an ancient family. It is said that the recipient will receive blessings from the unicorns.
In the face of time, everything decays, only the noble soul remaining indestructible.
PledgeItem.12801_ItemStory:
A metal pass card with the symbol of The Scissors, gifted by Lawine, marking the beginning of your acquaintance with her.
The pass represents the trust and recognition of The Scissors, granting free access to certain areas of its territory.
PledgeItem.10101_Desc: Every time she talks about games, her eyes twinkle like little stars.
PledgeItem.14603_ItemStory:
A handmade bracelet with the sun at its center, connecting stars and moons at both ends.
The bracelet is made from crystals mined on Old Earth. Celestia's name is engraved on the inside of one of the crystals.
PledgeItem.13703_ItemStory:
A wireless transmission and reception remote control device, compatible with all the smart devices in Kanami's home.
Ranked as the best smart home product, the universal remote is capable of controlling the indoor environment by integrating electronic devices.
PledgeItem.10501_Desc: Making friends is similar to negotiating - both are a struggle to earn someone's respect.
PledgeItem.10704_Desc: Protecting the most beautiful story of harvest with the paintbrush!
PledgeItem.13101_ItemStory: Yvette invented a device capable of “sensing emotions”, but due to her social anxiety, she has not been able to recruit any test subjects. To avoid wasting her research efforts, she has turned to the Navigator for assistance.
PledgeItem.13102_Desc: Yvette and Fay's favorite milk tea!
PledgeItem.12401_ItemStory:
A carefully crafted acrylic figurine featuring a Chibi version of Kokona giving a thumbs up.
Bestowed only upon businesses recognized for their taste, quality, and innovation, this badge of honor is widely acknowledged by the citizens.
PledgeItem.14602_ItemStory:
A finely crafted telescope with a metal star pendant hanging from a thin chain.
The tube of the telescope is made from brass, incorporating precious wood, and retains the classic design aesthetics of old Earth.
PledgeItem.13701_ItemStory: A finely crafted lavender handheld glow stick with a matching butterfly ribbon, just like Kanami's. Custom-made by the Kanami fan club, this limited-edition item is exclusively distributed.
PledgeItem.13701_Desc: A must-have item for idol support.
PledgeItem.12404_ItemStory:
A portable projector capable of storing large volumes of engineering data, suitable for viewing blueprints on the job.
Recommended by senior engineers, it is light and compact, leaving precious space for other items on the workbench. The content stored within carries people's thoughts and memories.
PledgeItem.12801_Desc: Decisive and swift, a captain should lead by example.
PledgeItem.11201_ItemStory:
A cutely fierce limited-edition shark toy, far more challenging than the regular version. It is said that only biting shark masters can manage to avoid the shark's sharp teeth.
Fuchsia received this toy as her first payment for helping out at Astral Sanctuary. Although she has collected a large number of shark-themed items, this one remains her favorite. Around the time Fuchsia started working at Astral Sanctuary, the toy suddenly became popular among the children at Astral Sanctuary.
PledgeItem.10702_ItemStory:
The creator designed this basket with the hopeful wish of a rewarding journey, decorated with her favorite sweet tea strawberries.
The basket is often empty, but perhaps thanks to the art consultant's blessing, the designer's wish has been fulfilled.
PledgeItem.12803_ItemStory:
A beret and a pair of sunglasses purchased during a sale, with a simple look and excellent UV protection. Given to Lawine after she cleverly handled a crisis. As a result of her careful maintenance, the hat now carries a faint scent and looks as glossy as new.
Lawine cherishes them deeply, believing that they bring her good luck and courage as she wears them out on sunny days.
PledgeItem.10503_Desc: In the arena of negotiation, the dark side faces against the light side as logic and emotions clash.
PledgeItem.13103_ItemStory:
Losing one's family turns the nearby home into an unreachable place.
Yvette has in her pocket a bear keychain with a heavily worn access card attached to it, seemingly leading to a secret place.
PledgeItem.10502_ItemStory:
Audrey has collected and organized chocolate recipes that cover over a dozen styles. From ingredients to production methods, everything is included.
Thanks to her dedication, the century-old family stands proud, turning even the bitterest chocolate sweet and crisp.
PledgeItem.12804_Desc: Closing her eyes, she feels as calm as you.
PledgeItem.12803_Desc: Improvise, adapt, and overcome like a pine standing firm against the wind.
PledgeItem.12402_ItemStory:
The Sea Bunny healing drone Kokona uses, designed with her personal aesthetics in mind.
The drone's ears flop lifelessly due to the loss of power. Perhaps it is just tired and only needs a little rest before returning to Kokona. Protect it for Kokona until it wakes up.
PledgeItem.12403_Desc: Kokona's treasured possession, filled with memories.
PledgeItem.10103_Desc: I am Investigator Michele, but I'm also the super gamer Michele!
PledgeItem.11203_Desc: In the hands of a shark, the controller becomes a hunting weapon.
PledgeItem.12802_ItemStory:
Lawine's personal first aid kit. Simple and modest in size, it is stocked with common medical supplies, especially for treating wounds.
Lawine uses these medicines sparingly, seemingly not caring about her own wounds.
PledgeItem.12804_ItemStory:
Lawine's wooden training dagger for practicing martial arts. It is light, compact, and easy to conceal. The blade is severely worn, marking every training session of Lawine's.
Found on the weapon rack of the dojo, it now accompanies Lawine as she seeks inner peace, whether in the bamboo forest behind the dojo or the moonlit tea house.
PledgeItem.11202_Desc: This certificate allows the holder to strive to break through their limits...
PledgeItem.14604_Desc: An electric sparkler that emits a gentle glow.
PledgeItem.14602_Desc: Celestia's childhood favorite, now with new meaning.
PledgeItem.12401_Desc: Acknowledgement from the gourmet street food.
PledgeItem.11204_Desc: A battle fought without guns can still bring surprise and excitement...
PledgeItem.10102_ItemStory:
The P.U.S badge embodies the spirit of perseverance of past investigators, with the sword of justice piercing through it, its valiant glory still shining.

“Justice, bravery, and perseverance - this is the motto of P.U.S.”
“By wearing this badge, I, too, can become a hero!”
PledgeItem.14603_Desc: A bracelet of Celestial bodies, engraved with Celestia's name.
PledgeItem.10704_ItemStory:
One of Maddelena Leary's signature pieces, created with the help of her consultant using paint made from berries, featuring every specialty product of Berrytown.
However, there are few who can pronounce the full name of this heartwarming artwork.
PledgeItem.10703_ItemStory:
Maddelena's favorite paintbrushes and the Kaleidoscope palette, covered in paint made from berries.
Maddelena received Kaleidoscope on her 7th birthday. Despite it being stained over time, Maddelena still uses it to mix colors every time she paints.
PledgeItem.10704_Name: Sweet and Dreamy: Story of Harvest IV
PledgeItem.11203_ItemStory:
The official Champion of Fighters Tournament controller, provided by Big Cat Arcade. Compared to generic controllers, it feels more like Fuchsia's personal weapon.
Fuchsia is meticulous when it comes to combat preparation, tuning the controller to be as handy as Sawtooth. As for the eye-catching shark decoration on the joysticks, it is unclear whether it is a display of battle aesthetics or just a personal preference.
PledgeItem.10501_ItemStory:
Written by Audrey's parents, the negotiation handbook contains comprehensive techniques and expertise, helping Audrey emerge victorious in countless negotiations.
The first page reads, “To Audrey Grove, our most beloved daughter.”
PledgeItem.10504_Desc: The pride and purity of the storied family flow within it.
PledgeItem.13704_ItemStory:
"A hardcover music scorebook adorned with dancing notes and decorated with two pure white magnolia blossoms.
It's said that long ago, Kanami carried this scorebook everywhere to jot down her song inspirations."
PledgeItem.14601_Desc: A memento of your first collaboration.
PledgeItem.10503_ItemStory:
A simple, classic bone china coffee cup, a birthday gift given by her parents. Audrey seldom uses it due to her dislike of coffee.
The coffee carries the flavor of memories, witnessing the gatherings and partings of an ancient family.
PledgeItem.10104_ItemStory:
When Michele received a gift of appreciation for her gamer's style for the first time, she engraved her beliefs on the trophy, protecting the cat paw cookies inside.
“To the amazing cat detective, your courage and perseverance are not different from those of the hero in the game.”
PledgeItem.13104_Desc: A delicate ribbon, treasured by Yvette and kept at the top of her gift box.
PledgeItem.10502_Desc: Through the creator's ingenuity, the chocolate was sculpted from its molten state.
PledgeItem.13101_Desc: A device capable of visualizing various types of human data, invented by Yvette.
PledgeItem.10703_Desc: The palette and colors are not unlike the artist and the consultant.
PledgeItem.12802_Desc: As a weapon of destruction of The Scissors, Lawine sweeps through enemy lines like a raging flame.
PledgeItem.10702_Desc: The fruit basket is filled with inspiration!
PledgeItem.11201_Desc: This is Fuchsia's first payment for helping out at Astral Sanctuary.
PledgeItem.13704_Desc: This dream-filled score has returned to the girl's hands.
PledgeItem.10102_Desc: I alone have to uphold what the badge represents.
PledgeItem.14604_ItemStory:
An electronic device that simulates fireworks by emitting beams of light. Its safe and harmless design completely replaces traditional gunpowder fireworks.
While its electronic design fits the style of Strinova, it is actually an item from Old Earth.
PledgeItem.12403_ItemStory:
A replica of an oddly shaped ancient doll, a cultural heritage of Old Earth.
Even among the many unique gifts Kokona has received, this stands out as particularly unusual. Rumor has it that Kokona once used it to play house.
PledgeItem.13104_ItemStory:
An important gift cherished by Yvette and kept at the top of her gift box.
She only wears it on important occasions.
Every day spent with someone important is a perfect day.
PledgeItem.10104_Desc: What lies beyond the door? The girl gathers her courage and opens the door...
PledgeItem.13103_Desc: An old keychain with a heavily worn access card attached to it.
PledgeItem.11204_ItemStory:
The prize awarded to the winners of the Champion of Fighter double tournament. The following words are engraved on the trophy: “The honor belongs to both of you.”
The simple and unadorned design indicates that it is not a real champion's trophy but rather a souvenir awarded for participation. When Fuchsia brought it home, however, she still displayed it in the most prominent spot.
PledgeItem.13702_ItemStory:
Kanami arranged to have this pass issued to the Navigator, granting the same clearance as she has.
The pass contains a chip that records data from every access gate.
PledgeItem.13703_Desc: Kanami's smart device used in the dormitory.
PledgeItem.13702_Desc: A custom pass approved by Kanami's agency.

ReturnLetterCfg.10005_LetterTitleTwo:
The next taste-testing event is about to begin!
The competition has gotten way more fierce. Everyone seems super motivated to earn “Kokona's approval”.
I wonder what kind of food will be on offer this time? Who's gonna win the grand prize?
It's so hard to decide! Even thinking about it makes my head spin!
Navigator, will you join me?

Hehe... When I'm with you, it feels like I never run out of things to say.
I look forward to sitting with you at the food stall after work, chatting about this and that while we enjoy tasty skewers and sweet soda.
I hope that day will come soon - don't keep me waiting!
ReturnLetterCfg.10004_LetterTitleTwo:
Perhaps that's beyond my reach.
But that doesn't mean I'm going to give up. I'll keep chasing your shadow, no matter how long it takes.

On another note, I've planted some new flowers at home.
After some time, maybe around when you return -
They'll be able to bloom.
When the time comes, please come visit.
I wonder how it will feel - to drink tea and look at the flowers with you once more.

When I think about it, there are so many things I want to do with you.
Our bond still has a long way to go.
In the future, I'm sure the threads of our lives will wind an even more beautiful tapestry.
ReturnLetterCfg.10001_LetterTitle:
Do you remember those days when we gazed at the stars together...?
I showed you how, when the stars thin out at the horizon and four bright ones emerge, it signals the onset of autumn. 
I wonder when the next autumn will come...

While you've been away, I've continued to observe many distant celestial bodies alone.
They're both captivating and mysterious.
Among them, there's a splendid star cluster about 5,200 light-years from Earth, adorned with colors as deep and vivid as flowers.
In the old astronomical records of Earth, it is called the 'Rosette Nebula', where each petal cradles the birth of new stars.
ReturnLetterCfg.10005_LetterTitle:
Heya partner. It's been a while!
What kind of adventures have you been on?
You must have come across so many new and wonderful things to have been away for so long.

It's a shame that I can't join you out there.
I've many important friends here to protect. Many juniors to set an example for.
But it's not boring, either. Our world is also changing rapidly, with many new things happening every day.
While you've been away, everyone's been working hard to protect this world and make it a better place. If you return, you should take a look around at all the changes that have occurred

Oh! One more thing -
ReturnLetterCfg.10001_LetterTitleTwo:
In our world, the first observer can claim nominal ownership of a star.
This bouquet of stars, had it not been discovered by an observer from Strinova, would have faded into the oblivion of time.
Fortunately, I was the first to discover it—how magnificent this cluster of roses in the nebula is...

When the stars next align, would you be so kind as to join me in gazing upon it?
How wonderful it would be if I could sit with you under the autumn night, counting the stars one by one...
ReturnLetterCfg.10002_LetterTitle:
Long time no see, partner!
Do you still remember that wish we made together?
You would be the “Mighty Meow”, and I would be the “Mini Meow.”
Let's walk hand in hand and become the heroes of the next generation of Superheroes of Justice!

Partner, have you heard of all that's happened while you were away?
Some players have adapted our experiences into fan-fiction and posted them all over the Internet!
These stories have sparked a big response from the community.
Even game studios found the story of the Cat Inspector and Navigator to be super interesting.
This part is gonna shock you! They decided to -
ReturnLetterCfg.10006_LetterTitle:
Navigator! I'm starting to think you've forgotten about me!
What have you been up to lately? Still doing overtime at the Astral Sanctuary?
To be honest, I'm about the same... The Cloudburst Museum recently got commissioned to create a huge exhibition.
Word on the street is that it's being funded by our boss and the Grove family. The scale is meant to be as big as the “Headturner” exhibition.

Fortunately enough, I was able to put all the materials we collected in Berrytown to use, and my design was selected!
Maybe I even have the chance to win a Best Creation award!
I hope you'll be able to see it too...

One more thing...
ReturnLetterCfg.10004_LetterTitle:
Navigator, how long has it been since we've last seen one another?

I'm still a loyal patron of my favorite teahouse.
Feeling the cool breeze bow through the bamboo, I can't help but be reminded of...
Those days we sparred and sampled tea together.
For some reason, I always felt like something was missing - something that would give the tea in my cup the flavor I was used to.
Sure enough, it does feel rather lonely without you around.

Don't worry! I've been keeping up my practice, even while you're gone.
The more I practice, the more amazed I become at your tactics.
I wonder how long it will take me to achieve your focus in battle.
ReturnLetterCfg.10006_LetterTitleTwo:
I tried out a few new dishes on my family - stuff like chicken-fried steak, macaroni, and lasagna...
The feedback I've received is that they're as delicious as they are artistic!
When you have time, I'd love to invite you over.
Let's enjoy a long-overdue dinner.

To make a unique and delicious dish, you've got to use seasonings that people wouldn't expect!
I'm hoping you'll come back soon. I'm not the same artist without your inspiration and support.
Navigator, I've found a lot of good places to collect materials for my art. I'd love to visit them with you.
ReturnLetterCfg.10003_LetterTitleTwo:
But I wonder, can I really convey that sincerity that you spoke about?
My heart was uneasy, though full of hope.
Hmpf... With my skills, isn't success a forgone conclusion?

Of course... I wouldn't have been able to create such precious memories alone.

So, if just to commemorate that memory, why don't you join me for a tea party?
The pure unicorn represents my sincere feelings.
The warmth of the black tea represents my passionate heart.
At this moment, I formally extend an invitation to you, my comrade.

The venue will be somewhere most appropriate - my home.
Black tea, chocolate, and so long as you'll humor me...
I would be happy to play a song for you once more.
ReturnLetterCfg.10002_LetterTitleTwo:
Make the two of us the heroes of the next generation!

The devs have already sent me a copy of the demo.
I've no idea what the story is like, but I'm looking forward to finding out!
The dream I've held for many years has finally come true, and it's even with my trusted partner!
I had many nights of sweet dreams...

That's why... Partner, you've gotta come back, and quick!
I've already got the consoles all ready to go!
This time, there won't be any “Mighty Meow” or “Mini Meow.”
We'll play our own roles as we write a heroic story with our own hands!
ReturnLetterCfg.10003_LetterTitle:
It's been a while since we've seen each other.
Are you also busy with work?
Ah! Don't take things the wrong way. I'm writing this letter... Just as a routine gesture between comrades.

I've been very busy with the R&D of new products for the Hermes store.
Let me give you a preview!
We've got our eyes on the sweets market, and we're getting ready to launch a chocolate...
You remember, right? It was that one we came up with together.
The notes I've decided for this chocolate are “memory” and “sincerity.”
