RoleSkin.20146201_TskinDescription:
"Have you ever truly looked at the starry sky?"
"I heard there is a unique star for everyone, waiting alone in the universe, hoping someone would gaze at it."
"If one day you see an unusual light in the sky, that's probably your star winking at you."
"Where is my star? Well... that's a secret."

The girl never stops chasing the night sky.
Through countless nights under the stars, she patiently waits for that one star in the vast galaxy to reveal itself.
One day, the star winks at her.
And the entire night sky changes its colors.
RoleSkin.20107206_TskinDescription:
"How on earth am I supposed to protect this thing..." The detective worries, staring at the suitcase in the display case. "They've got such a valuable item out in the open. It's practically begging to be stolen."
A golden spark crosses the detective's round glasses.
“Wait a second. If it's not left in this fragile glass case but instead protected by a reliable detective like myself...”
Half an hour later, someone reports a bomb on the top floor! The guards rush off—a diversion by the thief. Suddenly, smoke blankets the lobby, and the display case shatters. The thief arrives as expected but immediately slips on a puddle of coffee milk, nearly falling.
As the thief struggles to regain balance, a small figure sneaks into the smoke and the broken display case.
By the time the guards return and see the damaged, empty display case, they gasp in shock—the Icarus Device has been stolen!
As the museum descends into chaos, the detective, who has been safely guarding the Icarus Device, checks her weapon and takes a deep breath.
"Get ready for the great detective's coffee reception!"
RoleSkin.20123102_Description:
During the Spring Festival, the "Dreams to Reality" exhibit inspired a trend among the Strinovians, leading to a collection of refined garments modeled after ancient mural attire.

"Ahem, stop staring at me and get back to work, everyone. The festival is approaching, but let's stay focused on our tasks."
RoleSkin.20205105_Description:
During the Spring Festival, the "Dreams to Reality" exhibit inspired a trend among the Strinovians, leading to a collection of refined garments modeled after ancient mural attire.

"Oh my, it feels like I'm about to ascend to the heavens in this outfit."
RoleSkin.20124109_Description:
During the Spring Festival, the "Dreams to Reality" exhibit inspired a trend among the Strinovians, leading to a collection of refined garments modeled after ancient mural attire.

"How do I look? It suits me, right? I've heard so many legends about ancient celestial beings, and it's my first time dressing up like one. This is so much fun!"
RoleSkin.20107206_Description:
"The most important ability of a detective is..."
"What is it?"
"Uh... Observing, summarizing, analyzing, and putting it into practice!"
"That's it? I expected some secrets. Don't forget you promised to catch the thief first."
"When is the thief planning to strike?"
"...Now."
"Oh! I better not waste time here! I'm off to find clues. See you!"

A girl with a coffee cup flits from a steam engine to an ancient whale fossil, exploring mischievously. In the retro museum, a battle between detective and thief is about to begin.
"I shouldn't have taken this job. I have no experience with thieves..." The detective nervously sips her coffee.
Her frustration centers around the exhibit in the glass case before her: the "Icarus Device." This legendary gadget, crafted with retro steam technology, uses intricate mechanisms to let a person fly—useless to Maddalena, but perfect for her quirky collection.
A notorious thief has issued a warning, vowing to snatch the Icarus Device in plain sight. Due to the bustling shopping festival, the warning arrives at the museum just a day before the scheduled heist. Desperate, the curator calls Urbino for help.
To cover her coffee expenses for the next month and the maintenance for her Fully Automatic Creative Retro Victorian Steampunk Gothic Hand-Operated Mechanical Latte Mocha Espresso Flat White Compression Modulating Machine, Maddalena jumps into action.
However...
RoleSkin.20112058_Description: “Combat and rock n' roll are not mutually exclusive.”
RoleSkin.20107201_TskinDescription:
"Today, I have to design a children's book for Astral Sanctuary. As for tomorrow, I promised my neighbor I'd help her design her living room..."
It is another incredibly fulfilling day for the girl who finds joy in helping others. But this time, you notice a hint of weariness in her expression.

"Hold on, Navigator. Don't move!"
"That's it! That's the look!"
The girl exclaims as if she has found the world's rarest treasure.
"Since it's your day off... Navigator, would you model for me?"
The girl approaches the person she trusts the most, sharing her unique warmth, her eyes filled with you and only you.
RoleSkin.20128201_TskinDescription:
【“What flower is this? It's an orchid.”
The floral fragrance of the tea wafts from the cups in front of Lawine and you.
The pale petals unfold in your cup of tea.
You notice that a similar flower is embroidered on her clothes.

“Orchids only bloom in spring, a season far too short in this world.”
As she sips some tea, the girl in front of you smiles, barely perceptible.
For her, this brief respite from all her responsibilities and duties is her spring.】
RoleSkin.20124206_TskinDescription:
“Look, Kokona-senpai! That character in the anime looks just like you!”
The screen shows a battle scene with Mecha Angel - Summer Yellow. “Red! Blue! Leave the grunts to me! Don’t worry; we agreed, right? Let’s have a barbecue after this battle—”
“Eh... Really? How so? But she got shot down right after saying that... Am I really that unreliable?”
“But that’s what makes Summer Yellow so amazing! No matter what she promises, she always returns safely. That’s why she’s called the 'Golden Phoenix'. She’s full of reassurance!”
“Is that so? I'd like to say a cool line like that sometime.”
“In that case, how about cosplaying as Summer Yellow and going to the Arton City Anime Convention with me?”
“Sounds like fun! Count me in!”
After that, Kokona pulled multiple all-nighters to finish watching Mecha Angel GEN, and hand-crafted an entire set of props with actual combat functionality. For a while, an urban legend circulated among fans that the Mecha Angels were actually real.
“Umm... I figured if I was going to do it, I might as well go all out. Maybe I went a bit too far?”
RoleSkin.20112206_TskinDescription:
“The person carrying out this mission needs to be sharp, swift, patient... and preferably knowledgeable about sharks.”
So, Fuchsia is chosen. Her mission is to put on a special diving suit and inject the frenzied shark with a tranquilizer.
For the first time, she doesn't need to hide and can meet a living shark face-to-face. This has always been her dream.
At the dreamlike bottom of the ocean, the shark does not reject her but instead circles her... No, the shark is circling the tailbone.
It was just a cold, lifeless tailbone, yet the shark instinctively chased it.
Even as she swims toward the shore, the shark mindlessly follows her.
Fuchsia finally understands the reason behind the shark's frenzy and that they are, after all, different creatures.
RoleSkin.20105201_TskinDescription:
【After playing a violin piece, Audrey sits next to you.
“Why do you still look so gloomy when I'm with you?”
“What are you worried about? The test we have to face? Or the inevitable collapse?”

She pours two cups of black tea and places one in front of you.
“Let go of all the troubles. Let us toast to hardship and... this world.”
As the cups touch, producing a crisp sound, the girl smiles confidently.】
RoleSkin.20137201_TskinDescription:
【As an idol, Kanami enjoys spending time on makeup and styles.
Whether it's a natural look or an elegant stage look, Kanami excels at putting them on, skillfully applying any makeup products.
As Kanami finishes her makeup, she draws a cute mark on the mirror with her lipstick.
“Navigator, will you be colored by my hues?”】
RoleSkin.20101201_TskinDescription:
Super gamer Michele has many stylish casual outfits. Of course, our cat lover prefers this cute cat-themed outfit, whether for its comfiness or the adorable kitty colors.

"Cats show their belly when they want to be friendly and feeling safe." The girl says, smiling.

Michele has changed her flashy gamer gear into a cute girl's outfit. Is the cat girl trying to tell you something with that change?
RoleSkin.20101206_TskinDescription:
Having become a frontline investigator, Michele carries with her the will of her father. When a badge number is reactivated, the pitiful criminals better tremble in fear, for the successor of the White Tiger will defeat every single one of them.

“Listen up! I have you surrounded! Surrender now!” Michele once intimidated suspects like this during operations.
And she kept her word, singlehandedly arresting over a dozen suspects.
"I thought I wouldn't see the light of day again. Was she going to devour us like a wild tiger?" a criminal recalls, trembling in fear.
RoleSkin.20105206_TskinDescription:
Rumor has it that as Grove Bank neared collapse, a barely-of-age Audrey single-handedly upheld her family's honor, inspiring the gown's name.
In the last surviving old photo, she stands fully armed, draped in a burnt cloak—her first time holding a gun.
“The throne is cast by iron. Saltpeter inscribes the glory... Was this truly my past style?”
“Always has been,” the butler replies.

Now, as the head of the Grove family, Audrey often revisits these old photos of herself.
Is she the same person as the girl in the photos? Does the name of the gown foretell the fate of her family?
As she stares at the photos, the girl in them seems to gaze back, awaiting answers.
RoleSkin.20137206_TskinDescription:
After the outbreak crisis, alien creatures overrun several key cities. The defense system centered around Komos is on the verge of collapse, plunging the region into an extremely unstable state of reverstring.
According to the Bureau of Anomalous Affairs, there's a direct link between the creatures' aggression and their emotional fluctuations. Certain special sounds can effectively suppress them. Upon learning this, Kanami races to the highest point in the world, the only place where her voice can reach every corner.
Kanami takes the sky as her stage and her voice as her weapon, launching into her grand performance. Waves of sound pierce the alien creatures, shattering their mutated crystals of delirium into dazzling "diamonds" that sparkle across the sky. With this, the diva completes her mission.
RoleSkin.20146206_TskinDescription:
The royal swordswoman, enchanting as a rose, gazes into the distance.
She sees nothing but carnage and rivers of blood.
The rose-decorated sword pierces an enemy's heart.
The rose is dyed in blood's hue; shadows cast wide their pall.
Her mind, like the breeze, wanders far, unconfined by any wall.
“For you alone, the flowers unveil their bloom; should they fade, what sorrow calls?”
RoleSkin.20128206_TskinDescription:
Broken weapons lie scattered on the battlefield as a biting wind sweeps through. Dust settles after yet another devastating battle, with no end in sight.
After a day's march, the general in red removes her armor, revealing snow-white garments and silk-black hair. Few know that this fearless leader is actually a woman.
On a cold, snowy night, outside the tents, once-silent plum blossoms reveal vibrant red. The general gazes at them, her thoughts drifting to a cherished friend far away.
After their last sparring session over tea, that friend had gifted her a plum blossom. She then left home, concealing her identity, to join a distant campaign.
Amidst the frigid blizzard and relentless warfare, perhaps only the red plums in deep snow understand her profound bond with the one who is both mentor and friend.
RoleSkin.20115206_TskinDescription:
The beautiful and noble Moon Goddess is truly captivating. Her deep, all-seeing eyes and gentle, accepting heart are enchanting, yet she becomes merciless and decisive when judging the guilty, erasing all with the sweep of her moonlit gown. She is the shared faith of all who walk the night.

People chase the same goal but arrive at different fates. Many claim to have seen Flavia; some find her kind and compassionate, others cold and unfeeling. Yet, few remember that in this world, the moon is never seen.
RoleSkin.20110206_TskinDescription:
The screen outside Urbino Business Alliance has been playing an advertisement: A blurry figure, just barely recognizable as male, moves through various Strinovan cities. His body is composed of shifting digital signals, appearing in bustling marketplaces, weaving through skyscrapers at night, and, at times, pixelating directly into a popular game. The ad ends with a mysterious: 1220. Passers-by stop and gaze at the screen, speculating on the meaning of the number.

A livestream with zero followers mysteriously appears on the homepage of the most popular streaming site at peak hours. The footage is completely empty, with only a spinning chair, and even the stream ID is censored with mosaic pixels. As curious viewers flood the stream, the mosaic gradually fades before completely disappearing, revealing the familiar number 1220. As the stream gains traction, a guitar appears mid-air, followed by Bai Mo holding it.

The livestream explodes in popularity, marking the beginning of Bai Mo's era as a top-tier streamer.
RoleSkin.20132206_TskinDescription:
Beneath the pressing dark clouds, the Lei Loong weaves through the urban jungle. In this vast city, there are many crimes she needs to put an end to.
She waves her hand, “warning” the armed street racers, while behind her, gangsters whose schemes she foiled chase relentlessly.
How many enemies have converged here? Too many to count...
For a moment, she nostalgically recalls the quiet days at the boxing gym. Has she grown tired of the constant confrontations?
As she finishes her last bag of chips, she leaps onto the roof of an ancient building. A clap of thunder roars, and the heavens seem to have answered with a thousand bolts, striking fear into the hearts of all criminals.
In that moment, she gazes not just at the criminals but also at the city's endless sea of lights—perhaps this is her silent answer.
RoleSkin.20205103_Description:
A blinding light, a fleeting illusion—no one can truly capture the beauty of a peacock's feather, nor escape the trickery of the deceiver.

"Just another trick on you."
RoleSkin.20109057_Description: In sharp contrast to Reiichi's indifferent demeanor, this outfit features patterns of raging flames. Even the coldest of tools need to be driven by heat.
RoleSkin.20101105_Description:
In stark contrast to her usual authoritative demeanor, Michele becomes a mischievous demon straight out of a fairy tale.
 
Knock, knock. “Open up. It's Investigator Michele from the underworld. I'm here to inspect your snack stash today!”
Donning this outfit, Michele appears happier than usual.
But she's still herself. So, it should be fine, right?
RoleSkin.20119108_Description:
Eika's exclusive idol costume. The bunny on her mask might be soft and cuddly, but the plaid puffy skirt and tank top give a real rockstar vibe. Just what kind of expression could this idol's mask be hiding?

"My face may be hidden behind a mask, but you can feel my sincerity, right?"
RoleSkin.20137208_NameShort: Century Idol - Light of the Embers
RoleSkin.20901001_Description: The question mark displayed on players who join mid-match
RoleSkin.20101051_Description:
Michele leapt at the chance to customize her own racing outfit for the Port Euler Jet Ski Grand Prix.

Three, two, one... Go!!!
RoleSkin.20131058_Description: In order to study the impact of letters on people's emotions, Yvette dons the courier's outfit, delivering letters to different households to feel their sentiments. However, when looking at the person she wants to send a letter to, Yvette notices her heartbeat suddenly accelerating.
RoleSkin.20133110_Description:
To blend into the nightlife of Neon City, Meredith dons a streetwear outfit she is not accustomed to. Her headphones help her shut out the city's restlessness and noise, allowing her to stay true to herself.

“I shall guide everyone in this city just as you have guided me.”
RoleSkin.20133101_Description:
While working for P.U.S, Meredith once led a team to explore the True Wilderness. She designed this outfit to embody the spirit of adventure.

“If explorers halt due to the fear of the unknown, it will undermine humanity's courage and future.”
RoleSkin.20205102_Description:
At the recent pool party, Galatea, a DJ under the Urbino music label, turned heads with her stylish ensemble. Attendees recall the moment she tossed her wide-brimmed straw hat into the pool, sparking a friendly scramble among partygoers. Somehow, by evening, the hat had made a surprising return to her head.




"I had a total blast! Count me in for the next one!"
RoleSkin.20109107_Description:
There is more to country life than just fields and farms. You need a skilled handyman who is a jack of all trades. Leaky roofs? Short-circuiting appliances? Whatever needs fixing, he has got you covered.

“What? You need me to take care of the P.U.S security squad instead of appliances? Very well. Leave it to me”
RoleSkin.20107101_Description:
It's been said that an explorer who can't fish isn't a true artist.
To visit the remote ecological zones in Strian's countryside for field sketches, Maddelena prepared this outdoor set. She journeys along the river, alternating between sketching and fishing, filling her canvas and fish basket.

"Yes! Got one! Don't run away! Taste my paint bubbles!”
RoleSkin.20112051_Description:
Since when
have we been trapped within the confines of towering steel?
The starry sky grows dim,
no longer illuminating the path arrived on.
RoleSkin.20109101_Description:
Reiichi's outfit for eavesdropping missions.
Blending in is part of being a spy, even in a café.

"Today, there will be... a different kind of rain."
RoleSkin.20109102_Description:
Reiichi's diving gear for his seaside vacation is mainly practical but adorned with a few stylish trinkets. It hints that there's more to him beneath the surface.

"Wow... Even underwater, the corals are stunning."
As Reiichi surfaces from his dive, a subtle smile graces his face. The typically aloof demeanor is replaced by genuine enjoyment of the beach escape.
"Relax. I'm actually quite easygoing."
You feel like you have seen a rare side of Reiichi.
RoleSkin.20131054_Description: A cute lab coat decorated with clovers. Hope, faith, love, and fortune —Yvette wishes all these good things to be with you.
RoleSkin.20105053_Description: An elegant outfit inspired by playing cards. Hearts, Diamonds, Spades, and Clubs... Where's the Ace? Of course, it's Audrey herself!
RoleSkin.20131109_Description:
Worn by Yvette during clinical trials to research Collapse Syndrome, this uniform symbolizes the dedication of a meticulous scientist. For her, a solid heartbeat is always a positive sign.

"Heartbeat at 60... 78... 110. All looks good. You're ready for discharge."
RoleSkin.20131103_Description:
Yvette's outfit for her internship at the café. On the navigator's advice, she took the job to improve her communication skills. Although Yvette tried to serve the customers, she was baffled to discover that they were more interested in serving her.

“Fay wouldn't know what to make of this either, sir...”
RoleSkin.20115109_Description:
Legend tells of Flavia, the immortal mistress of the Castle of Eternal Night, a stunning beauty who has existed for millennia. When the black moon ascends, a spirit butterfly carries the castle's invitation—a challenge and a test.

"I neither drink blood nor fear sunlight. If you're truly curious, why not see for yourself?"
RoleSkin.20110102_Description:
Rumor has it that there is a highly skilled young man who shows up in the auto shop from time to time. No matter what the malfunction is or the age of a race car, as long as he repairs and tunes it, the vehicle's performance will be enhanced. Everyone praises his repair skills, but few inquire about his identity - this is exactly what he aims to achieve.

"Check out the repair. There's nothing my wrench can't fix."
"However, the parts are severely worn. You gotta take care of your car, buddy."
"Feel like you've seen me before? Well, it's a large city. Perhaps you have; perhaps you haven't. Don't overthink it."
RoleSkin.20137111_Description:
As an idol, Kanami embraces the arrival of Spring Blessing by wearing outfits that capture the festive mood! This year's design theme is "Paper-Cutting," and she chose a bird pattern with a vintage flair, setting off a new fashion trend in the city.

"Fashion always comes back around. With a few modifications and some accessories, Kanami believes this outfit is stage-ready for performances too!"
RoleSkin.20115107_Description:
As a rookie investigator, Flavia is often sent on special missions due to her unique abilities. Everywhere she goes, she leaves behind the legend of the mystical purple butterflies.

"Ah, injured again... I've got to get better at this."
RoleSkin.20123001_Description: As head of the P.U.S Engineering Department, Leona oversees every project with unwavering dedication. Whenever she steps onto a construction site, whispers follow: "The boss doesn't miss a thing!"
RoleSkin.20137102_Description:
An outfit designed for the promotional event of Kanami's new song.
After several modifications, it strikes a perfect balance between the distance of an idol and the closeness of a maid. However, she seems to have another reason for liking this outfit...

"Kanami is everyone's idol, but... for now, let me provide you with an exclusive maid café experience."
RoleSkin.20108105_Description:
Nobunaga's street performance outfit shows his take on rock 'n' roll. Some say rock is about guitar solos, bass lines, and drum beats. Others see it as a spirit, a rebellion against hypocrisy, the city's voice, and a musical outcry. For Nobunaga, rock is a revolution, blending speed, power, and the bright burst of life.

"Chaos isn't just about overturning old rules; it’s the origin of a new order."
RoleSkin.20124054_Description: A work outfit similar to that of a taxi driver, yet exceptionally striking because of the wearer. Kokona says it is her disguise, but is that really the case?
RoleSkin.20105054_Description: The elegant blue dress with luxurious gold patterns is Audrey's go-to gown for formal occasions. As the face of Grove Enterprise, she sees social events as just another battlefield.
RoleSkin.20121053_Description:
No matter how dangerous the mission, Yugiri accepts it without flinching.

"Is it hard? I think it's fine. Leave the dangerous places to me."
RoleSkin.20133054_Description: The stunning violet blooms in the barren wilderness, not for others, but to shine alone. The beauty of a solitary orchid in a secluded valley needs no admiration.
RoleSkin.20105114_Description:
Audrey, the student council vice president, wears this haute couture uniform for major events. It incorporates the family crest, highlighting both the academy's prestige and her family's elegance.

"President? No, I'm not. But this uniform certainly is the symbol of the student council."
RoleSkin.20205008_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. The color scheme is said to be inspired by the fine red wine stored in her cellar.
RoleSkin.20121103_Description:
Spring Blessing has come again, and P.U.S designed a special uniform for its standout staff, including Yugiri. Her fondness for it is clear even if she doesn't say much.

"Was this custom-made for me? That explains all the questions about my tastes. I genuinely like it... I appreciate your consideration."
RoleSkin.20137054_Description: The cute pink wrapping paper encases the sweet cyan candies. Kanami's outfit perfectly highlights her charming sweetness.
RoleSkin.20137206_Description:
As the world faces the brink of collapse, Kanami reaches the pinnacle and end of her journey as an idol, becoming the embodiment of music and a vessel for souls. With all eyes on her, she sings a song of hope, using her power to rewrite the ending.

"I will become the eternal song of the century!"
RoleSkin.20110109_Description:
At the bustling alliance leader election, a streak of green lightning zips through to energetic music. Unlike his usual street dancer and graffiti king style, Bai Mo is dressed to the nines, looking dapper, yet his iconic smile still exudes a longing for freedom.

"If I am re-elected, we'll have 30 days of vacation each month!"
Bai Mo is taken aback by the tidal wave of cheers and applause.
"Wow, you're all more excited than I am!"
RoleSkin.20133103_Description:
The outfit Meredith wears while performing for displaced children at a charity event in Preton. Despite her expressionless face, the magician is still adored by the children.

“Magic is but a quantitative technique.”
RoleSkin.20120106_Description:
To celebrate Spring Blessing, Fragrans has designed a new combat uniform inspired by the koi fish. The mostly black and white uniform is accented with an elegant touch of red like a koi leaping out of an ink painting.

"Are you saying I look like I just walked out of a painting? Thank you. Being considered a personification of ancient art makes all the effort I spent designing this outfit worthwhile."
RoleSkin.20119105_Description:
In a world free of physical ailments, there are healers for the heart. The Scissors are known as radicals. And so, a regular high school girl must still conceal her true "identity."

"Fire purifies. Fire heals all."
RoleSkin.20110107_Description:
A mysterious man appeared at the arcade registration, trying to conceal his identity with sunglasses, a hat, and a fake mustache. Yet, the crowd still recognized him.

"I'm just an ordinary player. Being the organizer is a tall tale! I've contributed to the arcade scene; now I want to be a contestant!"
RoleSkin.20131104_Description:
When Yvette encounters bottlenecks in her research, she would occasionally slip out of the lab. No one knows where she goes, only that she would return with a satisfied look and continue to immerse in her work.
If you spot a bear in a milk tea shop, don't panic. Just act like you didn't see her, and she'll leave once she's had her sugar fix.

"Sugar is really important... That candy shop seems popular... Hmmm..."
RoleSkin.20131052_Description: An outfit in mysterious purple, featuring images of spider webs, bats, and an ancient castle. Even though this is a fairy tale, Yvette might not necessarily be the princess.
RoleSkin.20109006_Description:
Before the fireflies gathered into a bright moon,
I had never truly seen the moonlight.
RoleSkin.20121052_Description: Adding plenty of matcha powder to the cake turns its usual melt-in-your-mouth sweetness into a touch of bitterness. Thankfully, the orange slices add a hint of sweetness to the aftertaste.
RoleSkin.20121102_Description:
While designing her stage outfit, Yugiri expresses her love for vintage aesthetics. The final product is reminiscent of a Y2K-era idol from a retro poster.

"I usually only see this style in magazines... but dressing up like this once in a while feels pretty nice."
RoleSkin.20137109_Description:
Kanami's performance outfit for the Galactic Concert. Songs and battles across the galaxy were once the eternal theme of a sci-fi series. With this outfit, Kanami transforms into a diva singing across the galaxy, expressing her unique interpretation.

"Do you remember the galaxy and love?"
RoleSkin.20112053_Description: The phantom that walks the streets at night is none other than Fuchsia.
RoleSkin.20101056_Description: Upholding fairness and justice is a code every Investigator must follow. Michele is determined to uphold this principle completely.
RoleSkin.20146058_Description: The moon rises on a summer night, the grass sways in the wind, and dragonflies flutter. Close your eyes and enjoy this tranquil moment by her side.
RoleSkin.20146102_Description:
The nurse's uniform is angelically pure, but beneath its gentle appearance, there lurks danger.

"You haven't fully recovered. Please stay in bed."
"Perhaps I should stay a bit longer."
"...How about forever?"

In her story, she will protect you until the end of time.
RoleSkin.20105051_Description: A personal redesign of Audrey's mercenary outfit, inspired by the hot cocoa coffee she had at noon the day she came up with the design.
RoleSkin.20105201_Description: A casual outfit Audrey wears on vacation. Occasionally, she puts this elegant dress on to enjoy her rare holiday with you.
RoleSkin.20105104_Description:
A Far Eastern garment that was restored by Audrey's costume designer.
It is said that those who pray devoutly while wearing this outfit will obtain mysterious powers to dispel disasters.

“I pray to no one. However... if you were by my side, I’d have the power to dispel any disaster...”
RoleSkin.20107051_Description: She wanders in the red orchard, leaving traces of art on her canvas. By chance, I am drawn to the playful red, lingering on the paths.
RoleSkin.20119106_Description:
Her flames burn hotter than the desert sands. As she moves, ashes rise, heralding an incoming wave of heat.

“One must burn the old shell to gain new strength.”
RoleSkin.20122001_Description: She lurks in the shadows like a phantom, descending on her victims as if she were the Grim Reaper. Her presence is elusive yet omnipresent, just like death itself.
RoleSkin.20115206_Description:
Legends say that a heartfelt prayer to the moon will summon the Moon Goddess's response. To her devoted followers, she bestows blessings; to the deceptive, she unleashes divine punishment. It's the tale whispered to children through the ages.

"Divine creations and creations of the divine. Born from faith, as long as belief endures, so shall I."
RoleSkin.20128206_Description: This majestic and elegant attire of a warrior highlights the fearless bravery of the charge into battle. The eye-catching bright red garment resembles a red plum on a cold night, revealing a hint of femininity.
RoleSkin.20107054_Description: This childish blueberry milk outfit suits Maddelena perfectly. After all, only with the heart of a child can one create true beauty.
RoleSkin.20105103_Description: The girl's graceful figure resembles a willow with fine branches, her elegant gauze dress fluttering in the wind. Dressed as a classical dancer, Audrey exudes an indescribable exotic charm with her every move.
RoleSkin.20133102_Description:
What started as a curious experiment quickly became Meredith's secret hobby—drawing her ideal world in manga. But even in the world of manga, there are unavoidable challenges—the relentless deadline that every manga artist must battle.

"Yes, it’s me… pushing back the next mission. Why? Oh, just got a date with the demon king called Deadline."
RoleSkin.20124051_Description: An engineer-styled combat suit, adorned with playful construction site markings. This outfit is a memento from Kokona's past adventures.
RoleSkin.20108053_Description: The sleek, form-fitting outfit, with an old letter tucked at the waist, gives Nobunaga the appearance of a diligent postman. One may wonder: To whom will the most important letter be delivered?
RoleSkin.20108109_Description:
During the manor's dinner party, the butler tasked with decorating the trees appeared deep in thought.

"It's not about looking serious; the manor needs someone to step up and—uh, handle things in any situation."
RoleSkin.20128056_Description: If you gaze long enough into an abyss, the abyss will gaze back into you. Yet, she remains undeterred.
RoleSkin.20124201_Description: Kokona's loungewear during her vacation. Even at home, she is always ready for the next adventure.
RoleSkin.20124110_Description:
Kokona's custom combat suit designed for her mission on the Seeda Peninsula. It incorporates traditional local craftsmanship, making it suitable for all terrains and resistant to the area's unique climate challenges.

"The path to uncovering the truth is fraught with obstacles, but a brave heart will lead us to hope."
RoleSkin.20124009_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform, inspired by sand and dry wood colors, offers excellent camouflage in the Gobi Desert.
RoleSkin.20121056_Description:
Yugiri still remembers the darkness that once trapped her, yet in vast solitude, she stubbornly found her way forward.

"Do you see the stars under the sea? They are proof of the little jellyfish striving to find light."
RoleSkin.20121055_Description:
Yugiri loves the season when violets bloom. She could lie in a sea of purple that matches her perfectly. Endless romance and dreams would wash over her.

"Maybe in dreams, I can grasp a chance for happiness."
RoleSkin.20121002_Description: A recolored version of Yugiri's combat suit. It features a touch of soft purple, apparently her favorite color.
RoleSkin.20121007_Description: A recolored version of Yugiri's combat suit. Delicate yellow, like an unripe apricot, needing more time to mature.
RoleSkin.20121006_Description: A recolored version of Yugiri's combat suit. The deep pink shade adds a mature vibe, making her seem more reliable in battle.
RoleSkin.20121005_Description: A recolored version of Yugiri's combat suit. The deep green shade resembles a stroll through a forest, where sunlight is filtered and dappled.
RoleSkin.20121004_Description: A recolored version of Yugiri's combat suit. Adorned with youthful pink accents, it surprisingly suits her well.
RoleSkin.20121003_Description: A recolored version of Yugiri's combat suit. With a fresh and elegant tone, it would be perfect for a spring outing.
RoleSkin.20205101_Description:
As the countdown ticks down, the winner of this year's Stardust Magician is about to be announced. With a fleeting, languid smile, countless crimson silhouettes take the stage, resembling scarlet ibises returning to their roost, as every spotlight gathers upon them.

"Tonight's glory belongs to me, and many more of me."
RoleSkin.20128058_Description: Is the deep blue rhythm coursing through my mind an echo of the world's illusion or a true resonance from the depths of my soul?
RoleSkin.20131057_Description: A lazy afternoon is best suited for a cup of rich mocha brewed by apprentice barista Yvette.
RoleSkin.20124111_Description:
Redesigned by Handicraft Club President Kokona, this uniform's sleek design includes plenty of tool storage for her creative ideas.

"Studying all the time is dull. Let's make some cool inventions together after class today."
RoleSkin.20107052_Description: A blue painter's outfit with delicate hand-painted patterns, one of Maddelena's favorites. It sways gracefully, like the shifting starry sky.
RoleSkin.20115101_Description:
I invited Flavia to go out with me. To my surprise, she actually said yes.

"Hmm? What's the matter? The weather's lovely, and even butterflies need their sunshine."
RoleSkin.20128107_Description:
Lawine's fitted model outfit for a performance at Laurel Gallery. The elegant, mysterious gown, combined with Lawine's cold demeanor, makes the performance even more enigmatic.

“Target location confirmed. Commencing operation.”
RoleSkin.20128102_Description:
The outfit Lawine wore during a victory celebration for The Scissors. The clash of leather and metal is as punk as it gets. She screams at the world in rebellion.

“Since the world has no future to begin with, why speak of sin?”
RoleSkin.20128105_Description:
Originally there to observe P.U.S. at the Apple Festival, Lawine ended up in a fairy tale play. Her usual calm exterior is betrayed by lively ears and a tail that give away her thoughts.

"Hold on, who said I was enjoying this?"
RoleSkin.20128108_Description:
Lawine's special operations combat suit. The camouflage pattern helps her blend seamlessly into the environment, even without using stealth techniques.

“Clear. All areas secured. Victory is ours.”
RoleSkin.20124056_Description: Picking up shells, digging for crabs... Wear the summer beach on your body to enjoy the joy of beach treasure hunting at any time.
RoleSkin.20124057_Description: Legend speaks of an explorer from a distant land who chased the sun in search of truth. Her story, captured in local murals, hints at a familiar figure we might recognize.
RoleSkin.20146056_Description: Celestia's eye-catching green dress sways in the wind, as sweet and cool as a summer breeze. Talking to her while she's wearing it feels refreshing and delightful, like enjoying a cold, sweet drink.
RoleSkin.20205053_Description: As a magician with a knack for card tricks, she's unmatched in any card game—a true master indeed. Just remember, losing to Galatea is all part of the fun!
RoleSkin.20120104_Description:
From myriad angles, the city's vivid lights streak into the night sky. In the center of the blooming light stands a figure listening to the sounds of the city and taking in its scents.

“Misunderstanding, hatred, violence... I must rid the world of such things.”
RoleSkin.20128103_Description:
An early version of the P.U.S investigator's uniform, designed to emphasize strength and competence. This uniform holds Lawine's treasured memories.

"Do you wonder if I truly resent P.U.S.? Perhaps..." Lawine murmurs, fiddling with the edge of the uniform, lost in thought.
"...But what I truly despise is the 'illusion' that blinds us."
“Whether in my P.U.S. days or now, that has never changed.”
RoleSkin.20132106_Description:
Ming's tailored model outfit for a performance at Laurel Gallery. To aid her special performance, Ming chose to leave out elaborate decorations, ensuring every inch of the garment is form-fitting.

“If rebellion is the only way to achieve justice, then I don't mind going against the grain.”
RoleSkin.20132006_Description: Ming's spare combat suit features an orange-red hue, reminiscent of a sunset's glow.
RoleSkin.20132004_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform. Her heart is as pure as the clear lake in her homeland.
RoleSkin.20132005_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform. Despite her bold character, she does not mind lurking in the dark of the night.
RoleSkin.20132008_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform in purple, resembling the clouds at the edge of the sky.
RoleSkin.20132003_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform in green, resembling the beautiful dream she fights for.
RoleSkin.20132007_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform in blue, symbolizing her lofty aspirations.
RoleSkin.20132002_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform. The bright yellow top makes her as dazzling as the sun.
RoleSkin.20146001_Description: Celestia wears this dress while working at Astral Sanctuary. Its twinkling star patterns symbolize Astral Sanctuary's creed of not giving up on any patient.
RoleSkin.20146012_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in soft purple. The Purple Star - another name for the North Star.
RoleSkin.20121054_Description:
Spring has arrived, and P.U.S planned a team-building event, bringing along Yugiri, who rarely leaves her room. They even made her a special outfit. She put it on somewhat awkwardly.

"I hope it doesn't look too strange on me."
RoleSkin.20108055_Description: The best investigators are also great drivers, able not only to catch up with criminals in street chases but also to not break the speed limit. How does he do it?
RoleSkin.20128055_Description: As the moon waxes and wanes, people come and go. The only constant is change. An unchanging world is but a reflection of the moon.
RoleSkin.20110055_Description: A casual outfit in refreshing blue and white. Relax on a beach chair, sip a cool glass of coconut water, and enjoy your vacation with the sea breeze.
RoleSkin.20128051_Description: As the maple leaves fall, the interwoven red and white symbolizes Lawine's heart - once beautiful and pure, now tainted by the flames of war.
RoleSkin.20101055_Description: Wearing this pink outfit straight out of a fairy tale, Michele, together with Pawtector, guards the fairy tale kingdom of children's dreams.
RoleSkin.20133105_Description:
Meredith's outfit for the Ancient Civilizations event embodies the mythic allure of the Moon Goddess, blending classical elegance with lunar grace, while highlighting her cat-like charm.

"As the sacred guardian ensures wellness for all, I also witness the prosperity we share."
RoleSkin.20133003_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform, featuring her familiar colors. Perhaps, deep inside her, there is a blueprint of the future.
RoleSkin.20133006_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform in red, matching the color of The Scissors. The rusty blade of yesteryear shall hew an iron path.
RoleSkin.20133004_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform. Its gray-brown color evokes the scorching desert sands, with shadows growing deeper as the sun blazes brighter.
RoleSkin.20133007_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform. Its deep green color resembles ancient trees, blossoming with new buds after a long slumber.
RoleSkin.20133002_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform in purple, resembling litmus paper. Using herself as a measure, she gauges the balance of the world.
RoleSkin.20133008_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform in light green, resembling the tender buds of spring. A new hope needs nurturing and care.
RoleSkin.20133005_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform. Its deep verdigris color symbolizes the beginning of change.
RoleSkin.20121057_Description: Plum petals rest on branches, melting to usher in the coming spring.
RoleSkin.20146101_Description:
A dreamy dress with a lavish, intricate design, seemingly drawn from a well-known fairy tale.

"What lies in the dream world?"
"A queen, tea parties, and lovely dresses?"
"What else?"
"And the guiding Mr. Rabbit!"

People often assume her dreams dwell solely in fairy tales, filled with whimsical beauty. Yet, they also hold memories of real people.
RoleSkin.20121001_Description: P.U.S tailored a special combat suit for Yugiri with string energy suppression, serving as both shield and restraint.
RoleSkin.20121101_Description:
Yugiri qualified to attend the P.U.S. ball, with Yvette preparing her outfit. The shy researcher girl held up a delicate ballet dress, whispering, "I hope you like it... Um, it'll look great on you, Yugiri."

"Though she's so nervous talking to me, she insisted on preparing the outfit, saying 'someone did it for her before.' People at P.U.S. really are quite peculiar."
RoleSkin.20101053_Description: Whenever P.U.S roads are blocked due to weather, Michele never hesitates to take action. Clad in waterproof gear and equipped with warning signs, she becomes a striking figure in the rain.
RoleSkin.20101052_Description: Michele wears this outfit whenever there are holiday festivities. The vibrant colors and festive pattern put a joyful spirit in the air!
RoleSkin.20121051_Description: Yugiri prefers to make herself some warm, frothy steamed milk using the leftover milk after others prepare their lattes. It's not bitter but wonderfully fragrant, like swallowing a cloud.
RoleSkin.20115057_Description: Jellyfish drift through the sea like butterflies flutter through the air. It's rumored that Flavia designed this outfit, inspired by a visit to the aquarium.
RoleSkin.20120107_Description:
The corridor behind the Castle of Eternal Night leads to a garden lush with countless strange and eerie plants. People often wonder how the mistress, Fragrans, keeps them so vibrant, but none dare to ask.

"How do I nourish the plants? My special cultivation agent, of course. Hm? Why do you look disappointed?"
RoleSkin.20132103_Description:
The beach and the waves, music and dancing—it's the perfect retreat for a warrior like Ming. A brief moment of joy prepares her for fiercer battles ahead.

"This beach isn't half bad. Finally, a chance to relax." As she arrives, Ming reveals a rare smile. "Tonight, we sing and celebrate! Tomorrow, we fight as one!"

Who knows how many companions she'll outdrink tonight...
RoleSkin.20112052_Description: The act of protecting lives is the only thing more noble than life itself.
RoleSkin.20128052_Description: The elegant outfit resembles an ancient scroll of majestic mountains. The classical attire reflects Lawine's beautiful yet cold demeanor.
RoleSkin.20131055_Description: A pale pink lab coat adorned with cherry blossoms, snowy mountains, and a bright moon. Yvette seems to stand in the wind, with petals gently falling on her shoulders.
RoleSkin.20109054_Description: The light blue denim jacket is full of vitality and passion, creating a sharp contrast with Reiichi's indifferent expression. Beneath his cold demeanor, powerful energy surges.
RoleSkin.20112055_Description: Games can sometimes be deadly. At least, she believes so.
RoleSkin.20105052_Description: Audrey puts on this cute dress whenever she strolls along the beach. Only then does she reveal her tender side.
RoleSkin.20107102_Description:
Wearing this outfit, Maddelena appears sweet and energetic, like a dazzling neon light weaving through the streets. As an artist, she occasionally indulges in the extraordinary.

"Hiya! Good evening! Woo!"
With a face full of excitement, she glides by on her roller skates.
Her elegant figure and the flickering rainbow lights dazzle onlookers.
Whatever this whimsical girl does, it is always in the name of "gathering inspiration."
RoleSkin.20107055_Description:
A traveling outfit designed by Maddelena.
On the Ferris wheel in the amusement park, the girl in light pink gazes at the fireworks lighting up the sky, silently cherishing this unique inspiration.
RoleSkin.20107053_Description: Donning a simple and practical outfit, Maddelena embarks on a journey alone, resembling a courier on an urgent delivery. Only then does she realize that the world is much larger than she imagined.
RoleSkin.20122101_Description:
Mara's custom combat suit for her mission on the Seeda Peninsula is inspired by legendary local designs. This suit excels in stealth operations and simultaneously earns the support of the local community.

"Those who walk in darkness need not only gaze into the abyss; they have the power to ignite a light in the long night."
RoleSkin.20122051_Description: Mara's custom outfit in green, resembling vibrant greenery that flourishes as a ray of sunlight pierces through towering mountains.
RoleSkin.20122006_Description: Mara's spare combat uniform in yellow. The striking color accompanies her as she walks across the vast earth.
RoleSkin.20122007_Description: Mara's spare combat uniform with a touch of red to its purple base.
RoleSkin.20122003_Description: Mara's spare combat uniform in blue. The bold, deep color is as profound as the impression she makes.
RoleSkin.20122004_Description: Mara's spare combat uniform in green, reflecting her strong personality.
RoleSkin.20122005_Description: Mara's spare combat uniform in purple, symbolizing her elegance while exuding a sense of authority.
RoleSkin.20122002_Description: Mara's spare combat uniform in azure. She leaves behind but a shadow as she moves in the dark of the night.
RoleSkin.20122054_Description: Mara's modified combat uniform in yellow, resembling a lightning bolt that warns of impending danger.
RoleSkin.20122055_Description: Mara's modified combat uniform featuring psychedelic electronic patterns, resembling fluctuating sound waves.
RoleSkin.20122052_Description: Mara's modified combat uniform inspired by her favorite childhood drink from her hometown, though its taste might be considered a bit too intense.
RoleSkin.20122053_Description: Mara's modified combat uniform inspired by bats. Much like bats, Mara often remains hidden during the day and active at night.
RoleSkin.20120105_Description:
Fragrans loves snowy winter nights. She often stands under a streetlight, gazing at the sky as snowflakes fall. To think such pure white comes from the deep blue sky - perhaps it is nature's gift.

“When snowflakes fall into your palm, they don't disappear; they become a part of you.”
RoleSkin.20120008_Description: An alternative color scheme for Faglan's lab coat, offering a fresh bitterness that lingers intriguingly.
RoleSkin.20120055_Description: The outfit Fragrans wore when visiting the Sea of Blossoms. On that snowy day, plum blossoms bloomed on the corners of her fluttering clothes, covering her in their faint scent.
RoleSkin.20110206_Description:
As the leader of the Urbino Alliance, Bai Mo has endorsed the digital streaming equipment invented by the alliance's entertainment group, creating a miracle in the streaming world by gaining a million followers overnight! He has now added another title to his name - the trend-setting top-tier streamer. Clearly, he has adapted well to this identity and is ready to stir up another storm in the world.

“Look at me, look at me! Am I not interesting? Uh... a monster that devours attention? Is that how they describe me? Once you open my stream, you'll never close it, like an addiction?”
“How is that an insult? That's the best compliment I've ever received!!!”
RoleSkin.20108054_Description: The white shirt paired with a brown jacket and tie gives Nobunaga an air of elegance and unattainability, making him smell of aromatic coffee beans.
RoleSkin.20131056_Description: Under the simple white and blue coat, Yvette's orange socks evoke the sweetness of soda. Though usually introverted and shy, Yvette occasionally shows this sweet side.
RoleSkin.20132052_Description: With a green top resembling leaves and orange-yellow bottoms resembling flowers, Ming is dressed like a coltsfoot, symbolizing freedom. She vows that hunger and oppression will end, and coltsfoot flowers will bloom again on this land.
RoleSkin.20120056_Description: The air itself is odorless; what we smell are tiny molecules. This fresh, fragrant scent comes from the pulp and oils of citrus fruits—consider it a gift from her.
RoleSkin.20107001_Description: A simple yet artistic painter's outfit. Rather than elaborate attire, Maddelena cares more about the harmony of colors.
RoleSkin.20101113_Description:
Michele wore this outfit when invited as a volunteer representative to a pool party. To fully enjoy the pool, she styled her hair into a neat, cute braid and paired it with pineapple sunglasses.

"Doing good deeds has finally paid off. I got invited to a pool party! I, the gaming master, will take you all down in the water gun battle!"
RoleSkin.20101109_Description:
Michele's ski suit for the Winter Wilderness Challenge. A thick cotton jacket with a snow leopard-patterned fur trim, highlighting her cuteness as well as her zest for life.

“Come on. Can you keep up?”
RoleSkin.20101106_Description:
Michele's work uniform at the candy house. Michele volunteers to work undercover at the bustling new amusement park to prevent accidents.
Suddenly, a member of The Scissors appears in the crowd, putting Michele on high alert. But as their eyes briefly meet, they silently ignore each other, both seeing joy in the other's smile.

"If this is a fleeting dream, let it last forever."
RoleSkin.20101001_Description: Michele incorporates her favorite cat elements into her uniform, giving it a playful touch while maintaining the professionalism expected of a P.U.S investigator.
RoleSkin.20101013_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a dull grayish-red, perfect for blending in with The Scissors.
RoleSkin.20101201_Description: Michele's carefully matched casual outfit, sharing the more pleasant meow time with you.
RoleSkin.20146053_Description: The candies adorn the dress with rainbow colors as her aura blooms in the summer. What color will the next rainbow candy be?
RoleSkin.20108102_Description:
The form-fitting swimwear and beach shorts, while simple, highlight Nobunaga's remarkable presence. In this brief respite, he seeks solitude, enjoying the sea breeze on his face.

Amidst the joyous seaside holiday, Nobunaga reclines alone on a beach chair, gazing at the sky.
Is something troubling him? When asked, he denies any issues.
"I'm just reflecting on my future and my worth."
"Stay with me for a bit, won't you? Perhaps your presence will strengthen my resolve."
RoleSkin.20105055_Description: The clash of black tea and cherry blossoms creates a unique springtime flair. When Audrey dons this outfit, her mood seems to lighten with the season.
RoleSkin.20133104_Description:
A refined and professional cafe uniform, personally tailored by Meredith. With her precise timepiece, she closely monitors every movement in the cafe.

"Mind if I observe and take notes on you up close?"
RoleSkin.20112109_Description:
Fuchsia redesigned the uniform for the Go-Home Club, using precious free time to inspire a love for heading straight home after school.

"The best part of school ending is finding fun outside—like fresh taiyaki."
RoleSkin.20112056_Description: Fuchsia's disguise as a café employee. Sharks might not like coffee, but the rich aroma of caramel coffee adds a touch of warmth to her frosty demeanor.
RoleSkin.20146054_Description: Donning this gilded teal dress, Celestia looks like a gorgeous princess. Be careful not to touch her, for the thorns are prickly.
RoleSkin.20122102_Description:
Mara, the Undead Countess surrounded by rumors and secrets, has reappeared at the grand banquet of the Castle of Eternal Night. Clearly, the spirit butterfly has brought a distinguished guest.

"An intruder? Seriously? Look at my invitation before you say another word."
RoleSkin.20119005_Description: Eika’s winter uniform. Breathe in the cold air and gaze at the clear blue sky.
RoleSkin.20119002_Description: Eika's summer edition uniform. Perfect for napping among the dense trees and grass.
RoleSkin.20119008_Description: Eika's early spring uniform. As the winter snow melts, green sprouts once more.
RoleSkin.20119003_Description: Eika's spring edition uniform. Rushing to campus amidst a flurry of petals and pollen.
RoleSkin.20119004_Description: Eika's fall edition uniform. Amidst the falling leaves, she savors the aroma of roasted sweet potatoes.
RoleSkin.20119006_Description: Eika's worn-out uniform. It has been worn and washed many times, but she still cherishes it.
RoleSkin.20119007_Description: Eika’s taro colored uniform. To be honest, it only turned purple after being put in the wrong wash basket.
RoleSkin.20115052_Description: Flavia's formal attire for the P.U.S award ceremony. She won't stop there; she'll keep climbing until no one is left to bestow honors upon her.
RoleSkin.20115054_Description: Flavia's custom outfit. The viper lurks in the water, waiting for its thirsty prey. No, she is not the viper; she is the hunter waiting next to it.
RoleSkin.20115056_Description: Flavia's custom outfit. The fragrant and serene season has quietly arrived. The restless cocoon transforms, spreading its wings and dancing into the shadowy bloom of spring.
RoleSkin.20115053_Description: Flavia's custom lavender outfit. Its subtle fragrance lulls you to sleep amidst the dance of butterflies.
RoleSkin.20115007_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. A dim flame that has lost its warmth burns coldly like a phantom.
RoleSkin.20115003_Description: Flavia's spare uniform, resembling an unfathomable deep lake.
RoleSkin.20115004_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. The bud that has endured the cold winter waits for spring to bloom.
RoleSkin.20115005_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. The butterfly folds its wings, hiding among the decayed leaves.
RoleSkin.20115002_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. Butterfly wings flutter with the breeze, teasingly drifting near and far, always just out of reach.
RoleSkin.20115006_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. Lies and truth become indistinguishable, blending into the purple night.
RoleSkin.20108051_Description: The black and blue electronic-style outfit, featuring a walkie-talkie emblazoned with a record pattern, adds a touch of fashion to the typically stoic Nobunaga.
RoleSkin.20123103_Description:
Leona's outfit as a gaming event staff member reveals her carefree side. With her managing the event, everything should be organized... right?

"Hey, you with the strange look and suspicious behavior! Stop for questioning! Hey! No running!"
RoleSkin.20123005_Description: Leona's spare combat uniform in brown. Towering structures are built layer by layer. Ordinary rocks are the foundation of all things.
RoleSkin.20123006_Description: Leona's spare combat uniform in pink, enhancing her composed and approachable aura.
RoleSkin.20123007_Description: Leona's spare combat uniform in purple, exuding her elegance.
RoleSkin.20123004_Description: Leona's spare combat uniform in azure. The vast blue sky reflects the boldness and ambitions of builders.
RoleSkin.20123002_Description: Leona's spare combat uniform in army green, highlighting her disciplined and serious personality.
RoleSkin.20123003_Description: Leona's spare combat uniform in green, inspired by vast prairies that wait for visitors in silence.
RoleSkin.20123053_Description:
Leona's meticulous work habits extend into her personal life as well. Anyone lucky enough to sit in her passenger seat must first go through a round of questioning before enjoying the ride.

“Have you fastened your seatbelt? Check again.”
RoleSkin.20124101_Description:
A fun outfit for the concert of Duckyucky, the virtual idol. With a cute avant-garde design, this limited outfit is treasured by Kokona.

"Are you ready, Kokona? Duckyucky's concert is about to start!"
"Of course... Oh no!"
"W-What's going on? What was that noise...?"
"Something's happening! Emergency mission!"
And so, the girl, dressed in her fun outfit, rushes to the front line.
RoleSkin.20131206_TskinDescription:
Even though Yvette joined P.U.S as a senior researcher, her shy and socially anxious personality is hard to shake. She often pulls up her hoodie to blend into the background, unwittingly earning the "weirdo" label.
"Isn't she more like an animal than a human? Living on instinct is just sad."
"A workaholic freak, like a puppet."
"Just like her soulless robot bear."

It's okay, just block it all out and move away quickly, and those hurtful words won't reach you… Yvette quickened her step. Suddenly, two familiar faces appeared in front of her.
"Yvette, why aren't you checking your messages? Have you thought about what to wear for the P.U.S ball next month? Need any advice?" Michele asked with a cheerful grin.
"The ball? Uh..." Yvette’s face flushed with unease. "Is it the kind where you wear fancy dresses? I... don't really have anything suitable, and honestly, it feels a bit embarrassing..."
"No worries! We've got plenty of time. Whether you want to buy a dress or make one, we can help you out!" Kokona declared confidently, pumping her fist. "The most important thing is for you to shine at the ball and prove those gossipers wrong."
Kokona’s voice rang out for all to hear, purposefully: "Yvette isn’t some weirdo. She has lots of friends who really love her!"
"Michele, Kokona..." Yvette said softly, touched by their support. "Okay...! I've sewn for Fay before, so I should be able to create something for myself. I'll count on you both for fashion tips!"

A single snowflake may melt before touching the ground, but together they gain the courage to dance in the wind.
RoleSkin.20123052_Description:
Although Leona knows there are backup generators at the construction site, she still makes it a habit to check the equipment and its settings twice before starting work each day.

“We've got sufficient power. We can start anytime!”
RoleSkin.20205104_Description:
Galatea pairs a fluffy beret with her plaid stage outfit, adding a hint of softness and innocence to her elegant, mature image.

"This hat... doesn't it look just like snow settling on my head?"
RoleSkin.20205107_Description:
Galatea, the multi-time eSports champion known for her swift, dynamic moves, has entered this year's tournament to much anticipation. Her trendy outfit at the registration event has quickly become a hit among young fans.

"Watch closely—my bullet magic is a one-time show!"
RoleSkin.20128054_Description: The record player imagery on the outfit seems to constantly play melodies of the past, occasionally stirring Lawine's memories of bygone times.
RoleSkin.20132054_Description: A brisk outdoor outfit decorated with antler emblems. Ming often dons it when wandering in the wilderness, recalling her vibrant homeland while igniting a new fighting spirit.
RoleSkin.20120103_Description:
Fragrans follows the map in search of mythic ingredients in the Cosmite desert. She has changed into a cooler outfit to endure the scorching heat.

“Follow the scent. You can't read maps with a blindfold on.”
RoleSkin.20109055_Description: As a sniper, Reiichi has also participated in frontal assaults. Dressed in jungle-style attire, he is brave and ruthless, always managing to remain patient until the mission starts.
RoleSkin.20132051_Description: Dressed in a white, red, and gold combat uniform, Ming resembles a messenger calling upon holy fire to punish the wicked. Shoot and burn until true dawn arrives.
RoleSkin.20132108_Description:
Ming, the Music Club's lead guitarist, wears a custom Campus Open Day outfit for her performance. The design combines dazzling patterns with a vintage flair, creating a unique and expressive look.

"Are you ready? Let's set the stage ablaze with an unbeatable melody!"
RoleSkin.20119103_Description:
The summer sea is unlikely to remain calm, as the brilliant luster of spark fish takes center stage. Through fire and passion, they ignite a glorious storm beneath the waves.

“I can show you a sight - the seabed dyed red by hot winds.”
RoleSkin.20123054_Description:
The design of this uniform is inspired by one of P.U.S Engineering's exotic exploration missions. The mysterious shifting sands, towering stone pillars, and vividly carved mythical beasts left a lasting impression on Leona.

“These are the marks of an ancient civilization. If possible, I would like to preserve them in our new buildings.”
RoleSkin.20109056_Description: This outfit, adorned with crossed swords, resembles an ancient pirate captain's attire. Reiichi does not fear the curse of the sea, for he has long cursed himself.
RoleSkin.20137052_Description: A performance costume featuring a shooting star pattern. The fluttering starlight resembles Kanami's gorgeous dance moves.
RoleSkin.20132101_Description:
A black outfit designed for nighttime operations. Originally meant to blend seamlessly into the dark, Ming insisted on adding a touch of dark red, like a quietly burning flame—subtle yet unyielding. She will chase the night and drive it away.

“Go home, kids. The night is my battlefield.”
RoleSkin.20105108_Description:
In a ballroom of clinking glasses and swirling gowns, the star of the evening arrives fashionably late. She has shed the fierce spirit of a unicorn, draped in a deep-hued gown. Gracefully, she approaches her chosen dance partner, her skirt fluttering like the wings of a butterfly in the moonlight.

"Forgive me. I took a little extra time to find a dress worthy of our pairing."
RoleSkin.20107056_Description: Trying to figure out how to express feelings through creation, Maddelena takes a part-time job as a courier. She believes that letters are an important medium to convey one's intentions. She has designed her backpack in the shape of a mailbox, inviting the delivery of any precious sentiments.
RoleSkin.20101054_Description: Michele occasionally puts on this casual outfit and goes hiking in her free time. Be careful not to mistake her for a wildcat in the bamboo forest.
RoleSkin.20123051_Description:
Besides handling construction, P.U.S Engineering is also responsible for preliminary site investigations and surveys. As for why the target location this time is an ancient castle... well, that is another story.

“All engineering personnel, follow me and number off!”
RoleSkin.20124206_Description:
A Superstring Agent codenamed Summer Yellow. She is a member of the Mecha Angels, a secret special unit of P.U.S assembled to combat The Collapse and save the world with the power of love and peace.

—Official Artbook of the popular anime "Mecha Angel GEN"
RoleSkin.20109053_Description: In his crisp white attire, Reiichi looks like a young doctor. But in reality, he's only skilled in battlefield emergency care.
RoleSkin.20115106_Description:
A special host joins the midnight radio station of Neon City. What waves will the butterfly stir up in the dazzling city that never sleeps?

“To cleanse the city of its sins, you will serve as the first cycle of the butterfly effect.”
RoleSkin.20137103_Description:
Kanami's choice of loungewear while on vacation. Few realize that beneath the spotlight, the invincible idol is just an ordinary girl offstage, entitled to enjoy her youthful moments.
Still, as an idol, she's always aware of others' gazes, feeling slightly nervous and thrilled, holding onto the person next to her.

"Ba-dum... Can you hear Kanami's heartbeat?"
RoleSkin.20137058_Description: A special version of Kanami's performance outfit, inspired by the fresh green of four-leaf clovers, designed to pass good luck to fans through her songs.
RoleSkin.20108052_Description: The elegant outfit, embroidered with thorns and a sword, symbolizes Nobunaga's turbulent fate and his fearless resolve to confront hardships.
RoleSkin.20133052_Description: With a striking mix of black and white, which side truly represents her? Meredith is as enigmatic as this outfit.
RoleSkin.20128053_Description: The black and red hues symbolize the calamity that befell her hometown. Lawine is determined to give it her all to prevent history from repeating itself.
RoleSkin.20132053_Description: A combat uniform in black and blue, decorated with lightning and eagle emblems. Ming's eyes are as sharp as a hawk's. The outfit highlights her dangerously intimidating aura.

RoleSkin_I18N.20112111_Description:
The realm of martial arts is supreme and pure. For a martial artist to break through in technique, they must first break through their mindset. Fuchsia does not entirely agree, but she secretly hopes to find the answers someday.

“What are martial arts? Why do we practice them? Are the answers really that important? I never cared about these questions, and look how far I've come.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20120051_Description:
"Each type of coffee bean has a unique aroma." Fragrans places the cup of coffee in front of Eika. "This one has floral and fruity notes. It should be delightful."

"Really? Like, as sweet as fruit?... Ah! It's so sour!!!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20110105_Description:
A modified stealth suit inspired by the movie "Phantom Thief," with a sleek, fitted design that matches Bai Mo's taste for style and comfort. However, the added custom bandages and neon glasses kind of defeat the purpose.

Standing in front of a mirror, Bai Mo marvels at his style, but what happens next is unforgettable - “Hmm, cosplaying as the Phantom Thief once in a while isn't half bad. Hey! Let me go! I'm not a thief!”
RoleSkin_I18N.20101101_Description:
A sporty baseball uniform with playful cat ears and a tail. Donning this outfit, Michele seems impressively agile and sharp.

“Steal! Steal! Steal! Base after base!”
As the audience's thunderous cheering fills the stadium, Michele dashes to second base.
Not only is she a super good gamer, Michele is also great at sports.
Her glistening sweat and bright, sunny smile are the most beautiful sight on the field.
RoleSkin_I18N.20133107_Description:
A mysterious guest has appeared at the underground bar. No one knows what brought her here or what secrets she holds.

"Are you sure we haven't met before? I can't help but feel like I've asked you this exact question many times before."
RoleSkin_I18N.20108101_Description:
Nobunaga's exclusive P.U.S. Spec Ops suit blends steel and leather, yet his elegance and calm demeanor remain undiminished.

“Activate remote control and the radar system. Don’t let anything slip past.”
Under Nobunaga's command, a meticulous raid is underway.
However, the operation ended before it even began.
"You must be the target. So, will you surrender? Or will you make me do it?"
RoleSkin_I18N.20137208_NameCn: Century Idol - Light of the Embers
RoleSkin_I18N.20124001_Description: Kokona's custom sniper suit is fully functional with a modest design, suitable for all weather conditions.
RoleSkin_I18N.20133053_Description: A special outfit customized for Meredith with a diamond core symbolizing her sharp, rational, and unwavering resolve.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109103_Description:
A special combat suit designed for experimental high-energy electromagnetic weapons, with enhanced insulation based on Reiichi's combat experience.
The silent sniper enters the battlefield, channeling intense energy.

“Careful. You might get a shock.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20109105_Description:
Reiichi's outfit for chess exhibition matches. The fedora and the extra wide lapel add a touch of leisure to the elegance, while the plain glasses provide a unique impression. Together with the dyed hair, one would not recognize him if not a close acquaintance.

“How many times have I told you? The whole point of the Queen's Gambit is to ensure the safety of the central board. Now isn't the time to sweat over a single pawn.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20109003_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit. Even in total darkness, he harbors a glimmer of hope.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109007_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The army green symbolizes his discipline.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109005_Description:
Reiichi's backup combat suit. Fully functional, it matches the combat capabilities of the original.

“Do not stop fighting. Do not despair.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20109004_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The deep blue hue sings a song of sorrow.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109008_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The light blue lining symbolizes the clear sky in his heart.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109002_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The mysterious purple lining conceals his many burdens.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109009_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The dim green symbolizes his nearly withered yet undying hope.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109010_Description: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The bright shirt contrasts sharply with the dark coat. He rarely wears it.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109001_Description: Reiichi's favorite outfit. It is comfortable, simple, practical, and reliable, exuding the firm will of a warrior.
RoleSkin_I18N.20109104_Description:
Reiichi's custom-made outfit is inspired by old-era spacesuits, with some parts faithfully recreated. However, it has been modified for combat readiness in case of emergencies. If not for the conflicts, Reiichi might have pursued a path to the stars, unleashing his creativity across the vast cosmos.

“Pressure is normal, temperature is normal… Hmm, too bad I couldn't replicate the propulsion system.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20109106_Description:
Reiichi’s special gear for infiltrating the black market emphasizes the mystical allure of Eastern charm and his personal style. The pendant he wears is made from polished scrap, not a genuine antique, but convincing enough to pass as one.

“Heh... You've got a good eye. This is top-notch stuff.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20128101_Description:
Inspired by bamboo, this elegant outfit evokes a sense of peace, filled with Lawine's longing for her homeland.

【In her spare time, she often visits her cabin in the bamboo forest.
Through the gaps in the bamboo forest, the sun shines on the dim wooden floor.
Even with you by her side, she remains silent nonetheless.
Quietly, she hands you a fresh cup of tea.】
RoleSkin_I18N.20107104_Description:
A space-themed white bodysuit featuring stylish mecha rabbit ears, making Maddelena seem less simple and more daring than usual.
 
 “Look! Doesn't the reflection of this outfit resemble moonlight?”
 “I heard that a bunny lived happily on the Moon. Could there be a mecha bunny on Strinova's moon as well?”
 The girl happily dreams of space under the cover of the night.
RoleSkin_I18N.20132206_Description: Named after the ancient thunderous Loong from the East, this heroic attire features dragon and lightning motifs. It travels with its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.

RoleSkin_I18N.20108103_Description:
An outfit inspired by cranes, featuring two white cranes painted on a black background as if they are soaring from an inky pine forest, chasing daylight.
Nobunaga always feels nostalgic when he dons this outfit. During the P.U.S Investigator course, he learned ancient Eastern military strategies—"Crane Wing Formation" was once their forte, requiring two partners to flank the enemy from both sides. Even without a partner, Nobunaga has managed to adapt the same tactics for solo combat.

“I have you surrounded. Surrender now.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20131206_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131207_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
