RoleSkin_I18N.20131210_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131107_Description:
Yvette's outfit for the Urbino talent show. The light dress evokes poetic scenery of ancient civilizations. Yvette may not be the best dancer, but that didn't stop her from becoming the star of the show.

“I dance, for I miss you day and night.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20131105_Description:
Yvette's outfit for the Wilderness Winter Challenge. The elastic warm fleece is suitable for all winter outdoor activities, making it her favorite winter clothing.

“Are you cold? I don't feel cold at all.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20131106_Description:
The outfit Yvette wears to the Safety Day event. A sharp contrast to her usual cool-toned clothing, this outfit replicates a look from a fairy tale. However, unlike the protagonist in the story, she would not surrender without a fight.

【“Would you accept... my safety apple?”】
RoleSkin_I18N.20131004_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The soft orange makes her look even sweeter and more charming.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131007_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The touching warmth is buried deep in the snow.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131006_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The bright yellow brings a warm feeling to the heart.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131008_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The lush summer leaves can hardly conceal the girl's thoughts.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131005_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The budding green resembles fresh sprouts under the sunlight.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131003_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. Beneath her cold exterior, there lies a fiery heart.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131002_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The vibrant purple makes her as graceful as a slender lavender.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131102_Description:
Yvette's beach outfit radiates youthful energy and a refreshing vibe, grabbing everyone's attention, much like a cute panda.

"Pandas are bears too," Yvette giggles, touching her ears. "At least Fei won’t feel alone at the summer music fest with a fellow bear around."
RoleSkin_I18N.20131001_Description: Yvette's favorite lab coat. The pair of teddy ears on the hood reveals her childlike innocence.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131101_Description:
Yvette's outfit for outdoor excursions. The simple, unembellished style reflects her pure heart. Of course, she occasionally shows her cute, girlish side.

【“Eh? You would like to have lunch with us? But I can't find Fay...”
“How about you and I have lunch in secret this time...”
Can Yvette really not find Fay? Or...
She is the only one who can give you the answer to that question.】
RoleSkin_I18N.20205052_Description:
It's rumored that Galatea designed this dress after gazing at the night sky for half an hour. Others say inspiration struck after she visited the Cloudscape Gallery's jewelry exhibition. Galatea neither confirms nor denies these rumors.


"Stars and gemstones are quite similar, aren't they?"
RoleSkin_I18N.20133055_Description: An elegant outfit symbolizing scales of justice. A noble adjudicator shall deliver judgments for the world.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108107_Description:
Nobunaga's outfit for chess exhibition matches. The black and white checkered pattern and smooth lines exude a sense of fashion and elegance, making it Nobunaga's perfect “armor” for important occasions. Nobunaga used to be weary of the Bureau of Investigation's participation in such events, but...

“I thought you and I were just like these two pieces, never truly able to touch one another.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20108104_Description:
Nobunaga's racing suit for the Winter Wilderness Challenges offers great thermal insulation. The snow goggles and snug fit aid in securing the lead during snow races.

“Nobunaga! Again! That's his third Winter Wilderness title!”
RoleSkin_I18N.20108008_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The light fades, leaving only ashes.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108004_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, surging with emotions like waves rolling in.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108007_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit—the rust does not hide his lofty ambition.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108003_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, symbolizing his will to break through obstacles like flying sparks.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108005_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The flashing lightning represents his courage and wisdom.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108006_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The dazzling amethyst represents his elegance and pride.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108002_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, as fearless as a clear sky after rain.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108056_Description: Nobunaga's custom uniform features the rich green of a bamboo forest, perfectly highlighting the wearer's calm demeanor.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108108_Description:
Nobunaga dons this outfit when he is in charge of security at theater events. Inspired by the Mediterranean culture of old Earth, the design features a deep, understated style, conveying a sense of freedom and mystery.

“Toiling in the darkness, serving the light - Was it the same for that person?”
RoleSkin_I18N.20115103_Description:
Wearing a beautiful dress, Flavia is as glamorous as a dazzling peacock, capturing the spotlight on the dance floor.

"Don't stress about it. Leave it to me. As your dance partner, I'll take care of you."
RoleSkin_I18N.20146055_Description: The elegant purple dress accentuates Celestia's mysterious elegance. It suits her well, but she never speaks of the story behind it.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205007_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by top-grade cymophane.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205002_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by the colors of a peacock's eye.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205005_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by a gloomy dusk with impending snow.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205006_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. It is said that the color scheme was inspired by ripe grapes in the vineyard.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205004_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by an upper-class banquet.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205003_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by a lush bamboo forest.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205001_Description: Galatea's magic show outfit is understatedly elegant. To avoid being recognized, she puts on a wide-brimmed hat—ironically making her even more eye-catching.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146206_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a sharp and bold spirit.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146207_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a sharp and bold spirit.

RoleSkin_I18N.20146210_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a sharp and bold spirit.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110052_Description: A combat hoodie with a cola print, perfectly matching Bai Mo's vibe. Wearing this outfit, Bai Mo bursts with energy and passion, just like a shaken can of cola.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137101_Description:
Kanami wears this stunning gown only for formal events. It blends youthful romance with mature elegance, highlighting her unique brilliance.

"This is the dress I wore when I first took the stage as an idol. I will never forget how I felt back then. I must meet everyone's expectations to feel that kind of emotion again."
RoleSkin_I18N.20105101_Description:
The maid outfit worn by the manager of Café Reminiscence has been tailored to Audrey's liking. Despite the outfit, Audrey's elite leadership aura remains unmistakable.

"Go ahead, take a good look! B-But make sure to try our new coffee... please?"
RoleSkin_I18N.20120053_Description:
During The Scissors' castle exploration, Fragrans, to everyone's surprise, was the fastest to emerge, even with a blindfold on.
"Bats use sound; I use scent... The air outside the castle is indeed much fresher."
RoleSkin_I18N.20120054_Description:
After an aquarium trip with her friends, Fragrans made herself a jellyfish-themed outfit.
“Jellyfish... they strike me as light blue flowers blooming on the seabed.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20105056_Description:
Walls, turrets, gates—when it comes to classic castle design, that's Audrey's expertise. To assess this property's potential, Audrey donned a brand-new outfit.

"I'm just in need of a horror-themed mansion."
RoleSkin_I18N.20105001_Description: A mercenary outfit designed by Audrey, integrating her love for glamor into the noble aesthetics inherited from her mother.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105010_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Luxurious yet understated, the outfit showcases her resilient will.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105009_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her gaze reaches the vast ocean.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105008_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her gaze reaches the vast ocean.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105006_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Secrets flow beneath the simple attire.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105002_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her unwavering will stands firm like a green mountain.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105007_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. A verdant meadow lies within her dreams.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105005_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. True elegance needs no lavish adornment.
RoleSkin_I18N.20105109_Description:
Audrey's outfit for the Spring Blessings family banquet features a dress inspired by the sunset glow and a moonlit shawl, blending graceful elegance with youthful allure.

"Please, have a seat. You are an honored guest at the Grove family banquet."
RoleSkin_I18N.20105105_Description:
The outfit Audrey wears while exploring the True Wilderness. Lightweight and comfortable, the outfit lets air through and helps cool the body. The camera in the bag captures visions of the future.

"I must personally inspect the new development areas in collaboration with P.U.S. These photos will witness the rise of a new metropolis."
RoleSkin_I18N.20105110_Description:
Audrey's custom work outfit. Serious yet fashionable, it is her go-to choice for important occasions. The design has since become popular among office ladies of Neutroville.

“I'm in a hurry - I have another decision to make.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20110053_Description: A combat uniform in the style of a spacesuit, not only reflecting Bai Mo's unique personality but also possessing an elegant sense of fantasy.
RoleSkin_I18N.20205054_Description:
Although Galatea is used to being in noisy environments, she occasionally retreats to the peaceful mountains and forests.

“I listen to human voices all the time. Sometimes, I just want to hear what nature has to say.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20128104_Description:
Beneath the flamboyant combat uniform lies Lawine's calm and rational heart. In the shadows, she strikes with lethal precision.

Under the night sky, a shadow races through the city.
No one sees her. No one hears her.
“You let your guard down... playing right into my hands.”
Lawine, the enforcer of The Scissors, strikes again against those who oppose her faith.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124103_Description:
The outfit Kokona wears as a guide at the Space Center features radiation protection, making it ideal for space engineers.

"Astronaut Kokona out of the spacecraft and reporting for duty. I'm feeling great!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20124053_Description: A modified version of Kokona's combat uniform, incorporating the stripes of a white tiger into the design. Donning this outfit, she appears exceptionally valiant and undeniably dangerous.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124105_Description:
The outfit Kokona wears to mountain biking competitions in the fall. Light and durable, it offers excellent breathability and wind resistance reduction and comes equipped with a sufficient tool kit. Rumor has it that Kokona won the championship wearing this outfit.

"Are you surprised? Great power lies in my body!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20124106_Description:
The formal dress Kokona prepared for the Golden Tree Symphony concert, featuring a cute little hat that showcases her playfulness and eagerness for the challenge.

"Care to try a piano duet? How can a conductor excel without understanding the music?"
RoleSkin_I18N.20124104_Description:
A piece of outdoor gear modified by Kokona. Originally intended for exploration, it has been transformed into a ceremonial outfit suitable for outings and picnics. Speaking of which, the strawberries on the outfit seem to be edible.

“If you're interested, feel free to have a bite.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20124108_Description: The most romanticized explorer image in Xinxia's mind comes from the popular action-adventure movie series. Xinxia visited old clothing design stores and customized this classic outfit piece by piece. ["Treasures! There are treasures everywhere! Hehe~ But compared to the treasures, I prefer the adventures I encountered along the way!"]
RoleSkin_I18N.20124002_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform. The light pink lifts the spirits.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124005_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in light purple, resembling the twilight.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124007_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in light green, making one feel melancholic.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124003_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform. The mix of gray and blue resembles the sky over the mountains.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124004_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in azure, resembling the autumn sky.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124008_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in red and white, suitable for medical operations.
RoleSkin_I18N.20124006_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in green camouflage, perfect for stealth operations.
RoleSkin_I18N.20131108_Description:
Goggles, tactical helmet, combat suit... At the Navigator's invitation, Yvette thoroughly equipped herself with all the gear a tactical analyst needs. Although the battlefield is nothing like the lab, Yvette utilizes her analytical and research skills to support her allies on the front lines.

"T-Tactical Analyst Yvette reporting for duty..."
Her shy, soft voice trembles slightly.
"Um... Navigator, did the combat data I collected help anyone?”
Those gentle, familiar hands softly brush her forehead.
The nervous, blushing girl gradually calms down. The Navigator's reassurance seems to be a magical remedy, empowering her to face anything with courage and resolve.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128106_Description:
The outfit Lawine wears to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. Its rebellious design makes her stand out in the classical setting, drawing all eyes.

"Music does calm the heart. I don't mind joining you."
RoleSkin_I18N.20128109_Description:
Lawine's maid outfit for working undercover at the café. The red and black tones exude a sense of profound elegance, while the twin daggers hidden behind her add a dangerous touch of beauty.

“The daggers? They're for your protection. Please relax, my dear guest...”
RoleSkin_I18N.20128003_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The cold blue evokes a chill in the heart.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128007_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform in blue, resembling the silent cold night.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128004_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The forest green hem looks particularly sleek and neat.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128002_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The dazzling gold dust flows like fine sand in the wind.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128008_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform in blue, making her as sharp as thunder on a rainy night.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128005_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The beautiful purple showcases her graceful figure.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128006_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform in green, resembling grass fluttering in the wind.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128201_Description: The loungewear Lawine dons at home. Only her true friends have a chance to see her in this outfit.
RoleSkin_I18N.20108001_Description: Captain Nobunaga's specialized 1st Division outfit reflects his meticulous approach and disciplined attitude.
RoleSkin_I18N.20132055_Description: Ming's racing outfit incorporates her favorite racing elements. Behind wheels, she turns into a blue whirlwind, becoming the swiftest presence on the track.
RoleSkin_I18N.20132107_Description:
Ming's outfit for a night out during Spring Blessings. The bold red dress makes her look spirited and valiant, capturing a heroine's flair.

"No, I'm not here to uphold justice, just to savor some good food and drinks!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20132001_Description: Ming's combat suit effortlessly combines practicality and style, making it perfect for both battles and everyday wear.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146106_Description:
Celestia's outfit for meteor shower nights combines warmth with style. Its thicker material keeps her cozy while the cute design highlights her simple beauty under the starry sky.

“The beauty of a meteor lies in its fleeting light. Like meteors, we cross the night sky and find each other.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20146105_Description:
The outfit Celestia prepared for the amusement park event. The refreshing denim jacket exudes a sense of excitement while the hat perfectly covers her shy eyes when pulled down...

“There are still many attractions left... um, you don't have to look at me, you know?”
RoleSkin_I18N.20146109_Description:
Celestia's outfit for hosting the Spring Blessings Eve event at Astral Sanctuary. The decorated skirt can't conceal her wish to explore the night with the one she holds most dear.

"Would you go for a walk with me after the event? Just the two of us."
RoleSkin_I18N.20146201_Description: Celestia only puts on this loungewear when resting. Only those closest to her have a chance to see her in this outfit.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146104_Description:
An experimental spacesuit Celestia wears at the Space Center. Made from various polymer materials, the outfit offers excellent insulation and impact resistance. Originally designed for interstellar travel, it now resides in the museum for visitors to experience.

“Before stepping into space, we ventured into the fog of dimensions. That's what the tag says.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20146006_Description: Astierred's spare work uniform. The leaf-like skirt subtly reveals patterns of stars.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146007_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform. The deep blue dress gives her an air of mystery.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146011_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in elegant purple, suitable for formal occasions.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146009_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in navy blue, highlighting her grace.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146010_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in warm orange, reminiscent of lights and delicacies.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146005_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in lime green, accentuating her charm.
RoleSkin_I18N.20146008_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in purple, flowing like a drifting cloud.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120052_Description:
Spring is Fragrans' favorite season, full of vitality and renewal.
"Let's make this year's first fragrance a sakura scent."
RoleSkin_I18N.20205055_Description:
Who cast the old castle into darkness, and who turned that darkness into a new stage?

“A magician knows more tricks than making doves appear out of thin air. Bats could also do the trick.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20112054_Description: The crane ascends into the blue sky, taking hopes and dreams with it.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112101_Description:
The outfit is inspired by hunters who once roamed the forests at night. Its bizarre design embodies the tension of the era.

“Come on, Fuchsia. You're the only one left! The Nightstalker suits you perfectly!”
“This outfit is not suitable for carrying out missions.”
“Live a little, would you? Come on, it's photo time!”
“Uh... fine.”

Hearing her companions' teasing, Fuchsia remains silent for a while. She knows it's all in fun and that no matter how her outfit changes, her past remains unchanged.
Yet for some reason, she feels a long-lost sense of warmth in her heart.
RoleSkin_I18N.20133051_Description: An outfit prepared by Meredith for aquatic field research. She moves cautiously under the cover of the waves.
RoleSkin_I18N.20133106_Description:
Meredith puts on this outfit when performing with her band. The bold design reflects her understanding of the spirit of rock n' roll. A composed scholar, Meredith also longs for freedom without restraints.

“Rock n' roll embodies freedom and exploration, aligning perfectly with the spirit of science.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20124102_Description:
Inspired by flight suits from old movies, this outfit reflects Kokona's unfulfilled dreams. Ever curious, she has always yearned for the sky and distant lands, eager to explore the unknown.

“Let's see. This is the center stick, and that is the altimeter... Relax. I've read the manual dozens of times. Remember where to pull to activate the ejection seat. We're taking off!”
RoleSkin_I18N.20101206_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101207_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101208_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101209_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101210_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107103_Description:
The beautiful seaside inspires the young painter. The refreshing sailor suit makes her even more charming.

【The azure sea, the white waves, and the singing crowd; Maddelena is intoxicated by the beautiful scene.
Taking out the paintbrush she carries with her at all times, she expresses her emotions onto the canvas.
After a while, a sudden idea comes to her:
Deep in everyone's heart, there is an ocean unique to them.】
RoleSkin_I18N.20137053_Description: This elegant mint-colored outfit makes Kanami appear even more pure and charming, adding a touch of coolness to the passionate summer concert.
RoleSkin_I18N.20115104_Description:
Wearing a vibrant and elegant restaurant uniform, Flavia seamlessly blends into a street-side café. Under the beautiful sunset, Flavia and the guests savor Iberian delicacies as much as the romantic atmosphere.

"At sunset, I serve them jamón ibérico and all its rich flavors."
RoleSkin_I18N.20107105_Description:
Maddelena's outfit for flash mob performances. Ever since the Golden Tree Symphony event, her passion for music has awakened, though not for classical tunes...

"Melodies exist only for a moment before vanishing. Don't you find it romantic?"
RoleSkin_I18N.20107110_Description:
Maddelena prepared this outfit for the amusement park event. Its cute design blends seamlessly with the park's cartoon characters.

【“I'm only dressed like this to better understand children's feelings... After all, I get commissioned to create children's picture books from time to time.”】
RoleSkin_I18N.20107106_Description:
The outfit Maddelena wears to the Golden Tree Symphony concert, designed by herself. The small hat sometimes helps her hide her shy face.

"I can't afford to embarrass myself here!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20107007_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The interwoven silver and red make her stand out from the crowd.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107010_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit, incredibly clear like a lake in winter.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107011_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit, modest and serene like leaves of fall.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107002_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The bright green symbolizes vitality and vigor.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107004_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The deep indigo symbolizes creativity and intuition.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107003_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The tender pink resembles butterflies and blooming flowers.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107009_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The interwoven blue and green resemble ripples in a lake.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107008_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The noble purple makes her seem like a flower swaying in the wind.
RoleSkin_I18N.20107108_Description:
Maddelena designed this vibrant classic dress after doing a lot of research. When she dances, tambourines ring with her every move, reflecting the romantic charm of a bygone era.

“I initially just needed some inspiration, but now I've completely fallen in love with the dance!”
RoleSkin_I18N.20107201_Description: Loungewear designed by Maddelena, inspired by the green fields and orange fruit. Coming up with fun designs at home with you is the precious time she cherishes the most.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120005_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat. Its deep rose color highlights her mature elegance.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120002_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, in a refreshing green reminiscent of freshly sprouted tea leaves.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120006_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, with tones reminiscent of autumn leaves, foreshadowing winter's arrival.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120004_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat. The violet blooms in the night, as intoxicating as fine wine.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120007_Description: An alternative color scheme for Fragrans' lab coat, where blue symbolizes not just melancholy, but also inner peace.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120003_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, featuring a purity akin to refined essence.
RoleSkin_I18N.20120102_Description:
Fragrans' medical attire, whether she's accustomed to it or not, serves the same purpose: to heal and soothe.

"It's important for you to rest well."
RoleSkin_I18N.20120001_Description: Fragrans' smart and elegant lab coat is exactly what you'd expect from a person with such a scholarly temperament.
RoleSkin_I18N.20133001_Description: A special combat uniform crafted with the cutting-edge technology of The Scissors, incorporating Meredith's lifetime of knowledge into its complex design.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110101_Description:
A baker's uniform designed by Bai Mo, featuring an avant-garde design and comfortable lining. However, he has rarely had the chance to put it on.

【“Look. This blueberry milk bread is golden on the outside with a soft and fluffy texture and a sweet and sour taste. I baked it myself. ”
Bai Mo once worked undercover in one of his bakeries for several days.
Seeing people enjoy the bread he has baked fills his heart with joy.
To this day, that remains one of his fondest memories.】
RoleSkin_I18N.20110001_Description: Bai Mo wears this mercenary outfit when he is out on missions. The design emphasizes practicality while incorporating streetwear elements - sleek, carefree, unfettered.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110056_Description: Bai Mo's barista outfit is rumored to be from when he secretly worked at a cafe in Urbino for half a month.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110007_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit. He has battled waves and dived into the depths of the sea.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110002_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit makes him look like a young boy about to enjoy a picnic.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110005_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, resembling the vast green fields in his childhood dreams.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110006_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, resembling the autumn leaves that dance in the wind of freedom.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110004_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, bold yet romantic and elegant.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110008_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit. In the sea of sand, the voice of freedom will stir a new storm.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110003_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit in elegant lake blue reflects his unrestrained spirit.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110106_Description:
A performance suit customized by the Bai Group. Donning this outfit, Bai Mo exudes a calm and dignified aura; that is until he speaks...

【“My pitch isn't half bad, right?”】
RoleSkin_I18N.20101112_Description:
Michele's outfit for the Spring Blessings fireworks celebration. The vibrant dress captures the festive spirit, and the jingling gold bells announce the arrival of spring.

"Ding-dong! What are you waiting for? The fireworks celebration is about to start!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20101011_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in an industrial style, reliable and practical.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101008_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a muted khaki, simple and durable.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101009_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a bright, spritely pink.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101012_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a calm, subdued blue-gray.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101006_Description: Michele's investigator uniform in a minty fresh blue.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101007_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a lively spring green.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101010_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a mysterious, ethereal purple.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101110_Description:
Michele's Campus Open Day esports outfit includes a compact backpack that opens into an Esports Club game console. Cute accessories highlight her identity as a passionate gamer.

"Gaming and studying aren't at odds—a super gamer puts 100% passion into both!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20132104_Description:
A rugged cowboy outfit that embodies a maverick's longing for freedom and adventure. Thinking of this, Ming whistles cheerfully.

“Let's pull off a big score!”
RoleSkin_I18N.20115102_Description:
A luxurious and elegant maid outfit inspired by butterflies. Donning this enhancing outfit, Flavia mysteriously appears in the café. She seems to have obtained important intel about someone.

“Are you looking to trade information? You'll have to defeat me first.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20124055_Description: An elegant outfit with snowflake and pine tree patterns becomes even more graceful on Kokona. She alone may understand its true significance.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112102_Description:
Fuchsia's assassination suit for urban combat, combining practicality and mobility with her personal aesthetics. The shark-fin aerodynamic panels further aid in gliding. Donning this outfit, she becomes a shadow darting between buildings, speaking via the sound of gunfire.

【“Bang! A quick and clean end. That's all.”】
RoleSkin_I18N.20112105_Description:
A maid outfit designed by Fuchsia, reflecting her understanding of maid duties. It is lightweight and tight-fitting, allowing Fuchsia to display her powerful and efficient combat abilities.

"If you don't want to end up on the declutter list... stay out of the way."
RoleSkin_I18N.20112103_Description:
Fuchsia's outfit during the first Champion of Relaxation competition. Lightweight, comfortable, and cool, the outfit features brown and green tones that allow her to blend into her surroundings as she treks through rivers and mountains.

“Thanks to my outfit, I could sneak up on animals without being noticed... An interesting experience.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20112104_Description:
The outfit Fuchsia wore to the holiday parade. Originally intended to help her keep a low profile while protecting VIPs, its attention-grabbing design unexpectedly made her the star of the parade.

“What a noisy bunch.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20112106_Description:
Fuchsia wears this outfit when she works as a bartender in the underground bar. Watching her expert moves, one can't help but ask,

"Why are you so skilled at this?!"

"It's nothing out of the ordinary. I just like to be the best in every field, bartending included. Would you like a drink?"
RoleSkin_I18N.20112206_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112207_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112208_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112209_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112210_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112007_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. May all who walk upon this earth be free.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112006_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. Aren't humans just another type of fish?
RoleSkin_I18N.20112003_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. The eye-catching red signifies the heat of the muzzle.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112002_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform, cold as ice, sharp as a killer.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112005_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat suit: Purple isn't just mysterious, it can also be deadly.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112008_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. Stealth is not just about concealing one's presence.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112004_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat suit, designed for twilight—the witching hour, when demons emerge, ready to devour.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112057_Description: Fuchsia's athletic outfit features a striking mix of pink shark and teal iceberg, creating a unique visual impact.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112001_Description: A professional assassin's tight suit. Born for battle, its streamlined design is devoid of any superfluous elements.
RoleSkin_I18N.20119101_Description:
Eika’s self-styled outdoor gear showcases bold and edgy fashion that embodies the wild spirit of a high school girl. Exactly where she "lets loose" after school is her little secret.

“The day of a high school student only begins after school!”
RoleSkin_I18N.20119055_Description: Eika's uniform for her farm job. Based on a basic work uniform, it blends elements of meadow green and earthy tones. Her cheerful presence is a hit at the farm, even attracting the farm's robotic herding dog. Are they playing a friendly game... or is Eika simply afraid of dogs?
RoleSkin_I18N.20119052_Description: Eika's outfit for her café job, inspired by the "Manager's Daily Coffee Pick." As both a barista and model, Eika often prepares coffee for customers herself. Her sales figures are said to be impressive.
RoleSkin_I18N.20119102_Description:
Eika put together this outfit for her side job at the planetarium, blending elements from sci-fi movies with a girl's dreamy imagination of the stars. While working inside the planetarium, Eika realizes that being a galactic courier could be the coolest job ever.

"If our family restaurant spanned the universe, would I have to deliver food among planets?"
RoleSkin_I18N.20119053_Description: Eika's fast food uniform. This unique combo of a school and staff attire, helps her look the part and complements her youthful style. Rumor is that the dripping red feature was inspired by Eika's mournful experience of accidentally spilling chili sauce all over a big plate of chicken nuggets.
RoleSkin_I18N.20119051_Description: The outfit Eika wears while working at a fashion store, blending uniform style with trending pink and dark city designs. As an in-store model, Eika often showcases these outfits herself, reportedly boosting sales impressively.
RoleSkin_I18N.20119054_Description: Eika wears this uniform when working part-time at the game store. It's accented with the color scheme of a popular gaming console. Promoting games is part of the job, so Eika often competes with pro gamers. It's become quite the attraction.
RoleSkin_I18N.20119001_Description: Eika's school uniform is the most common style in the Preton region. However, due to Eika's high body temperature, she has specially modified it with ventilation openings.
RoleSkin_I18N.20115051_Description: Flavia's custom outfit, inspired by coffee, milk, and cream. Walking the line between coffee and milk is a dangerous game.
RoleSkin_I18N.20115001_Description: Flavia's combat uniform features a simple and comfortable design. Butterfly elements add a final touch, highlighting the wearer's elegant charm.
RoleSkin_I18N.20101107_Description:
A blue and white navy combat suit, thoughtfully designed to match Michele's fighting style, complete with a communication device and a cute survival backpack. Facing the sea breeze, Michele looks even more spirited than usual.

“Anchors aweigh! Hope you don't get seasick!”
RoleSkin_I18N.20205051_Description:
Though Galatea prefers "stronger" drinks over coffee, she admits that these coffee beans do have a unique flavor.

"Hmm... Next time, I'll add some liquor and make spiked Sidra coffee."
RoleSkin_I18N.20110103_Description:
A futuristic sports outfit with bright colors and a sleek design. Bai Mo has infused it with his own unique touches.

"Oh, you've found me! Are you here to take me back as well?"
Although cornered, Bai Mo still bears a cunning smile.
"I'm not slacking off. The leader of Urbino must be free. Locking me in an office would be a huge waste."
As you're drawn in by his words, he leaps away, skillfully escaping your view with expert parkour.
RoleSkin_I18N.20128001_Description: A special ops suit compatible with The Scissors' optical camouflage technology. Efficient and practical, it was designed specifically for Lawine.
RoleSkin_I18N.20112110_Description:
Aside from a well-stocked arsenal, victory in battle requires clever strategies and overwhelming firepower. Fuchsia knows this well, as shown by her Shark Squad's success in live-action shooter games.

"If you're my eagle eyes, Navigator, then I'm your shark teeth. Let's win this, just like we always do!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20110051_Description: A chef's outfit featuring patterns of fish and bamboo leaves, reminiscent of the aroma of sushi. To Bai Mo, freedom and delicacies are the two most important things in life.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137104_Description:
The outfit Kanami wore when she performed in a rural concert. The mud on her light dungarees skirt does not ruin her cute style. Kanami chose to keep this outfit after the show ended.

“There's something so satisfying about watching the crops grow day by day.”
RoleSkin_I18N.20137108_Description:
Kanami's costume for her mythological play. Inspired by a Greek goddess, the dress resembles pure ocean waves with a skirt shaped like a mermaid's tail, topped with a golden laurel for a touch of sanctity.

“I will pray for you. Always.” The girl pours all her emotions and thoughts into the final line. “Rehearsing with you really does... Uh, never mind.”

The girl hesitates for a moment before deciding not to finish her sentence.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137055_Description: Kanami's promotional outfit for the coffee brand was inspired by latte art, designed to convey a warm, coffee-like sentiment to her fans.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137106_Description:
Kanami wore this dress, which borrows elements from the tuxedo and the tutu, for the magic show that she was invited to perform in at Laurel Hall. Elegance and romance are Kanami's eternal pursuits, and there seems to be a hidden mystery in the gorgeous ornaments on the skirt.

"Phew... You can do it, Kanami. We must get our things back!"
RoleSkin_I18N.20137105_Description:
The outfit Kanami wears when invited to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. It highlights her charm and coordination with the conductor. Intentional, perhaps?

"I would like to dream the most beautiful dream with you."
RoleSkin_I18N.20137056_Description: Kanami's special edition costume is inspired by a sunflower field under the bright sun, showcasing Kanami's boundless ardor.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137051_Description: Kanami's special performance costume, with a charming yet slightly dangerous aura. Perhaps she will appear in your dreams tonight.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137006_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume, as elegant as a phoenix and as subtle as a dragon's whisper.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137005_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume. The nightingale's song lingers in the endless night.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137004_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume in brilliant violet, blooming to its fullest.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137003_Description: Kanami's spare performance outfit, in dazzling orange and yellow, mirrors the passionate flames in her heart.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137007_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume. The gilded color reflects the idol's radiance.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137002_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume in cyan, resembling delicate petals.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137008_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume in green, symbolizing growth.
RoleSkin_I18N.20137001_Description: Kanami's performance outfit is both beautiful and practical. Its slender, flowing design resembles a nightingale spreading its wings.
RoleSkin_I18N.20132102_Description:
A tight combat uniform in black and red that blends high-tech and retro aesthetics. Her cool and tough facade does little to hide the burning heat deep in her soul.

“Don't make a mess. I don't have time to clean up after you.”
“Listen to me if you want to live! Understood?”
Under Ming's command, each attack is as sharp as a scalpel.
But she fights not for distant ideals, but for survival and the wrath deep within her.
RoleSkin_I18N.20110054_Description: A black and green racing-style combat uniform makes Bai Mo look dashing and unique. Speed and passion perfectly describe him.

RoleTeam.3_TeamDesc: These Strinovian from all walks of life have banded together to fight for their "own ideals."
RoleTeam.2_TeamDesc: Active in all parts of Strinova society, this mysterious organization is not to be underestimated. They are wary of the changes in Strinova and hold a deep suspicion toward "Utopia."
RoleTeam.1_TeamDesc: Led by Sistine and made up of veteran agents and talented newcomers, PUS is dedicated to protecting the order and security of "Utopia."

RoomGraphGuide.11_Desc: In Solo Brawl, you fight alone, with enemies in every direction.
RoomGraphGuide.22_Desc: Second, defuse the device before the timer runs out.
RoomGraphGuide.12_Desc: To survive the onslaught, you must have good aim and movement.
RoomGraphGuide.13_Desc: Try to avoid getting caught in the crossfire. Strike your targets amidst the chaos.
RoomGraphGuide.20_Desc: Victory is only achieved when the bomb detonates or all enemies are eliminated.
RoomGraphGuide.17_Desc: As the attacker, you need to cover the teammate carrying the bomb as they enter the bomb site and plant the bomb.
RoomGraphGuide.21_Desc: If you're a defender, there are two ways to win. Eliminate all enemies before the bomb is planted.
RoomGraphGuide.5_Desc: Additionally, you can stringify and stick to all sides of the payload.
RoomGraphGuide.18_Desc: If the teammate carrying the bomb goes down, it will be dropped at their current location.
RoomGraphGuide.24_Desc: The first team to reach the target score wins.
RoomGraphGuide.23_Desc: Also, after playing the set number of rounds, both sides will switch roles.
RoomGraphGuide.14_Desc: After all, eliminating the required number of enemies is the only way to win.
RoomGraphGuide.16_Desc: Knowing the map layout, bomb sites, and key routes is the first step.
RoomGraphGuide.19_Desc: Stay alert even after planting the bomb—don't celebrate too soon.
RoomGraphGuide.6_Desc: Master these rules, and victory will be yours.
RoomGraphGuide.2_Desc: Attackers must escort the payload along the route to the destination in time.
RoomGraphGuide.3_Desc: Defenders must intercept the payload and eliminate enemies in its path.
RoomGraphGuide.4_Desc: Note that the attackers can only push the payload when they stay close to it.

RoomModeSet.1_LockTips: Reach Lv. {0} to unlock the mode. Please try another mode for now.
